   <text:p text:style-name="P20">Scrieri</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">Bolliac,Cezar</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P18">Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 Unported (CC BY-SA 3.0) <text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T10">https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/</text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T10"><text:line-break/></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P19"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/Autor:Cezar_Bolliac" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T11">https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/Autor:Cezar_Bolliac</text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T11"><text:line-break/></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">ro</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="P24" text:outline-level="1">Poezii</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Carnavalul</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">ncepe carnavalul! i-n salele bogate<text:line-break/>Se cerc artiti i muzici plceri mai noi s-arate,<text:line-break/>n nou veselii!<text:line-break/>O! ce de griji acuma la nou toalete!<text:line-break/>Ce visuri dulci, frumoase, n junele cochete!<text:line-break/>Ce mii de bucurii!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Fetia tot viseaz la flori, l-a ei ghirlant,<text:line-break/>La gaza cea subire, la rochia-i elegant<text:line-break/>i la ai ei cercei;<text:line-break/>Gndete la rspunsuri, la graii, la cuvinte;<text:line-break/>i rde n oglind de loc ce-i pune-n minte<text:line-break/>Ceva ce-i place ei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Corsetul aci-i pune; i cearc iar rochia,<text:line-break/>Pandlica care-o prinde,  srac copilia!<text:line-break/>Viaa-i e roman!<text:line-break/>O! ct a s mai joace! Ce bine a s-i vie<text:line-break/>i pr i rochi, pandlice, buchet de iasomie<text:line-break/>La sol n contra-dan!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Mulime de machine prin case de neveste!<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Fmei i croitorii abia le prinzi de veste<text:line-break/>Cnd vin, cnd se strecor!<text:line-break/>Prinii schimb cifre n foile de zestre;<text:line-break/>Galanii-n neastmpr citesc pe sub ferestre<text:line-break/>Bileturi dulci d-amor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">O! cte case nou i cte case sparte!<text:line-break/>Ce visuri i mai face btrni i juni n parte<text:line-break/>n lungul carnaval!<text:line-break/>Tot fierbe-n capital! i lumea i propune<text:line-break/>Un lan de fericire, un ir de lucruri bune<text:line-break/>De la ntiul bal!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Voi, ci v rde soarta! gndii c-n aste zile<text:line-break/>Stau sub pmnturi, ocne, prin temnii i exile<text:line-break/>Ati nevinovai,<text:line-break/>Pe care pizma, ura i neagra calomnie<text:line-break/>I-au prsit cruzimei, i oarba tiranie<text:line-break/>i ia necercetai!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Cnd armsarii votri, cu coama lor pletoas,<text:line-break/>Alerg i scapr iute p-o ghea-alunecoas,<text:line-break/>Ca fulger, ca nluc;<text:line-break/>i lng drumul vostru,  o! tremur n cale<text:line-break/>Un biet btrn ca iarna, cu piept, picioare goale,<text:line-break/>Flmnd i fr suc;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">S-oprete, -i ia cciula, spre voi mna ntinde,<text:line-break/>i trista lui ctare n rug se aprinde<text:line-break/>Vznd c nu-l vedei;<text:line-break/>i tremurndu-i barba, spre ceruri mormiete;<text:line-break/>Cnd sania din urm de ziduri l strivete;<text:line-break/>Voi trecei i rdei!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Nebunilor ce suntei! V pare c e o glum<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Un cap strivit de ziduri, un om ce se consum<text:line-break/>De foame i de frig!<text:line-break/>V pare c e glum cnd crunt disperarea<text:line-break/>i int ctre ceruri;  v rdei voi de starea<text:line-break/>Victimelor ce strig:<text:line-break/>.....................................<text:line-break/>.....................................</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="III"/>III</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Cnd o cldur dulce, samururi, catifele,<text:line-break/>Sub draperii bogate de stofe, de dantele,<text:line-break/>V-adoarme p-un divan;<text:line-break/>Cnd mii lumini ascunse n lampe colorate<text:line-break/>Resfrng i v-nmulete-n oglinzile-ardicate<text:line-break/>De jos pn-n tavan;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">-o copili dulce, rznd, graioas,<text:line-break/>n reverene intr uoar i frumoas<text:line-break/>Ca i un ngera, -<text:line-break/>i dup ea un june mre, voios i tare,<text:line-break/>Cu faa vie, plin, cu fruntea-ntins, mare,<text:line-break/>i ed p-un scuna;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Cnd v vedei ntr-nii pre voi miniatur,<text:line-break/>i gest, organ, accente, oricare a lor trsur<text:line-break/>E-a voastr,  i iubii!<text:line-break/>i vede muma soul, i tata iar soia;<text:line-break/>i tii c-avei mijloace, v iart avuia<text:line-break/>S-i facei fericii;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Oare gndii atuncea c poate-n alt cas<text:line-break/>Au doi btrni o fat, tot astfel de frumoas,<text:line-break/>Dar e trit ru;<text:line-break/>i plng, cci mine poate copila o s-apuce<text:line-break/>O cale... n-au de hran; i viaa este dulce,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>C-aa va Dumnezeu.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="IV"/>IV</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Cnd cina v ateapt n sala de mncare,<text:line-break/>i-n giurul vostru vase cu flori mirositoare<text:line-break/>V-mbat de miros;<text:line-break/>Cnd ochii vi se pierde pe mese ncrcate<text:line-break/>D-argint, de porelane, cristale tot-spate,<text:line-break/>C-un viu foc luminos;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">i cnd pe masa voastr cea plin de legume<text:line-break/>Ce globu-ntreg produce, d-esene i de spume,<text:line-break/>De vinuri spumegnd,<text:line-break/>Vedei ndestularea ce car, grmdete,<text:line-break/>-un ir de servi n prajm ce-alerg, v ocolete<text:line-break/>Punnd i ardicnd;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Atunci, atunci gndit-ai c lng casa voastr<text:line-break/>Este-o csu veche i spart, mic, proast;<text:line-break/>i crivu lund<text:line-break/>Hrtia din ferestre, un viscol o petrece,<text:line-break/>Bag n ea zpada; e frig ntr-nsa, rece,<text:line-break/>Cci toat e n vnt!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Gndit-ai vre o dat c-aci-n ast cocioab,<text:line-break/>O vduv srac, bolnav, goal, slab,<text:line-break/>Cu ase copilai,<text:line-break/>Stau n ocol pre vatra abia cu un tciune!<text:line-break/>L-e frig, l-e somn, l-e foame i pic de slbiciune,<text:line-break/>O, mult sunt drglai!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Cnd unul dintre dnii ardic-o mnui<text:line-break/>Scu roie ca racu, i-i zice: &quot;Miculi,<text:line-break/>Te scoal&apos;, nu mai dormi!<text:line-break/>N-e frig i ne e foame; te scoal&apos;! f focu mare!<text:line-break/>D-mi pine! Pune masa!&apos; i ea,-n delir, tresare!<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Nu poate a-i mai mini.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Se scoal,-i smulge prul i iese pe zpad,<text:line-break/>i vede casa voastr n veci tot n parad,<text:line-break/>n veci n veselii:<text:line-break/>Ferestrile-ndoite ce crap de lumin<text:line-break/>i vesela-v umbr rznd, dulce, lin,<text:line-break/>Sltnd n bucurii...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Curnd! Dai n genunche! Uitai! O! piar slava!<text:line-break/>Blstemele s-azvrl, precum s-azvrl lava<text:line-break/>Ce-o vars un vulcan!<text:line-break/>O! Tremurai! cci glasu-i n ceruri e puternic!<text:line-break/>Mai greu dect sentina cu care un nemernic<text:line-break/>Strivete un srman!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">O diminea pe Caraiman</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">i iac-m pe vrfuri ararea strbtute,<text:line-break/>i unde achilonii locaul lor i pun.<text:line-break/>Dar nici o vegetare! A iernelor trecute<text:line-break/>Ninsorile, prin rpe, grmezi, grmezi s-adun.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Nici muchiul nu se ine pe cremenea lucioas<text:line-break/>Ce-o zvnt vijelia n drumul su trecnd.<text:line-break/>O! nici un semn de via! nimica nu triete,<text:line-break/>Dect p-un col un vultur lumina aintnd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">i corbi, afund n vale, de carnivore doruri<text:line-break/>mpuni, se-ntrec i plan,  vr&apos;un hoit i-au nsemnat,<text:line-break/>Sau paseri d-alte paseri mai tari ucise-n zboruri,<text:line-break/>Sau fiare ce-alte fiare mai tari au sfiat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Pe a crunt stnc -adesea porfirie,<text:line-break/>Se sparg, se primbl norii, troienii mictori,<text:line-break/>i raza dimineei, d-un soare ce-a s vie,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Aduce salutarea la vrfuri peste nori.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Departe, pe o creast de culme lung ntins,<text:line-break/>Se-nir, fr numr, molifi ieii din nor,<text:line-break/>i-n pomp militar, c-o frunte nenvins,<text:line-break/>mi trec pe dinainte cu uniforma lor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">n vile afunde, a nopii locuin,<text:line-break/>Coboar-n iruri brazii spre rul zgomotos<text:line-break/>Ce spumeg, se lupt, n repedea-i silin<text:line-break/>i cade, se sfram p-adnc prpstios.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Pe poalele de munte, colnice nverzite<text:line-break/>Pe care-mbrieaz praie erpuind,<text:line-break/>Albesc mulimi de turme ici-colo risipite,<text:line-break/>i buciume din stne s-aud pe vnt venind.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">i erghelii, cireade, pduri, livezi, corneturi<text:line-break/>Pe coaste, prin vlcele, cnd jos i cnd mai nalt,<text:line-break/>Ca frunze, umbrulie pe nite largi bucheturi,<text:line-break/>i drumuri, potecue,  cordele-n cmp de smalt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Cmpia e adnc, i sate semnate,<text:line-break/>Orae ici i colo pe ruri se ntind,<text:line-break/>i muncitori i holde pe brazdele arate<text:line-break/>Abia le prinde ochiul pe peisagi umbrind.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Departe, mult departe, Danubul lat albete,<text:line-break/>i dincolo de dnsul st Emul ncruntat;<text:line-break/>Cu el pare Carpatul din cnd n cnd vorbete;<text:line-break/>De Tisa parc-i spune, de Nistru deprtat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">ntins panoram ce-ncet, ncet se pierde,<text:line-break/>n care se nmoaie, se sting i se-nfresc<text:line-break/>Colorile d-a rndul, din cel mai nchis verde<text:line-break/>Pn-n rozoii aburi ce razele-auresc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">n urm-mi catedrale de talii uriae<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Ce din trmuri fierte potopul a zidit,<text:line-break/>Se-ntrec i i nal crunte i golae<text:line-break/>Mulimi de turnuri gotici n cerul azurit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Aeriane stavili ce taie Firmamentul,<text:line-break/>Pe care bat n frunte furtunele trecnd;<text:line-break/>Domenuri largi de iarn pe care Orientul<text:line-break/>mbrac n tunice de purpuri luminnd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Sub strate de zpad ce timpul nnoiete,<text:line-break/>O strat se ntinde de coli adnci shistoi,<text:line-break/>Coloanele ce timpul smerit le ocolete,<text:line-break/>Din care ies gigantici butingii monstruoi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Ca monstruri legioane ce se trsc, se-nvit<text:line-break/>n aer s rsufle de unde sunt strivii,<text:line-break/>i-n forme mari, schidoale, ce arta nu imit,<text:line-break/>Se-nir pe sub prpstii cnd negri, cnd plvii.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Palaturi milioane din vrstele titane,<text:line-break/>Prlite, ruinate, stau negre ncruntnd,<text:line-break/>Rmasuri tari, semee, antideluviane,<text:line-break/>Ce-i rd de timp, de secoli, vecia strbtnd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">P-aicea uriaii ai Daciei cei crude<text:line-break/>Sgeata otrvit zvrlea din mal n mal,<text:line-break/>P-aicea umbla umbra lui Zamolx ce s-aude,<text:line-break/>P-aici ncura calul viteazul Decebal.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Dar unde e poetul ce poate da o seam<text:line-break/>De toat majestatea cldirii n eter?<text:line-break/>Cine-ar putea s spuie aceast panoram?<text:line-break/>Prin vorbe cine poate s-arate-acest mister?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Eshil le-ar zice iaduri, adncuri sfrmate,<text:line-break/>n care el privete pe Jupiter trsnind,<text:line-break/>Gigani i Ecatonhiri, Titani care l bate,<text:line-break/>Zvrlind n ceruri muni, i p-Adis greu rnind.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4"><text:soft-page-break/>Pe Leaota noroas ce ochiul n-o ptrunde,<text:line-break/>Lungit, ca un alt munte, ar da pe Prometeu;<text:line-break/>Pe criv ne-ar aduce i gemete afunde,<text:line-break/>i zgomotul ce face vulturul din Orteu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">n largi domeni de brum ce soarele-aurete,<text:line-break/>Un Osian ne-ar spune c-eroi aci conjur;<text:line-break/>n tronuri de porfiruri, o fiic c iubete<text:line-break/>Un june erou mndru cu ochii de azur.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Dar ns acum nu e nici bardul Tesaliei,<text:line-break/>Ce vede zbrlind munii acel imens Titan,<text:line-break/>Ce-aude umblnd Scila pe vntul Siceliei;<text:line-break/>Nici al Scoiei bardul, btrnul Osian;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Profeii de ai Iudeii ce pot s compareze<text:line-break/>Troienii de calcair, graniii ascuii<text:line-break/>Cu capete aprinse mergnd s adoreze,<text:line-break/>Cu trmbe nzeite de preoi i levii.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Cci nu ai vrut, Stpne, la dreapta-i mprire<text:line-break/>S-atingi i a mea frunte cu snta mna ta;<text:line-break/>Tu nu ai vrut n pieptu-mi s sufli nzeire,<text:line-break/>Tu n-ai vrut s-i fiu preot, la lume-a te-arta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">ns-ai plantat n mine credina, contmplarea,<text:line-break/>Tcuta admirare a drepilor de sus;<text:line-break/>Ai pus n mine-Amorul, Sperana, Adorarea,<text:line-break/>-ai ncuiat Eternul n slabul tu supus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">O, ct de mult slbete cu spusul o credin!<text:line-break/>Ct e de trist i veted amorul cel trezit,<text:line-break/>i ct de mult i pierde obiectul de dorin<text:line-break/>Cnd omul ce-l adoar d-aproape l-a privit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">D-a fi putut a spune ntreaga mea simire,<text:line-break/>D-a arta vederii orice a contmpla,<text:line-break/>Cnd m cobor n sine-mi, n ore de mhnire,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Ca ce fel de senzaii a mai putea afla?<text:line-break/>...............................</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">*</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4"><text:line-break/>Se schimb decorarea. Cortine aburoase<text:line-break/>Se-ntind, se trag, -un munte ascund cu al lui cer;<text:line-break/>l las-apoi p-acela, se pierd i, neguroase,<text:line-break/>Se-ntorc i se-ndeseaz ca muni n vag eter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Se leagn, s-oprete, se las, se destinde;<text:line-break/>Vederea se nchide i totul e blocat:<text:line-break/>Nu vezi ceea ce pipi, i fulgerul s-aprinde,<text:line-break/>Alunec, i cerul apare despicat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">i zgomotul pe urm-i cutremur-n trie;<text:line-break/>Eco l prelungete departe revibrnd,<text:line-break/>L-amestic, confund... e noapte de magie?<text:line-break/>E vreun cor de demoni sabatul lor serbnd?...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">E caos universul i ceaa umezete;<text:line-break/>Mici prticele umezi dau rsuflarea greu;<text:line-break/>Dar negura cu-ncetul se trage, se rrete,<text:line-break/>i raza, ntr-o clip, arceaz curcubeu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Pe vrfuri e lumin i razele curate;<text:line-break/>Dar norii greu se scutur pe vile adnci;<text:line-break/>Mai trec vr&apos;o cinci minute, i ruri turburate,<text:line-break/>iroaie rupnd fagii, i-azvrl peste stnci!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">i ct e de mic Omul cnd s-afl pe un munte!<text:line-break/>Ce slab-i e fiina n urlet d-element!<text:line-break/>Se vede cum se pierde la norul ce-a s-ncrunte;<text:line-break/>D-o linie greeal, i piere-ntr-un moment...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Din ast nimicie n care el se crede,<text:line-break/>Pierdut n elemente, un punct microscopic,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Suflare de insect ce nici chiar el se vede,<text:line-break/>O particul-a brumei pe val oceanic,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Se simte totd&apos;odat c nu mai e nemernic;<text:line-break/>E mare ct i lumea, nu-ncape-n firmament;<text:line-break/>D mna cu principul al Totului puternic;<text:line-break/>E univers gndirea-i; amoru-i, element.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">n el e i registrul epocelor trecute,<text:line-break/>n el e i putina natur-a scormoli;<text:line-break/>L-ascult elemente, se-njug, sunt prefcute<text:line-break/>La semnul mnii sale, la ce va chibzui.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">El are facultatea Tria a strbate,<text:line-break/>A msura eterul, a-l strnge, compacta,<text:line-break/>A descompune corpuri, i globuri deprtate<text:line-break/>S-ainte, -a lor lege s-aplice la a sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Fiin mult schidoal! insect gnditoare!<text:line-break/>Piticule gigantic! furnic creator!<text:line-break/>O raz-i numai poate cu-ntregul s msoare<text:line-break/>i tu ntreg,  nimica!... un vierme trtor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">De ce oare Puterea acea nemrginit,<text:line-break/>Puterea creatoare, a Totului princip,<text:line-break/>Zdrobit-n mici scnteie p-atomuri risipit,<text:line-break/>Se-nchin i ea soartei slvit-n acest chip?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">i cum ea poate toate pn a nu se-mparte,<text:line-break/>-o dat mprit, puterile-i se stric?<text:line-break/>De ce e nimicit, d-al su ntreg departe,<text:line-break/>-atunci i ia puterea cnd intr n nimic?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Fatalitate!  Basta!  Blestem i e dorina!<text:line-break/>Ateapt, trufa vierme, cnd viermii te-or mnca;<text:line-break/>Ateapt-i nefiina, de vrei s-i tii fiina!<text:line-break/>Sau intr n nimica de vei s fii ceva!<text:span text:style-name="T15"> </text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4"><text:soft-page-break/>Pegasu-i nu e-n stare acolo a strbate,<text:line-break/>Ia-i cal apocaliptic, -atunci vei izbuti:<text:line-break/>El singur tie drumul ce nu se mai abate;<text:line-break/>-atunci vei afla taina,  nimic cnd nu vei ti.<text:line-break/>......................................<text:line-break/>......................................<text:line-break/>Eu las pe ast calcair cu form omeneasc,<text:line-break/>P-ast uria ce-nfrunt rstimpii pmnteti,<text:line-break/>Martur eternitii n bolta cea cereasc,<text:line-break/>O liter strin tiinei omeneti!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4">Acel ce va strbate pe ast nlime<text:line-break/>Unde un geniu vine, vedenie de vis,<text:line-break/>i smulge muritorul pe aripi de lucime,<text:line-break/>Ptrunz el arcanul,  citeasc ce n-am scris.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Zburtorul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce slbeti, copil?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce-ai nglbenit?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce de joc i-e sil</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-att te-ai ofilit?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te tiu de vorbitoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La danuri tu-ncepeai,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i noaptea-n eztoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe toate le-ntreceai.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce d-a ta cosi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acum tu nu-ngrijeti?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spune-mi, spune-mi feti,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce ai de ptimeti?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce, tat-tu te bate?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">l tiu a te iubi.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Au va n alte sate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A te cstori?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-s buzele-i prlite</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i pieptul tu rotat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De pete-nvineite?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sti: cine te-a mucat?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce plngi, copili?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Doreti vr&apos;un cltor?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, ce pcat! Feti,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu crez c-ai zburtor!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aa e, vecinic;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aa gndesc i eu.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un june... Oh! mi-e fric!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">l vz n somnul meu.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">M-apuc, m trudete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i eu cu el m joc;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M strnge, m ciupete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M muc plin de foc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe pieptul meu s-apas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i eu de gt l-apuc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar ziua cnd s ias,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El piere ca nluc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cugetare</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nous naissons, nous vivons, bergre,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nous mourons sans savoir comment;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Chacun est parti du nant:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ou va-t-il?... Dieu le sait, ma chre.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">Voltaire</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prieteni! privii zidul acela chinezesc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i templii, elefanii, colosuri egiptene,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pagode suterane, pagode indiene,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce se mai lupt cu timpul ca neamul omenesc,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i spunei, unde-i omul ce-odat le-a zidit?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Privii Memfis, Efesul, privii Babilonia,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cetile gigantici din Indii i Asia,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cui vrei a le ti vrsta din stilul ce-a pierit!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Privii! Sidonul, Tirul ce pe profei au dat;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Gndii l-a lor putere, pe lumea cunoscut; </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ctai-le-i ruina! A! este prefcut</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">&apos;N acele elemente din care s-a creat!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Oari unde e mulimea ce-atuncea le mrea?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i unde l-e comerul? Unde le e otirea?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unde le este legea? Ce s-a fcut mrirea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">tiina, avuia ce-atunci le nflorea?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mirai-v-i acuma de crmida lor!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">mplei-v-i muzeul de spturi, inscripii!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ctai chei d-alfabeturi! Croii-v-i descripii!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rdei d-a lor credin, de epopeea lor!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Trei mii de ani vor trece si ali pitici turbai</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vor popula deerturi acuma neumblate.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca mine Paris, Londra pe pietrele surpate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">&apos;i vor spune epopeea la altfel de-nvai.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">...................................................</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">...................................................</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">...................................................</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">...................................................</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca mine-n aste templuri, palaturi i ceti,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Loca al veseliei, al pompei, al trufiei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sracul unde-aint p-l beat de bucurie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i unde desfrnarea se-mbat-n nedrepti,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Castori or s s-adune; maimuele, jucnd,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Or s se strmbe-n cioburi din lustrurile sparte;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i bufnia, ciovlica, ipnd p-un col departe,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vor trage prin palaturi haitic de lupi urlnd...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">i ce-ar fi poezia? </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph">Te privesc, i urc<text:line-break/>De dragoste aprins,<text:line-break/>Pn la buzele mele inima.<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="9"/>P. Sutzos</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I1"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i ce-ar fi poezia<text:line-break/>Cnd n-ar fi frumuseea?<text:line-break/>Ce-ar fi -un muritor<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cnd n-ar simi amor;<text:line-break/>Ce-ar fi i veselia<text:line-break/>Cnd n-ar fi tinereea;<text:line-break/>Ce-ar fi nite comori<text:line-break/>La cei din nchisori;<text:line-break/>Ce-ar fi mreul soare<text:line-break/>La cel ce vederi n-are<text:line-break/>Sau geme-n chinuiri;<text:line-break/>Ce-ar fi o motenire,<text:line-break/>Ce-ar fi o fericire,<text:line-break/>Ce-ar fi a ta iubire<text:line-break/>La cel fr simiri.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II1"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Albastra ta privire<text:line-break/>E-att d-atingtoare,<text:line-break/>Ca i un cer senin<text:line-break/>Ce scoate un suspin<text:line-break/>Din cel ce-n absorbire,<text:line-break/>i uit ce l doare.<text:line-break/>Spre cei ce-i arunca<text:line-break/>Dulcea ctare-a ta, <text:line-break/>Abstracie-n simire, <text:line-break/>i pierd a lor gndire;<text:line-break/>In tine toi triesc.<text:line-break/>Rcoarea cea de sine<text:line-break/>Ce-n preajm-i simi c vine,<text:line-break/>Ast vnt ce tragi n tine,<text:line-break/>E suflet omenesc.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Sperana n ziua de mine </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mine i iar mine; i de mine, mine;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Astzi e durerea, mine fericirea:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Astfel crede-acela care n-are pine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Astfel i bogatul: Toat omenirea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Crede i ateapt mine-ntr-ajutor!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar ast mine oar cnd se ispravete?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, ce rtcire! Mine, e vecia.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Astzi, este viaa, ct omul traiete:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Astzi, e-ntristarea; Mine, veselia:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Viaa, este vrajb; Moartea, e amor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Ai vrea, precum se vede, s-i mai aduci aminte</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ai vrea, precum se vede, s-i mai aduci aminte<text:line-break/>D-acea miniatur a sexului frumos,<text:line-break/>D-a ei vioiciune, spirituasele-i cuvinte,<text:line-break/>D-ocheada cea focoas din ochiu-i amoros;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De ochii ei cei negri ce-ar sparge o-ntristare<text:line-break/>A lumii toat n doliu, d-acel surs ceresc<text:line-break/>Ce veselete lumea ca ziua de srbare,<text:line-break/>De gestele-i vioaie i timbrul ngeresc;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De buclel-ebenine, lucioase i flotnde<text:line-break/>Pe snul d-alabastru, ca aripe de corbi<text:line-break/>Ce flfie pe bruma ninsorilor cznde<text:line-break/>Cu toat rsuflarea-i ce tu n drag absorbi? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P7">Pleca cnd am vzut-o, i tremuram de fric;<text:line-break/>Cci inima-mi sta gata cu dnsa a zbura.<text:line-break/>Purta pe piept o cruce, o cruce mititica,<text:line-break/>Pe care i evreii prea c-ar sruta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">1840, mai 26</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Alaiul unui ceretor </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph"><text:s/>The proper study of mankind is man.<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="19"/>Pope</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Popor, facei loc! trece-un cltor!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un sfenic nainte -un preot dup dnsul;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De sraci se duce un trist cociug de lemn.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nfurat n trene, un corp este ntr-nsul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lacrime sau doliu tristarea nu nsemn. </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cei mari, v plecai! trece-un ceretor!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bogailor, loc! trece-un cltor!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acel ceretor care chiar ieri nu avea pine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Clopotul rsun, c a ajuns la port:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">I-a ncetat durerea i grija pentru mine;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Regii-s d&apos;opotriv cu ceretorul mort.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stai, ari i cezari! trece-un ceretor!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Loc! loc, suverani! trece-un cltor!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">rna-i se depune n urna veciniciei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unde concheranii p-a lor o au depus,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i viermii putrejunei dau pnteci lcomiei </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sufletele toate se vd acolo sus.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ndrt, bogai! trece-un ceretor!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stpnilor, loc! trece-un cltor!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">V tragei, plecai capul, gtii-v-a rspunde:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Creatoru-ascult pe ceretorul mort.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din cte-a tras aicea nimica nu ascunde; </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Greu or s rspund acei ce griji nu port!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tiranilor, loc! trece-un ceretor!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Un suvenir </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu, nu se uit lesne, cnd, din copilarie.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cineva iubete precum te-am iubit eu;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i blestem pe aceia care, prin viclenie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-au amrt viaa i tot amorul meu.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mnia mea din urm, mndria-mi cea silit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd ai ti acuma cu ce pre le pltesc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ct, sub faa-mi rece, mi-e inima zdrobit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu te-ai mira poate ca poci s mai triesc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A geme la picioare-i, mi-a arta cirea!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar, ca s fiu vrednic n veci d-amorul tu!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nec durerea-n mine, mcar c-mi vz pieirea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n rana ascuns ce-o roade-un vierme ru.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i arburile,-ntocmai, ce focul mistuiete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i i suge sucul cu-ncetul i p-ascuns, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd rdcina-i ars, cnd frunza-i glbinete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd cenua-i zboar, cnd focul l-a ptruns, </text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai st tot mndru nc i capul nu i pleac:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">St cu brae-ntinse zefirii nfruntnd;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Privete ns vntul ce-acuma o s treac,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-o s-auzi un trosnet i focu-i vifornd.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Deertul mi-e o lume</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Deertul mi-e o lume, cu chipul tu de fa,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i lumea mi-e deert cnd vei s nu triesc.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n tine mi-am sperana, n tine am via,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i fr tine toate sunt negre, le ursc;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar mi-eti etern de fa, -etern sunt fericit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De sunt n adunare i salt veselia,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd danul se rpede pe pasuri de zefir,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd nimfe trec, alearg, alearg bucuria,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De eti ori nu cu mine, te-aduce-al meu delir</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i eti etern n minte-mi, -etern sunt fericit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">-atuncea, ca un geniu, ca vie zeitate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu pru-i cel de aur n unde resfirat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ntr-o mulime rece, faci pieptul meu a bate;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin ceruri zbor atuncea, i raiul am aflat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i mi-eti etern de fa, -etern sunt fericit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cele trebuincioase </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un Talent va i tiin;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Concheranul, contiin;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Diputatul, semeie;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ministrul, ipocrizie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i un prin mrinimie.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Judele, va iscusin;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Preotul, va umilin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ostaul, va credin.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O feti, modestie;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tnra, cochetrie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-amorezul, va mndrie.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Galantului, trebuie stare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Brbatului inim mare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nevestii, viclenie.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Amorului, mpiedicare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Moralului, puina sare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Temtorilor, plimbare; </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar cornailor, rbdare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-orencii,- nobilare.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Astea toate, n credin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sunt de mare trebuin.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Sonet</text:h>
