   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din zi n zi mai trist, srman Romnie;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De dou veacuri jalea i crete ne-ncetat!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Traian se mir, plnge, privete-a ta cmpie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-o tie cmp, odat de Acvil-aprat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O! Trist-i suvenirea la cei n agonie!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Amar e cnd te doare, s vezi ca-eti mpilat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-neci a tale lacrmi; s vii, cu bucurie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A sruta i mna ce tii c te-a trdat!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe cine atepi oare s-aline-a ta durere?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe-acela ce te suge? te calc n picere?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe cei carii te-ar vinde de mii de ori p-un tron?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te amgeti!... Dar, afl i crede n tcere:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Oricare slbiciune n chinuri ia putere...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n fiare crete iute vrtutea lui Samson!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Zdrobit geme inima-n mine </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zdrobit geme inima-n mine;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n flcri, chinuri arz ne-ncetat;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Viaa-mi toat o am n tine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar tu de mine te-ai deprtat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eti tu o fee? Eti zeitate?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sau, ca iubirea, vii a-nclzi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un suflet rece ce nu mai bate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n noaptea urii din zi cu zi?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De eti aproape, pieptu-mi palpit;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De eti de fa, eu m uimesc;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La glasu-i mintea mi e rpit;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar mi-eti strin, i m-ngrozesc...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Detept, n somnu-mi chipu-i e-n mine;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M uit la lume, i, ca strin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Reviu n sine-mi, triesc n tine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Le las pe toate, de tine plin.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fiina-mi toat ie-i urmeaz,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci eu sunt umbr corpului tu;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A ta, ca spirit, m nviaz,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci tu eti suflet corpului meu.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Muncitorul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd m nscui n lume, murise al meu tat;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci mult el se luptase cu iasma ncruntat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-i zice Srcia!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El locuia cu dnsa din frageda-i junie;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i s-a luptat, srmanul, cu mult brbie;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar, vai! l-a-nvins pustia!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btrn de june nc, iertatul meu printe</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ct la cer i zise:  Oh! Fie-i mil, sfinte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">De bietul muncitor!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atunci veni la dnsul trimisul ce desface</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-i zise: Ia-i iertarea: eti liber; du-te-n pace</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">La bunu-i Creator!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i biata maic-atuncea, n lacrimi i sudoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu mine-nsrcinat, privea la el cum moare.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Apoi groapa-i sp...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fr nimic de hran rmase-n vduvie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nu putea s lupte cu iasma Srcie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce i mai ru turb...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Puin dup aceasta, n ziua sorocit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin munci m-aduse-n lume, flmnd, prsit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sraca miculi!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Plngea pe dou paie pe care m nscuse;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci n-avea fae, mica; acum nti fcuse;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-avea nici crpuli!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Apoi vrsa ea lacrimi cu mult i mai amare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vznd c-i seac pieptul, c n-are demncare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vznd c n-ajungea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cldura rsuflrii -a snului de mum</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S ie, s-nclzeasc un ubred prunc de spum,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un prunc ce tot plngea.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Amorul mamei ns hrnete i-nclzete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i biata miculi, cu doru-i, izbutete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din via-i s-mi dea via.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lucrnd, i zi, i noapte, i vara pe greu soare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i fr foc pe iarn cnd firea toat moare,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd toat firea-nghea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea n-avea alt grij dect s m fereasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De tot ce doare-n via, s poat s m creasc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">S poat a-mi zmbi.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Creteam i-mi mergea binesub dulcea-i ngrijire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rdea cnd ziceam: mam! la-ntia mea vorbire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vzndu-m-a pi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum a putut, sraca, m-a dat apoi la carte.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O! ct bucurie avea cnd, de departe,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vedea c viu acas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu cmsua alb, cu cciulia neagr,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu carte-n subioar!... avea ea lumea-ntreag</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd m vedea la mas.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Apoi mai trecu timpul i m fcui mai mare.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O! ct bucurie i ct lucram de tare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca s produc ceva!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Gndeam adesea-n sine-mi: Eu sunt voinic acuma</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i, o, ce fericire! oi s-mi hrnesc eu muma!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea nu va mai lucra!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar viaa-i se scursese n vreme prea puin...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acel care privete din cer p-l de suspin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Chem pe a mea maic.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zmbind, p-a mele brae s-opri a ei suflare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i, dndu-mi, prin ctare-i, o binecuvntare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se duse l-al meu taic.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd am bgat-o-n groapa de braul meu spat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-am dat pe ea pmntul... oh, Maic Preacurat!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu tii ct am jelit!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acum, n lume singur, triam fr simire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nutrindu-m cu lacrimi, cu trista suvenire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">A maicei ce-am iubit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin negura vieii zrii eu o lumin:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n drumu-mi singuratic, o fiic orfelin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Trimise Providena.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O! Roua primverii, ninsoarea afnat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu poate fi ca dnsa, ca dnsa de curat!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-am pus n ea credina.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dup-o intire, ochii n jos ni se lsar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i sufletele noastre de loc se-mbriar;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">D-atuncea ne-am unit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu, cerul niciodat, n snta-i veselie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu are strmutare, mai mare bucurie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ceea ce-am simit!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu i ziceam adesea, sorbind a ei suflare:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vezi lumea asta, drag? orict e ea de mare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">De noi este strin;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe nimeni nu l doare, i nimnui, nu-i pas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ne-o fi ru sau bine... Vin&apos;, vin&apos;, s facem cas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Srman i orfelin.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stingher turturic prin crnguri rtcit!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i voi cldi eu cuibul n care-i fi ferit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">De frig i vijelii.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voi alerga eu, drag, ca s-i aduc de hran,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i voi aduce toate: i voi aduce man </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vom fi n veselii.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-mi rspundea copila:  i eu, cu srguin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n lipsa ta, voi face ce-o sta-n a mea putin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce trebuin cere.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cnd te vei ntoarce, i-oi da mbriare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voi fi cu ngrijire, i-oi face demncare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voi fi l-a ta plcere.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Munceam eu ct i patru, i fr-a face gur:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cnd veneam din munc, gseam n bttur</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe ngeraul meu!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Oh! ce plcere, Doamne! cnd ntr-o zi mi-arat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C am plecat pe drumul de a m face tat!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mrite Dumnezeu!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu m topeam cu ziua de mult nerbdare.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Gndeam ca ce dulceuri s-i dau eu demncare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce poate s pofteasc.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar ea, mai neleapt, venea pe lng mine</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i mi zicea s strngem pentru acel ce vine </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spunea cum a s-l creasc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Era aproape ora ce-atta ateptam,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd o schimbare-n ar, ce noi nu o visasem,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">ncepe-a se vesti:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-adaog iobaciul! s-adaog la clac,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-adaog ct Omul nu poate s mai fac,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu poate dini:</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T7"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Noi n-avem dect braul; dar braul este-al nostru!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Noi nu putem s-l spargem n veci n lucrul vostru,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">S mai scdei ceva!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Strigar muncitorii din satele vecine</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar iat c otire a stpnirii vine</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-ncepe a lega!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O! cum ai s mai tremuri, dreptate omeneasc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd va veni odat Dreptatea cea cereasc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Puternica Dreptate! </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Este un vis d-acilea pe care nu-l iu minte;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">tiu c m-au dus la ocn i nu mi-au dat cuvinte...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce crud rudate.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ce nverunare!  Peste puine zile</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zri draga-mi soie ce se-nla prin grile.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">ip cnd m vzu!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea mai veni odat, veni i alt dat;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Da-i tremura genunchii, era nsrcinat...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sraca! o btu...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">D-atunci n-am mai vzut-o!... Printe, dulce taic!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spie mult iubit! O, scump a mea maic!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fiu nc fr nume!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce! voi, voi suntei colo, sus colo-n a lumin?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voi suntei cea grmad cu fa-att de lin?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voi suntei p-aia lume?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu m lsai, o, drage! nu, nu fugii de mine!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se sparg a&apos; mele lanuri; v-ajung... ajung la bine.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">L-al nostru Creator!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O clip, i nu-mi pas de loc de a lor sil!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Oh!... iat-o vine!! vine!!  O, Doamne! fie-i mil</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">De bietul muncitor!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Sila</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Era o iarn aspr -o noapte ce-ngrozete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i crivul, cu viscol, mugea precum mugete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un taur ce-a rnit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ntr-un ctun de laturi a unui sat mai mare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O raz ngnat de slab luminare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Subt un troian albit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Troianul era cas, ccioar locuit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-i astupa nemeii intrarea umilit </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bordei de muncitor;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i raza ngnat venea dintr-o lumin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">D-o flacr-n cenu ce vlvia n tin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe un uscat cotor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu furcile n brne, cu feele voioase,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ntind ct pot cu fusul din caiere stufoase</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dou femei cntnd.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btrn este una, ca iarna de albit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar alta este jun, blaie i iubit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ci o vd rznd.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">P-un pat de paie numai un biet btrn bolete.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Femeile, cu rndul, cnd el se dezvelete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se duc de-l nvelesc.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i rd cnd vd c fierbe n oal o gin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-au cptat pe lucru de la a lor vecin:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci tortu-i omenesc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Oft btrna ns i zise ctre fiic:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd am luat pe tat&apos;tu, pe cnd erai tu mic,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eram mai fericii;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aveam csua noastr, aveam coprinsuri bune,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aveam frumoase holde i turme la pune,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aveam argai pltii,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i vite-n bttur, i plugul lng cas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-un cltor, oricare, afla ceva pe mas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd s-abtea la noi.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Era frunta btrnul, ca el puinu cu stare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Abia-nvrtea prin curte cu carul su cel mare </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un car cu ase boi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe orice puneam mna ieea n toate bine.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu semnai cu tat&apos;tu i frate-tu cu mine...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aicea a-ncetat...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-un ochi de disperare inti pe o icoan</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A sntei nsctoare, zicnd:  n orice goan</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">A soartei te-am chemat!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T7"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tata spunea odat c-aveam i noi moie;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce-ai vndut-o, mam? C-e ru n obcie;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Munceti pentru strin.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-o lacrim din pleoapa-i luci precum lucete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe geana aurorei o rou ce pistete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dintr-un azur senin.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T7"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Noi n-am vndut-o, mam; vecini ne-au luat-o.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cum! aa cu sila?  Ba tot ne-au tot scurtat-o</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu cri de judeci,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn-au luat-o toat...  Ce viscol e afar;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unde-o fi nenea, mam?  Aleii l luar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">-acum ca -alte di.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe mas, lng tat&apos;su fetia-n nerbdare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ntinse o maram i-i puse demncare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fiertura de la foc.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">O! s-mi trieti, fetio, c foamea m doboar!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-i am i vin, ticu; i-i am i pinioar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Uite-o colea, o coc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T7"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">S am de tine parte, feti cu durere!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Att mi mai rmase din toat-a mea avere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">La btrneea mea;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci frate-tu, se vede c mi-l tot mn satul:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sracii duc povara, iar rodul ia bogatul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">n lumea asta rea!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ora asta dulce cnd vesel-i copila</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-a bucurat pe tat&apos;su, fiica Satanii,</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">Sila</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">La ua ei grina.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Doi dorobani ce calea prea c rtcir,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zrind lumina noaptea, s stea aci venir,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">C doar va senina.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">mping i intr-n cas cu iarna n spinare:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aci avem de toate, i cald, i de mncare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n cup vinior.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai facei foc pe vatr i dai-ne i patul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai d-te jos, btrne, sau culc-te de-a latul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">C dau de v omor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Oft adnc btrnul, cci</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">Sila</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">e cumplit!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ls btrna furca! era obicinuit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu astfel de nevoi.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar biata copili, n marea ei durere,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rosti plngnd:  Jupne, n-avem nici o putere;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-avem nici car, nici boi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i suspinnd din suflet, tergnd cu zevelcua</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">iroaiele de lacrimi, se dete srcua</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe ubredul btrn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i i opti acestea: i fac eu demncare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Numaidect, ticu. Jupne, aibi rbdare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">C doar n-ai fi pgn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mncarea-i pentru tata, cci vezi-l cum bolete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E an acu-n presemi de cnd se chinuiete;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">S nu-l dai jos din pat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i mama e btrn i n-avem nici gteaj,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe nenea de trei zile de cnd l-au dat la streaj...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aleii l-au luat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar dorobanii epeni tot sparg i tot njur,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i zvnt i a pine, i vinul i fiertur,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-s oameni stpneti.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El nu mai st la vorb cnd are biciu-n mn;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd leapd opinca i calul i nfrn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu el s nu glumeti!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se-mbrobodea copila -o neca suspine.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Era s-noate-n viscol, s mearg la vecine</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">S cear-un ouor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O mn de fin, s fac-o pinioar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">St dinafara uii s vad-o prtioar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">S vad vrun focor,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd un argat din curte, din curtea boiereasc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O prind i-o-ntinde s-o duc s munceasc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci tie a lucra:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i e la curte clac, i s-a fcut de veste,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La ci au fost p-acas, la fete i neveste,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">S mearg-a ajuta.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci este nunt mare, e nunt boiereasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Duminica ce vine, i trebui s gteasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Miresei aternut.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i rugile i lacrimi zadarnice i fur;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Argatul nu glumete, o bate -o njur,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sau cere de but.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar nu avea fetia dect o zeghie veche</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i vreo trei parale cercel la o ureche,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Care voi a-i da.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nu vru s priimeasc cumplitul fr mil.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btnd-o, suduind-o, o tot brncea n sil</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">La ln-a scrmna.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Trei zile biata fat nimica nu aflase</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De tat-su cel bolnav pe care l lsase</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Flmnd i chinuit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cnd scp, micua, veni n nerbdare...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nmeii cotropise i cas i intrare.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Abia a-nemerit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Luptndu-se cu iarna, s intre izbutise,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar tat-su, ca gheaa, de mult nepenise,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i mum-sa murea;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe frate-su l dase aleii la otire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i singur, orfana, plngea n zpcire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i prul i smulgea.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sufla n pieptul m-sei ca doar s-o nclzeasc;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cuta cojocul... dar unde s-l gseasc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci e la arenda</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dodat cu cldarea luat zlog n sil</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">P-o oarb datorie.  O, Doamne! fie-i mil</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">De rob i de clca!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">1840, ianuarie 4</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Clcaul</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I2"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Oh! legai pentru vecie<text:line-break/>De pmntul und<text:span text:style-name="T14">e</text:span> stm,<text:line-break/>Pltim vecinic chirie<text:line-break/>i pe apa care bem.<text:line-break/>Nu avem nimic al nostru;<text:line-break/>Tot n preajm e strin!<text:line-break/>Venim rupi din lucrul vostru<text:line-break/>i dm peste-al lipsei chin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ca un dobitoc de munc,<text:line-break/>Ca copaciul roditor,<text:line-break/>Ca rodirea dintr-o lunc<text:line-break/>Voi strivii pe muncitor.<text:line-break/>El i fiii, i soie,<text:line-break/>Boul, vaca i viei,<text:line-break/>Toi sunt zestre pe moie:<text:line-break/>Robi ai muncii, robi ai ei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Suntei veseli cnd ne vindei<text:line-break/>n arend la cochini!<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Camt pe munc prindei<text:line-break/>Pruncilor de la prini!<text:line-break/>Btrn, vduv, copilul<text:line-break/>Munca-le v sunt datori;<text:line-break/>i sudoarea lor, suspinul<text:line-break/>V-aprind setea de comori.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dup ce, prin asuprire,<text:line-break/>Stoarcei, ca proprietari,<text:line-break/>Venii iar, ca stpnire,<text:line-break/>Nscocii la biruri mari,<text:line-break/>-apoi v-aezai pe jee<text:line-break/>Jefuind ca dregtori! <text:line-break/>Zgripori cu-ntreite fee,<text:line-break/>Jupuii pe muncitori.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II2"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Noi le suntem toat-averea.<text:line-break/>Munca ne-o msor cum vor;<text:line-break/>Fiii notri l-e puterea,<text:line-break/>-aste mini, comoara lor.<text:line-break/>Ei triesc n nelucrare;<text:line-break/>Munca-ne de zece ani<text:line-break/>Pun p-o hain de purtare,<text:line-break/>P-un osp, cu arlatani.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">L-a lor jicnie, grnare,<text:line-break/>Ca p-albine ne adun;<text:line-break/>Cnd sunt pline de mncare,<text:line-break/>De tot ce-are ara bun,<text:line-break/>Gonesc musca, nfund nfund uleiul.<text:line-break/>Ne pun fum ca s fugim;<text:line-break/>Ei iau mierea, noi bordeiul<text:line-break/>Gol ca palma lor gsim.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="III1"/><text:soft-page-break/>III</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">D-astzi, munca-ne e-a noastr<text:line-break/>-o schimbm pentru pmnt.<text:line-break/>Mncai voi rna voastr!<text:line-break/>Munca noi n-o dm n vnt.<text:line-break/>i, de vrei s-avei cuvntul,<text:line-break/>De vrei a v domiri:<text:line-break/>Este-al braului pmntul,<text:line-break/>A-l lucra, nu a-i robi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pinea, fierul o rodete;<text:line-break/>Tot cu fierul ne-o pstrm;<text:line-break/>Ea e-a celui ce-o muncete;<text:line-break/>Trntorilor n-o mai dm.<text:line-break/>V-am cerut, de mil, dreptul<text:line-break/>Cu tocmeal ntre frai.<text:line-break/>Nu vrei? Ni-l inem cu pieptul,<text:line-break/>i venii de ni-l luai!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Paris, 1851, ianuarie</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Acvila strbun </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Buciumul lui Zamolx sun,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Scoal Acvil strbun,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Scoate capu, te trezete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Du-te de te-ntinerete:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Du-te-n Pareng de te scald,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C d Mithra vremea cald.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">F-i apoi o avntare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i te-oprete-n Turnu-Mare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-mi aint, fr fric,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Soarele ce se ardic!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tinde lung a ta umbrire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cheam-i fiii la unire;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">D din aripi i rcnete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i adun, le griete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C Traian plin de ardoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">St pe Omul n picioare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Le trimete voie bun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i porunca-i aa sun:</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce e ast mprire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i a numelui smintire!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C vlscenii, moldovenii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Transilvenii, bnenii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu-s n tablele d-aram,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici c-i tie vechea Faim.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pot s fac din Dacia,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe dreptate, Romnia;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar romnii au un nume</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe ct vor tri n lume.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Deci s-ncete poroclirea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dezertarea, dezunirea.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">D-te-n Istru-apoi, cu fal,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ia p-aripi ap lustral</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i te-ntoarce de-i stropete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i pe toi i nfrete:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n strvechea Romnie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dect frai s nu mai fie!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Paris, 25 martie 1856</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Ah! las s-mi curg-ast aer </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah! lass-mi curg-ast aer ce d a ta suflare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca apa cea sfinit el poate curi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din sufletu-mi i minte, cumplita apsare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i relele dasupr-mi el poate mpri!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah! las-m ca umbra s umblu dup tine!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i coarda-mi fiorat o las a cnta</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe psurile tale!  Tu f-i un joc din mine;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar las-a mele imnuri la tine a-ndrepta!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu calc-m-n picioare-i, strivete-m ca ceara</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce curge, i ia forma oricare i.vei da;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar las-m s sufer! i visurile-mi seara</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spre tine i n tine le las-a s-ainta.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O! daca p-ast frunte, profana ta coroan</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-ar nnegri n ochii-mi aceste caliti</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin care zeitatea ntreaga ei icoan</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A transformat n tine ca mie s-o ari,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atunci, fr ruine, a face s rsune</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pmntul l-al tu nume i chiar acel tartar;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i lira-mi la picioare-i, la locul tu te-ar pune,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i pieptu-mi i-ar fi templu, i inima-mi altar!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu gem! i n deliru-mi, te chem, Eleonor! </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca Tass de fiare-n temnii eu voi s m ncarc! </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n veci tu pentru mine s fii o alt Lor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n veci eu pentru tine s fiu un alt Petrarc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca el, fr speran, s plng pe a ta urm,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n tine eu fanatic s nu mai am alt zeu!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voina-i fie-mi lege; i viaa-mi o precurm</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd vei i cnd i place, cci tu-mi eti Dumnezeu.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Apostrofa</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Paris, 1856</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P15"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voi, ce strecurai narul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cmila nghiii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-n ochi nu v vedei parul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-un pai pe alii zrii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lingi de pe la domnie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ambiioi picmei!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Hrnii tot din calomnie!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tartufilor!  farisei! </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voi, ce-mi veninai exilul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voi, mai cruzi i mai barbari</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dect cei ce-mi iau cminul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ara, muma, frai, surori;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voi, cu care-n curie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M-am sculat spre a lupta</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pentru ast Romnie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce ciocoii o trda!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spunei,  de avei credin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ct grunte de mutar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ce-ai jurat,  e fiin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Care-n ast exil amar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu mai mult brbie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca mine a suferit?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nfruntat-am cu mndrie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Relele ce m-au izbit?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-ai surprins vro nevoin?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Umilitu-m-am la ri?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ovit-am n credin?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Alergat-am la cli,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La clii rii mele...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La ciocoi?  In ore grele</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd necazurile curg</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu boale; cu srcie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu soia suferind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu ura, cu calomnia</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n umbr-mi n veci grinnd,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spunei!  care se alege? </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prsit-am ast stindard?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-am clcat eu a mea lege</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca apostol, sau ca bard?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar principuri voi nu cerei;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voi ctai un partizan</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La ambiia ce mergei:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Calea tras de Satan.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Butada</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P15"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici ceara ta cea neagr, nici muctoru-i dinte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici lacrimi mincinoase, nici toate-aste cuvinte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu m-au nduplecat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-am spus c pentru tine eu mort sunt n vecie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cerului dau glorii, ca robul din robie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De tine c-am scpat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Ciocoii din revoluie </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Num-opinca, srcua,<text:line-break/>Numai ea nu ne-a-nelat,<text:line-break/>Numai dnsa, ea micua,<text:line-break/>Numai ea nu ne-a trdat;<text:line-break/>Dar ciocoii gulerai<text:line-break/>Sunt la inim spurcai.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ei intrau s fure sume<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i la rui s-i fac rost.<text:line-break/>Ca s-i spui pe toi pe nume,<text:line-break/>Voi nu-i tii ci au mai fost?<text:line-break/>Nu tii c au fost spurcai<text:line-break/>Toi ciocoii gulerai?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">C eu bine-am spus, sracu;<text:line-break/>Eu v-am spus numaidect<text:line-break/>C n-ai s te-mpaci cu dracu,<text:line-break/>De i-ai face oriict:<text:line-break/>Toi ciocoii gulerai<text:line-break/>Sunt la inim spurcai.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ba c-om face, ba c-om drege,<text:line-break/>Ba s-avem i pe boier;<text:line-break/>C-o fi bun de-l vom alege<text:line-break/>Pin guvern, pin minister.<text:line-break/>Dar ciocoii gulerai<text:line-break/>Au fost, cum am zis, spurcai.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">C-ncepur-a face fracii<text:line-break/>-a lega pe opincari:<text:line-break/>ntr-o lun,-n trei reacii,<text:line-break/>Ne-au scpat i mcelari.<text:line-break/>C ciocoii gulerai<text:line-break/>Sunt la inim spurcai.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i noi, tot cu evanghelii<text:line-break/>Din balconuri predicam;<text:line-break/>Tot spuneam parascovenii<text:line-break/>i-i iertam, ne mpcm;<text:line-break/>Dar ciocoii gulerai,<text:line-break/>Ei rnjeau c-s ru spurcai.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd venir-apoi muscalii, <text:line-break/>Agi, sptari i controlor!<text:line-break/>Alii  mrleo! fug cu banii.<text:line-break/>Turcii prad i omor.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i ciocoii gulerai<text:line-break/>Rd de noi c stm legai.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Toat-opinca-n pucrie;<text:line-break/>Toi legai, sraci lipii,<text:line-break/>Zac n ploaie pe ghimie,<text:line-break/>Pribegesc proscrii, gonii,<text:line-break/>Iar ciocoii gulerai<text:line-break/>Rd de noi c-i credem frai.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Num-opinca, srcua,<text:line-break/>Numai ea nu a furat;<text:line-break/>Numai dnsa, ea micua,<text:line-break/>Numai ea nu a trdat.<text:line-break/>Iar ciocoii gulerai<text:line-break/>Sunt spurcai i veninai.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Braov, 1848, 10 decemvrie</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cocheta btrna la oglinda </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Tu vzui, vzui, oglind,<text:line-break/>Frumuseea-mi rsrind,<text:line-break/>i cu-ncetul eclipsind,<text:line-break/>O vezi iari apuind.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n zadar colori silite,<text:line-break/>Frumusei de-mprumutat;<text:line-break/>n zadar sunt ngrijite<text:line-break/>Nite flori ce s-au uscat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Plngi, oglind, plngi cu mine!<text:line-break/>Nu gsim ce mai ctm!<text:line-break/>Cnd m vz acum n tine<text:line-break/>Amndou ne-ntristm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Acea bucl aurie,<text:line-break/>Ce cu graii resfiram,<text:line-break/>O vezi trist, argintie,<text:line-break/>N-o-ngrijesc cum o-ngrijam!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Acea frunte ngereasc,<text:line-break/>Care-ati o adora,<text:line-break/>A-nceput s se-ncreeasc;<text:line-break/>Nu mai este ce era.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Acea pieli ca crinul,<text:line-break/>Acei ochi ce schinteia,<text:line-break/>Cele buze ca rubinul,<text:line-break/>Cea dintur ce sticlea,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ca nlucul se trecur:<text:line-break/>Sunt ca flori ce-au vetejit!<text:line-break/>N-au lsat nici o trsur,<text:line-break/>Moartea parc le-a plit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Plngi, oglind, plngi cu mine<text:line-break/>Nu gsim ce mai ctm!<text:line-break/>Cnd m vz acum n tine,<text:line-break/>Amndou ne-ntristm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Prin povaa ta, odat,<text:line-break/>Iscusina mea fcea<text:line-break/>Mii de inimi ca s bat,<text:line-break/>Mii de capete-ntorcea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S-a dus timpul fericirii,<text:line-break/>Cnd n faa ta sltm<text:line-break/>S-mi cerc armele zmbirij:<text:line-break/>O! ce lume subjugam!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dimineaa cnd, zglobie,<text:line-break/>nc-n patu-mi te priveam,<text:line-break/>Ce ascuns bucurie!<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>n ce fermec m rpeam!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O! ce dar e tinereea!<text:line-break/>i noi cum o nengrijim!.<text:line-break/>Ce frumoas-e frumuseea,<text:line-break/>Dar, puin ne folosim!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S mai vie nc-o dat,<text:line-break/>Cu cercarea care am;<text:line-break/>S m vz iar adorat...<text:line-break/>-atunci... viaa, Doamne, ia-mi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Inima-mi -acum a cere,<text:line-break/>-acum nc a iubi...<text:line-break/>M gndesc... o! ce plcere<text:line-break/>n amor a birui!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar sunt armele zdrobite<text:line-break/>De ast timp afurisit,<text:line-break/>De ast timp ce ne trimite<text:line-break/>Brazdele de ngrozit;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De ast timp care plete<text:line-break/>Orice-n drumuri va clca,<text:line-break/>-urmele ce tiprete<text:line-break/>Nu-i putin-a se spla!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Toi aceia care-odat<text:line-break/>mi da lacrme d-amor,<text:line-break/>Abia mila lor mi-arat;<text:line-break/>mi surd drept un favor,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">M-ocolesc; i vz departe;<text:line-break/>Se anun de confidani;<text:line-break/>A lor glume sunt dearte:<text:line-break/>Sunt amici, nu sunt amani!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n deert sunt muctoare;<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>n deert sarcasmul meu;<text:line-break/>Cci acum nu d fioare<text:line-break/>Aeru-mi picant sau greu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Plngi, oglind, plngi cu mine!<text:line-break/>Nu gsim ce mai ctm!<text:line-break/>Cnd m vz acum n tine,<text:line-break/>Amndou ne-ntristm.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cugetare I </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Un pr alb! Iat semnul c iarna m ajunge.<text:line-break/>Aa i bruma cade pe verdele ce fuge,<text:line-break/>Aa albete anul cnd este spre sfrit.<text:line-break/>Tot astfel, trecnd vara, pe criv se ivete<text:line-break/>Al iernii fulg de brum ce fluturnd s-oprete<text:line-break/>P-un arbor fr frunze,  el iarna i vestete<text:line-break/>i-ndat, dup dnsul, troieni l-au nvlit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Devreme nc-n mine sim focul cum se stinge;<text:line-break/>Viaa-mi curge iute, spre moarte-n grab m-mpinge.<text:line-break/>Un an ntreg mi-e ziua, un chin e-n mine-afund!<text:line-break/>i sngele-mi n vine nghea de durere,<text:line-break/>Precum nghea unda l-a vntului putere,<text:line-break/>Cnd zeul ce-nclze<text:span text:style-name="T16">t</text:span>e e-n alte emisfere<text:line-break/>i razele-i slbite deloc n-o mai ptrund.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd firea o s moar, nti nglbinete:<text:line-break/>Copaciu-i las frunza, ctina vetejete<text:line-break/>i pasrea vroas i cat alte climi.<text:line-break/>Pe lutu-mi glbineala o vz cum se lete,<text:line-break/>Puterea mea m las, din zi n zi slbete,<text:line-break/>Simirea mi adoarme, iluzia s-oprete,<text:line-break/>i chiar sperana-mi fuge s-i cate alte lumi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Aa i moartea toate cu-ncetul putrezete,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Aa sub coasa vremii fiina-nglbinete,<text:line-break/>Aa un corp se pierde cnd altul s-a format;<text:line-break/>i econoama mn, prin care se d via,<text:line-break/>Prin legea nemuririi, din zi n zi ne-nva<text:line-break/>Nimic c nu se pierde prin ast-a iernii ghea, <text:line-break/>Un lut ce st d-a bate deloc a i-nviat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Din magazia firei, l-a soarelui capriii,<text:line-break/>Machina fr margini i ia, fr condiii,<text:line-break/>Materia i-o toarn pe forma care vrea.<text:line-break/>Contractul este unul -etern ea e datoare<text:line-break/>S mite fr preget, s-nvie tot ce moare, <text:line-break/>Nimic s nu se piarz i totul n sudoare,<text:line-break/>Materia s fiarb cu viaa ce-are-n ea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Prin lanul cel de forme prin care se unete<text:line-break/>Metalul ctre plant i planta se rudete<text:line-break/>D-aci n animale treptat pn la om,<text:line-break/>Puterea cea vital din toart-n toart-alearg,<text:line-break/>Msoar-a lor organe pe timpul ce-or s mearg,<text:line-break/>Se-mparte-n toate focul, i-n eentru-apoi, ntreag,<text:line-break/>Se-ntoarce, prevegheaz spre oriice atom.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n locul unei forme ce timpul o slbete,<text:line-break/>Se toarn alt form, i-n ea se nvrtete<text:line-break/>Viaa hotrt la toarta ce inu.<text:line-break/>Inteligena i ea n via locuiete:<text:line-break/>mpins de ea nsi atomu-i crmuiete,<text:line-break/>i-ntreaga armonie nimica n-o oprete,<text:line-break/>Se ine ea de sine sub legea ce-i fcu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Aa, dar singur omul, fiin gnditoare<text:line-break/>Ce are voie-n sine, ce are mai mult soare,<text:line-break/>Mai nobil dect toate, e mult nedreptit; <text:line-break/>Cci toat creatura printr-un instinct triete,<text:line-break/>Cu el se nate-n sine, cu el mbtrnete;<text:line-break/>Dar Omul, d-a sa voie, dorete, se muncete<text:line-break/>i meritul su este c e etern trudit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Fatal izvor de lupte! Ce oare-mi folosete<text:line-break/>i chiar inteligena cnd sfera-mi m oprete<text:line-break/>S-mi prinz a mea himer -un bun ce am dorit?<text:line-break/>Ce-mi trebuie i ast voin absolut<text:line-break/>Cnd ea la alt nu-mi serv dect s-mi fac o lupt<text:line-break/>Cu nsumi eu n sine-mi? i rvna mea czut<text:line-break/>S o privesc cu fal, s strig: m-am biruit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Un tigru pe alt tigru deloc nu pizmuiete,<text:line-break/>i leul alte fiare a stpni voiete;<text:line-break/>Dar Om, mai crud tu nc, omori pe fraii ti! <text:line-break/>Puterea minii tale te-a dus ctre trufie;<text:line-break/>Iubirea ta de sine a rupt orice frie; <text:line-break/>Corupia fu gata fatalu-i tron s ie<text:line-break/>i toate-i ajutar s-i rzi tu chiar d-ai ti!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">mbrcmintea-i, hrana i toat-a ta micare,<text:line-break/>Tot pasu-i, tot capriul, o simpl-a ta plimbare<text:line-break/>Omoar mii fiine, i nici c te gndeti.<text:line-break/>Un monstru n natur, numeti precum i place<text:line-break/>i fapte, -elemente; -apoi conspiri, n pace,<text:line-break/>Pierzarea rasei tale, pierzarea-n dobitoace; <text:line-break/>Cult, lege, nsi pacea cu moartea nsoeti.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O! daca se mai ine fiin-n omenire<text:line-break/>Ce preuiete firea -a Domnului mrire, <text:line-break/>A Omului icoan abia mai st-n poet:<text:line-break/>D-a sclavului durere el singur se atinge;<text:line-break/>A sceptrului trufie prin el se mai nvinge;<text:line-break/>Pe Om la libertate el numai l mpinge;<text:line-break/>El singur e-advocatul a orice drept clcat. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Nu credei c poeii triesc n lumea voastr;<text:line-break/>Nu credei c-aste vorbe ce-nsemn gndirea noastr,.<text:line-break/>Art cu demnitate ce simt n fundul lor:<text:line-break/>Anima lor e harp cu mii de coarde-ntinse,<text:line-break/>Plpnde, simitoare, de orice clip-atinse,<text:line-break/>-a cror sfinte-acorduri, ca-n bronz n voi nvinse,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>S-amestec-n orchestra de lng Creator.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Fiin neneleas! Pentru dureri strine<text:line-break/>Tu gemi i plngi mai tare dect i pentru tine,<text:line-break/>Cnd ei, spre rspltire, te blestem, te gonesc. <text:line-break/>Tot astfel e gonit i paserea miloas<text:line-break/>Ce vine s jeleasc n noaptea-ntunecoas<text:line-break/>Cu cel ce e-n durere, i-n plngerea-i duioas,<text:line-break/>In loc s-i dea scpare, o bat i n-o primesc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i eu am plns ca dnsa ruina-n omenire;<text:line-break/>i eu am fost ca dnsa, n loc de mulmire,<text:line-break/>Urt n multe rnduri de cei ce am iubit.<text:line-break/>In primvara vrstei vz prul c-mi albete,<text:line-break/>i fr-a tri nc viaa-mi se sfrete;<text:line-break/>nghe n miezul verii i steaua-mi s-eclipsete,<text:line-break/>i fr-a putea prinde nimic din ce-am dorit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">ntocmai ca i pomul ce fructu-abia i leag<text:line-break/>i piatra-n mai i bate i fruct, i frunza-ntreag,<text:line-break/>i-i las numai trunchiul mnat i ofilit,<text:line-break/>M vz n primvar-mi izbit i eu de soart, <text:line-break/>De soarta nempcat ce-n scurta-mi via moart<text:line-break/>nchise tot n fa-mi a fericirii poart,<text:line-break/>-etern a mea speran din buz-mi a rpit!...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cugetare</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph"><text:span text:style-name="T7"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">e raiul pmntesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n inimele care nencetat iubesc.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">LABBE DB LAMENNAIS</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ne-ar fi fost deschis a soartei noastre carte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-a fi vzut ntr-nsa prescris a mea parte;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dorinele-mi atuncea a fi tiut supune,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-a amgirii mele grozav-amrciune</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Deloc n-a fi cercat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Amor i amicie, ferice-nchipuit, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Strin n lumea noastr,  eu n-a fi mai gonit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici n-a fi ateptat!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce te sfarmi atta, fiin trectoare?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce goneti nlucuri, himere pieritoare?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dorine neatinse, sperane nemplinite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din crepuscul n noapte, visri necontenite?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aceast-i este viaa de care te mndreti!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Am blestemat cu lacrimi, i n a mea mhnire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un glas strin m-ntreab: De ce m tot huleti?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu simi tu fericirea? n tine n-ai iubire?...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iubete! asta-i viaa ce-o zicei voi cereasc;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Amorul i sperana e viaa ngereasc;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iubii i suntei angeli  e raiul pmntesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n inimele care nencetat iubesc!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">D-atunci eu sim cldura n snu-mi palpitnd,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sperana vz d-atuncea nencetat rznd.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">1842, septemvrie</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cugetare</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Etern aceleai patimi pe ast pmnt hulit!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Etern aceeai lupt, etern aceleai trude!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i omul vine vesel la jugul unde-aude</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Gemnd mpovoratul, sub sarcin-i zdrobit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca i milionarul aa -un certor</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se plng de-a lor via, d-a lor nemulumire;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca i un sclav ce geme n fiare, asuprire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aa i concheranii se plng de soarta lor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i unde este bunul d-aici de pe pmnt?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unde-l ctai, prieteni? n lupte sngeroase?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Saraiuri desftate? n biruini pompoase?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n inventri mree, p-al fantaziii vnt?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ctai de motenire otelul dinvalizi?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Panteon, piramid, d-un Sardanapal soart?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Oricare v-a fi inta, a fericirii poart</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E dincolo de via,  -acolo v gndii.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Egalitate, pace i oricte dorim;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Frie, libertate i toate-aste cuvinte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fr-neles, dearte, cu care omu-i minte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dorinile i patimi,  acolo le gsim!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Socrat ce afl raiul, Columb i Galileu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cesar i Bunparte avur-amar via,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca cel care cerate i viforul nghea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca sclavul care geme, uitat de Dumnezeu!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Egalitate-aicea e numai n dureri;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe cea adevrat mormntul o vestete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unind pe animale cu om -orce triete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i confundnd sracul cu putredul d-averi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce s-a fcut virtutea lui Lafayette de ieri?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A lui Rothschild avere? a lui Rousseau gndire? </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ctai-le rna!  aflai vro osebire? </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Oari pe Traiani cunoatei din Neroni sau Tiberi?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar au lsat un nume!  i ce le pas lor!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai simt ei oari acuma a noastre comparaii?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai simt ei vro plcere l-attea veneraii?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De onorm ast nume, sau e ngrozitor?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cntec oltenesc </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Leleo muic, rndurica</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu mai poate, mitutica,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-i frumoas diminea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Roua-i nasturi pe verdea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i Zoril-n rsrit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Joac-n cmpul aurit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Plec, m duc la d-i ciocoi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-i bat joc i-i rd de noi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Leleo muic, leleo Doamne!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prunculeii-mi mor de foame.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mor n ara Romneasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cea avut, cea cereasc!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Codrul mndru c-a-nverzit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Frunza mi l-a-mpodobit;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M duc s pndesc ciocoi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C prea mult i rd de noi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce folos d-aa cmpie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De a rii avuie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-aduc aurul cu sacii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Daca parte n-au sracii!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C din holda ce muncesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici un bob nu folosesc;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Muncesc tot pentru ciocoi.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copilaii mi stau goi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-au cmae, n-au mncare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C i biata m-sa n-are.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-are-a toarce, n-are-a ese,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i din trene nu mai iese.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C pltesc, pltesc, pltesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nu mai m rfuiesc.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tot e-n plat la ciocoi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lumea nu e pentru noi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">ntr-o zi ne-a cere doare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Plat p-aer i pe soare.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C cer vam i chirie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i p-a fiarei vizunie.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pltesc locul de bordei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i n-am nici mlai de mei.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, ciocoi, ciocoi, ciocoi,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-am fi oar de vin noi!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Anul tot n lucrul vostru,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-avem timpule al nostru.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">P-o oi cerei plat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fiindc pate, fiindc fat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Gini cerei s v dm;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De n-avem, s cumprm.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai iertai-ne, ciocoi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-abia pielea e pe noi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn cnd s dm n var,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Doi copii mi degerar;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-i coliba drmat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cerga d-arenda luat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De gteaje am sfrit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ciocoiul le-a scumpit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, ciocoi, ciocoi, ciocoi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce ne frigei, vai de noi!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">C pltesc i pentru vatr,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pentr-un cpti de piatr,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pentru tot ce e sub soare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-a zis Crist, c daca moare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Al d-a fost mai necjit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El e-n cer mai fericit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai dai cer pe la ciocoi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i pmnt la d-alde noi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cristulee, mai ia-i cerul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C ne rebegete gerul.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ia-i i cerul i cuvntul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i mai las-ne pmntul.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">D-mi ct poci mcar a sta,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Capul a mi-l rezima.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai du-n cer i d-i ciocoi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i mai iart-ne pe noi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Leleo muic, dac-a prinde</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Hoomani d-i de ne vinde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Hoomani de la biserici,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">D-i ce ne tot fac la predici,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S le spui ce-a zis Cristos</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe cnd mi-i umbla pe jos</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i da lumea la ciocoi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-oprea cerul pentru noi!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Leleo muic, cucul cnt!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Var verde, var sfnt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Codrului c plete-i crcte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe voinic c mi-i umbrete.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Umbra-i deas-n crpeni,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S m-aez la un coti,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S pndesc la d-i ciocoi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C prea sunt spurcai cu noi!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Leleo muic, miculi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ia d-mi toanta puculi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C de an n-am mai ctat-o</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i rugin-a fi mncat-o.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C de an n-am dat cu ea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-asta-i toat-averea mea.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C m duc la d-i ciocoi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-i bat joc i-i rd de noi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Puc lung ghintuit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din rzboaie dobndit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Motenire de la tica,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tica ce nu tia frica.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C intra n crjali</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i da groaz-n pazvantli.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tata n-avea plug i boi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se hrnea de la ciocoi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Poterile i catane</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i zicea tot cpitane.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd rcnea, scotea vpaie;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu-i sta nimeni n btaie;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El mi-a zis cnd a murit:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te-am crescut i te-am iubit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Punte-n pnd la ciocoi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C ei nu sunt frai cu noi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Leleo muic, cucul cnt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voinic codrul s-avnt;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Frunza-i verde i curat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Parc-mi vz nevasta fat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar m duc voinic i viu</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nu tiu d-o s mai viu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-oomanii de ciocoi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Or fi poteri dupe noi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">C ei fur n ziua mare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n Divan, n Adunare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fr fric de robie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De btaie, pucrie;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci ei sunt privileghiai</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i de prvili aprai;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Brasle rele de ciocoi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce sug sngele din noi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd pleca n haiducie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copilaii i soie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu btrna lor bunic,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">l inea plngnd de fric.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El pe toi i sruta,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Flinta-n umr -arunca,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i, lund-o spre Vulcan,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zicea-n frunz pe Jian.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Ctre tinerii rumni</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">Tineri rumni,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">Pn s nu intrai in citire, m socotesc dator a ntmpina cugetarea voastr cu oareicare ndreptri despre grealele ce vei ntlni n slabele-mi nceputuri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">Daca nengrijitele-mi ncercri, att de n grab scriser nu vor putea ascunde nendreptatele-mi greale, de care negreit trebuie s fie pline, nu fii att de aspri a le prejudeca fr a v nchipui greutile ce trebuie s cerce un nceptor i piedicile ce trebuie s ntmpine la orice rnd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">Poate ns s-mi adaoge cineva: c cine m-a silit a m da nsumi naintea unei critici att de prevzute? Eu i laud i i cinstesc al lui cuvnt de sfial, dar se vede c este fireasc acea nerbdare de a-i vedea cineva ostenelile tiprite, o patim ca i toate celelalte, ce nu se poate domoli dect cu dobndirea lucrului. Patima este pe urm i sofist: ii pune nainte felurimi de amiratori; din toate prile judeci blnde i felurimi de mulumiri nchipuite. n sfrit, am ndrznit, i iat o carte mai mult rumneasc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">Am ntitulat Meditaii scrierile mele, pentru c mi-a plcut s gndeasc oamenii c eu am fost absorbit n cugetrile mele cnd am scris. Le-am fcut aa de scurte, cci nu-mi prea venea bine s-o iu ntins cnd luam condeiul in mn, i m-am socotit c i cititorul o s-mi mulumeasc c isprvete mai curnd capul ce a nceput odat. Pe lng acestea, la sfritul fietecrui capitul, pin ncepe altul, se obicinuiete a se lsa ceva hrtie alb; cu aceasta, <text:soft-page-break/>cartea mea pe de o parte va semna voluminoas i pe de alta n multe rnduri mi-a venit n gnd c hrtia alb de multe ori preuiete mai mult dect cea scris.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">mi pare ru c cam dau n satir, i niciodat n-am vrut s aleg aceast urcioas ramur de scris. Provedidina, ngrijind de a nu nceta niciodat mirarea omenirei asupra fiilor romanilor, ne puse ntr-o clim mai dopotriv cu aceea ce a produs duhurile cele mari ale strmoilor notri; i [cu] ct m bucur a vedea n toate zilele crescnd simtimentul de patriotism, ntrecerea la nvtur, producte literale i ntinderea luminilor, cu atta m ntristez cnd pe muli din cei de o vrst cu mine i vz a-i ntrebuina duhul i mijloacele ntru a iui veninul satirei, ntr-o vreme cnd patria noastr are trebuin de alte scrieri. Boalele morale snt foarte grele i doctoriile trebuie s fie mai dulci, daca cele eroice snt primejdioase.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">Dar am ieit din pricina mea, cci eu nu-mi propui in scrierile mele s tmduiesc boale morale, nici s ndreptez lumea cu umrul. Mi-a plcut s-mi fac nite visuri dulci i s m rtcesc ntr-o lume ideal. Am scris fr int i fr ir, i n-am fcut dect s presr nite idei vage i s le nclzesc cu un simtiment cruia singur nu tiu ce nume s-i dau. ndreptarea mea a fost ctre voi, tineri rumni! Vrsta mea, nici ncercarea nu m iart a m posomori i a v da povei. Tot ce am a v zice snt acele ce mi le-am zis i mie, i nu fac dect s-mi destinz ideile ce nencetat mi s-au nfiat in cugetrile mele.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P16"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Epoha noastr este mult mai fericit dect a prinilor notri. Pe temeiurile aezmnturilor celor nou se nal cu nelepciune zidirea cea mare a fericirei noastre i a urmailor notri! Avem un prin patriot</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4"><text:note text:id="ftn1" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>1</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
       <text:p text:style-name="P23"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Alexandru Dimitrie Ghica.</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">,carele, ptruns de adevrul i foloasele acestor mntuitoare ntocmiri, se silete ca s ne aduc un viitor vrednic de cugetrile fctorilor notri de bine i de cunotinile veacu lui nostru. Subt a lui ngrijire coalele psc cu atta nelepciune i sporire. Cei mai mari ai patriei noastre, insuflai de simtimentul ce a caracterizat totdauna pe brbaii cari au lucrat pentru fericirea noroadelor, se strduiesc a pune n lucrare i a vecinici dispoziiile constituiei ce am dobndit; jrtfesc la felurimi de ntocmiri ce se aaz pentru binele i mulumirea obteasc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P16"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dou soieti s-au ntocmit: una Agricol i alta Filarmonic, ale crora isprvi au nceput a se vedea peste ndejdea publicului. Cea dinii, fundat de nsui fratele preanlatului nostru domn, alctuit de cei mai nrvnai i cu cunotine soi, va rodnici brazda muncitorului i va rsplti sudorilor lui. n cea de a doilea, ntemeiat pe bazurile cele mai patriotice, prin soii si cei mai hotri a sluji pentru cinstea neamului, s-au aruncat nite semine fericite, care aa de curnd i-au dat rodul pentru: hrana duhului. Teatrul naional mai s-a statornicit, publicul simitor a nceput a cunoate folosul ce poate dobndi din aceast coal de moral. Literatura rumneasc a nceput a-i lua zborul su. Nu snt doi ani de zile i repertoriul teatrului s-a mbogit cu attea traducii i buci originale, spre a crora tiprire s-au i pus fonduri ndestule i s-au luat msuri spre publicarea i altora. Mdularele acetii soieti, aprinse de cea mai nobil cldur, fac cele mai simitoare jrtfe: dnii nsemntoare s-au vzut n atta scurt vreme. Numele Manu</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3"><text:note text:id="ftn2" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>2</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
       <text:p text:style-name="P23"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Marele vornic Ion Manu.</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">va fi scump pentru totdauna tinerimei ce se va folosi n coala filarmonic i tutulor rumnilor ce vor dobndi a lor petrecere i nvtur n teatrul ce se gtete a se zidi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P16"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fondatorii acetii soieti snt cunoscui; pe cel mai de aproape ngrijitor i ostenitor nu este de trebuin s vi-l spui. Numele lui este nscris n zidurile din Sf. Sava</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4"><text:note text:id="ftn3" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>3</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
       <text:p text:style-name="P13">Se refer la Ion Heliade Rdulescu.</text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">,n fietece vorb a limbei rumneti, care n minile lui s-a fcut att de mldioas, n Curierul rumnesc care a fost ca un mergtor nainte al Regulamentului organic; n tipografia sa, pe care a ntemeiat-o cu ale sale nsui osteneli i din care totdauna o parte a consfinit-o.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9"><text:soft-page-break/>Pentru faceri de bine; n teatrul acesta naional, n care a deschis un dsosebit drum, literaturei rumneti; n inimile tinerimei i n gurile tutulor cari citesc scrierile lui. Nimeni din rumni n-a cntat patriotismul mai cu mare cldur i entuziasm, nimeni n-a suspinat dragostea cu mai mult tineree; nimeni nu s-a nchinat cerului mai cu mult credin, i nimeni nu a blestemat i nfruntat iadul cu o mai mare mnie. El a fost amiratorul i idolatru al virtutei i biciul cel mai grozav al viiului, patriot i cosmopolit totdeodat, ceteanul cel mai nrvnat i supusul cel mai credincios. O, brbat fericite! Cci nu poci uni pana ta cu rvna i recunotina mea, ca s poci a te luda pe cit eti vrednic! Dar, tineri, voi l cunoatei; viaa lui v poate fi de pild la cei care ntru neavere v ostenii a v folosi din facerile de bine ale nvturei. Pana lui povuiete de model pe tot care voiete a seri aceast limb, ce a ajuns att de frumoas n minile lui. Acest duh, trimis ntr-adins spre a deschide drumul literaturei noastre, i credincios mplinitor al datoriei sale, pate cu statornicie i fr abatere ctre preursirea sa. Mndru de a rspunde prejudecilor ce nu-l ating, departe de orice trufie, afar de aceea de a face binele fr rsplat, i-a format fericirea n faptele sale i n contiina sa. Care nu l-ai vzut mergei i vei cunoate pacea i linitea sufletului su pe in veci a lui zmbitoare fa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">i voi, care n-avei nc ndrzneal a publica scrierile voastre, care dorii a afla un prieten povuitor al penii voastre, mergei la dnsul i-l vei afla gata a jrtfi ceasuri ntregi, i plin de bucurie a v cenzura cu blndee, a v povui pe drumul simului celui bun, a v curai stilul, a v mprti ideile sale cele sntoase, a v arta metodul cel mai nlesnitor i a v insufla dragostea virtutei i a bunei cuviini. Mergei la dnsul i n veci l vei afla, ca s zic ca el:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">Blnd, dulce, vesel, -aspru nu l-am vzut vrodat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">Vorbind pentru literatura noastr, cu toat vorba mi se nfiaz i autorul Primverii Amorului, acel geniu, ca s zic aa, creator al limbei rumneti, acea mldi acelii familii stpn a acetii limbi, i care n cele mai nenorocite epoce ale decadenii neamului nostru, in veci a avut fal de a se numi i a se arta rumni i a seri i a vorbi limba naional i a-i deschide un drum prin gramatica cea dinii, vrednic monument al duhului de care in veci a fost nsuflat i s-a motenit din generaie in generaie; i acest teatru, care astzi se privete cu atta mulumire i trufie de toat rumnimea, este un rod tot al seminelor celor dinti ce s-au aruncat de acest brbat prin traducia bucilor sale: Regulu, Ermiona, Britanicu, Ceasul de sear i Grdinarul cel orb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">Cnd m gndesc la cariera cea plcut a literilor aceti doi brbai mi snt necontenit nainte i pe acetia vi-i aduc i vou ci v nflcrai de nobila arsur a scrie.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">CEZAR BOLIAC</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Dormi n rcoare </text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I3"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dormi n rcoare,<text:line-break/>P-amantul tu!<text:line-break/>Dormi, dormi, viseaz<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>P-l de vegheaz<text:line-break/>Ca s adoare<text:line-break/>Idolul su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dormi, dormi,frumoas,<text:line-break/>Eu te iubesc.<text:line-break/>Dormi, dormi, divin,<text:line-break/>Luna e plin<text:line-break/>i amoroas,<text:line-break/>Eu te privesc.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II3"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Scoal, iubit,<text:line-break/>Nu mai dormi!<text:line-break/>Las-i suflarea,<text:line-break/>Las-i ctarea<text:line-break/>ntremijit<text:line-break/>A m privi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Scoal, frumoas!<text:line-break/>D-mi un zmbit.<text:line-break/>Scoal, iubit!<text:line-break/>Luna-i plit;<text:line-break/>Steaua focoas<text:line-break/>A rsrit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe mal vlvoare<text:line-break/>Se prelungesc.<text:line-break/>Apa-e senin;<text:line-break/>Zefir suspin<text:line-break/>Prin stuf fioare,<text:line-break/>Luntrea zresc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Raza aprins<text:line-break/>Pe lac cdea,<text:line-break/>-a mea blondin<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>O mn lin<text:line-break/>inea ntins<text:line-break/>n mna mea.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Epistol la colonelul I. Cmpineanu<text:note text:id="ftn4" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>4</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
      <text:p text:style-name="P13">Cenzura a desfigurat mult aceast epistol cnd s-a tiprit pentru ntia oar. Prile cele scoase nu s-au mai putut gsi (n. a.).</text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph">,,Tu rgnes cependant! Tu rgnes sur toute me,<text:line-break/>Dont ce sicle glac na pas teint la flamme<text:note text:id="ftn5" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>5</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
      <text:p text:style-name="P23"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu stpneti totui! Tu stpneti orice suflet. Cruia acest veac ngheat nu i-a stins flacra.</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note>.<text:line-break/>VICTOR HUGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Destul! omul a sa soart trebuie a-i ntlni:<text:line-break/>Cnd va vrea s-o ocoleasc mai turbat-l va izbi.<text:line-break/>Num-acela este mare care tie a rbda,<text:line-break/>Care tie cu mndrie un rstimp a nfrunta:<text:line-break/>Nu e nici o vijelie dup care-un curcubeu<text:line-break/>S nu vie s vesteasc c triete Dumnezeu!<text:line-break/>Astfel cerul hotrte i trimite-n veci martiri,<text:line-break/>S se-arate n popoare care gem n chinuiri,<text:line-break/>S vesteasc mntuirea, s zdrobeasc tron de fier:<text:line-break/>Ei sunt prad tiraniei; dar sunt toi pltii n cer! <text:line-break/>Cnd toiagul tiraniei cade peste un erou,<text:line-break/>Fama-i este avocatul i protector Dumnezeu.<text:line-break/>Dei cade-n ntreprinderi cel ce face-ntiul pas,<text:line-break/>Adevrul, Istoria n uitare nu l las. <text:line-break/>Volontirul ce s-azvrl nainte el n foc,<text:line-break/>Dei cade fr-a prinde biruin-aci pe loc,<text:line-break/>ns gloria-i triete, el e-n veci nvingtor,<text:line-break/>l onor etern urmaii ca-nainte mergtor.<text:line-break/>Dar se folosesc urmaii de ast rod al minii lor;<text:line-break/>Ei au toat fericirea; gloria, acei ce mor.<text:line-break/>Al lor nume, fr moarte, triesc chiar ntre vrjmai,<text:line-break/>Amicii-l rostesc cu fal i dumanii sunt pizmai.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Toat cumpna dreptii se ardic-n viitor;<text:line-break/>Cntrete-a noastre fapte fr de prigonitor.<text:line-break/>Istoria-i nemurire, i ntr-nsa cin s-a scri,<text:line-break/>De pedeaps sau rsplat nu se poate mntui.<text:line-break/>Ca i Tiii, i Tiberii tot d-o mn sunt pltii;<text:line-break/>Unii glorii au eterne; alii sunt de toi hulii. <text:line-break/>Dar tu prea te-ai lsat moale, prea i rzi de gzii ti;<text:line-break/>Ei despreul tu nu-l simte; ct i lai, se fac mai ri.<text:line-break/>i chiar Crist va s se scape, cnd se vede-ntre pgni:<text:line-break/>Trebuie ca s te aperi cnd eti presurat de cini.<text:line-break/>Provedina, chiar ea nsi, nu te poate ajuta,<text:line-break/>Daca n-ei mai da din mn cnd noianul te-a-neca:<text:line-break/>Dintr-o inim, curajul, zice marele Voltaire,<text:line-break/>Face, sau un erou mare, sau un mare criminel.<text:line-break/>Ct de neagr-o fapt mare are puntul ei frumos,<text:line-break/>Numai mediocritatea este lucru urcios. <text:line-break/>Din osnd la rsplat e adesea chiar un pas:<text:line-break/>Cugetul e rea pedeaps n aceia ce se las<text:line-break/>Dintr-un drum ce poate duce la o iuit ce-a avut;<text:line-break/>Ct e calea mai spinoas, att preul e avut.<text:line-break/>tiu c Cromwellii se schimb,  se-nel bieii pmnteni,<text:line-break/>Dar, tot timpul, tim prea bine, a produs i Cmpineni.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd s tii ce bine-mi pare c eti astzi exilat<text:line-break/>Ca prizonier al curii i-n Rusia defimat,<text:line-break/>Ca s poci fr ruine i de fa-a arta<text:line-break/>Pn unde-a ta virtute m silete-a te stima,<text:line-break/>Tu, cu toat amicia, crez c te-ai fi ndoit,<text:line-break/>i ai crede cum c-n tain n veci rul i-am voit;<text:line-break/>Dar am martor contiina i m jur pe ara mea,<text:line-break/>C, de a dori o soart, este numai soarta ta.<text:line-break/>P-un exil att de nobil -astfel de nenorociri,<text:line-break/>Chiar tiranilor l-e pizm, afundai n fericiri.<text:line-break/>Daca cugetul cu tine este blnd, este-mpcat,<text:line-break/>Daca contiina-i spune c tu ru nu ai urmat,<text:line-break/>Las s-alerge calomnia!  tu eti vesel, linitit;<text:line-break/>Cnd n pace eti cu tine, pururea eti fericit.<text:line-break/>Calomnia n-are arme, eco nu poate gsi,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Se ntoarce,-i vars fierea acolo d-unde iei, <text:line-break/>Cnd viaa ce prate este limpede c-a ta,<text:line-break/>Cnd ntr-nsa fapte bune le gseti fr-a cta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">ns inta-mi acum nu e ca s-i fac panigiric,<text:line-break/>Nici s-i fac apologia, eu m sim ct sunt de mic.<text:line-break/>A voi s aflu numai acum eti mai sntos?<text:line-break/>Ast voiaj, la sntate, datu-i-a vre un folos?<text:line-break/>Acel nger de femeie care tu i l-ai gsit<text:line-break/>n nenorociri, cu tine, este i el mulumit?<text:line-break/>Costandin seamn tat-su? Poate-n temnii a tri?<text:line-break/>Sabia ce i-ai adus-o poate a o mnui?<text:line-break/>S-l nvei ct poi rbdarea; secolul ce l-a produs,<text:line-break/>Vre un leagn de mtase n-a crede s-i fi adus.<text:line-break/>L-ale tale interesuri, poate a te supra<text:line-break/>Dac-ai ti sinceri prietini n exil te vor urma?<text:line-break/>Spune-mi: Vrei s aibi cu tine vre un om ce te-a iubit<text:line-break/>Vrei s viu i eu acolo?  hotrate-mi desluit.<text:line-break/>La aceast ntrebare voi s aflu ce gndeti:<text:line-break/>i, nerspunznd, voi crede c tu nu m mai iubeti.<text:bookmark text:name="cite_note-21"/><text:bookmark text:name="cite_note-11"/></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Epistol la D.K.A.K. </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph">  ,<text:line-break/>   <text:line-break/>    <text:line-break/>   !<text:note text:id="ftn6" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>6</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
      <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu liberele idei,<text:line-break/>Frumoasele, vinul,<text:line-break/>Vinul i frumoasele<text:line-break/>Cnt tu, lira mea de aur.<text:line-break/><text:tab/>P. Sutzos</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note><text:line-break/>,  29</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ei, prietene, ia spune-mi din voiaj ce ne-ai adus,<text:line-break/>Au, n ar-i tot acelai te-ai ntors precum te-ai dus?<text:line-break/></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ai adus vro mantelic, vro lorniet, vrun lornion?<text:line-break/>nvat-ai s-i faci haine dup-al Franii frumos ton?<text:line-break/>Franuzete nvat-ai crlioni s-i nvrteti<text:line-break/>i, a limbesil, crvata mai cu gra</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">s</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6"><text:note text:id="ftn7" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>7</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
       <text:p text:style-name="P23"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T4">grce (fr.)  graie.</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">s potriveti?<text:line-break/>nvat-ai acea sticl ntr-un ochi a o inea,<text:line-break/>A ochia frumos pe dame i-n caleac a edea?<text:line-break/>nvat-ai de se cade de odat a intra<text:line-break/>n salonul unde-i cercul, sau de trebuie-a cta<text:line-break/>Alte ui mai indirecte, -aci, fr-a te simi<text:line-break/>Adunarea, cu ncetul, s te vaz a zmbi?<text:line-break/>nvat-ai de se cade sau de nu a saluta<text:line-break/>La intrare, la ieire,  plria a-i fura?<text:line-break/>tii, intrnd la vre o dam, cnd mnui va fi purtnd,<text:line-break/>Cum s ceri ca o pisic, i abia din ochi rugind,<text:line-break/>Mnuia s-i goleasc i apoi a-nainta<text:line-break/>C-o strnsoare lin simit frumos a i-o sruta?<text:line-break/>Dar cnd vei vorbi cu dnsa, nvat-ai cum s stai,<text:line-break/>Cum s joci prin gean ochii i ca ce miros s ai? <text:line-break/>Pieptul trebui scos afar, dosul dat mai napoi,<text:line-break/>Piciorul drept nainte i p-l stng s-l ncovoi,<text:line-break/>Plria-n mna stng, mna dreapt-ntr-un buton; <text:line-break/>Astea,crez, vor exersate pn-a nu intra-n salon.<text:line-break/>Ai bgat i tu de seam, cnd cu dama vei mnca,<text:line-break/>Cum s-o-ndopi pe tot minutul, asieta</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3"><text:note text:id="ftn8" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>8</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
       <text:p text:style-name="P23"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T4">assiette (fr.)  farfurie.</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">a-i schimba,<text:line-break/>Cum s-i torni i vin i ap spre a nu se osteni,<text:line-break/>i cu toat-mbuctura, s-o-ntrebi cum se mulumi?<text:line-break/>Cea de gintilom deviz tii acum a combina<text:line-break/>i pe viziera voastr cte creste a spa?<text:line-break/>tii ce nsemneaz: nou, eapte, ase, cinci i trei?<text:line-break/>tii cnd trebuie piezie i cnd dreapte s le-nchei?<text:line-break/>Dar coroana de dasupra, cnd va fi de prin, ci coli<text:line-break/>O s aib? Dar de duc, de baroni, de coni, viconi?<text:line-break/>Cu un cuvnt, spune-mi: tonul, heraldic-ai nvat<text:line-break/>n aceast lung cale pe pmnt civilizat?<text:line-break/>A! dar eti tu om d-aceia?  Mie-mi pare c te-auz<text:line-break/>Fcnd psuri mari pn cas, cnd pe gnduri, cnd confuz,<text:line-break/>S-mi spui c-are Englitera maini, prvili -ast venit;<text:line-break/>Canaluri, drumuri curate i comerciul nflorit.<text:line-break/>O s-mi spui c-au instituturi, coli i fbrici, n-au cenzuri,<text:line-break/>i c toi muncesc p-acolo, nu se plimb n trsuri;<text:line-break/>O s-mi spui cum c n Frana iat ce s-a mai ivit,<text:line-break/>i c-n Camera d-acolo iat ce s-a mai vorbit.<text:line-break/>Cum c sunt ranii notri asuprii i nenvai<text:line-break/>i c nici c au s fie ocrotii sau aprai.<text:line-break/>C subt ati arendai jidovi i sub otcrmuitori<text:line-break/>Gem, precum gemeau i servii subt toiege de tretori.<text:line-break/>i o s te-aprinzi cu-ncetul, s te-ntinzi la ast cuvnt,<text:line-break/>S rosteti dearte vorbe, s azvrli cuvinte-n vnt;<text:line-break/>C-ar fi adic mijloace i ei viaa a-i vedea,<text:line-break/>Neamul boieresc s scaz, privilegiul a cdea;<text:line-break/></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-avem legi i coli ca lumea, i teatru, i tipar,<text:line-break/>S-nceteze -ast boal de paharnic, de pitar.<text:line-break/>Voi suntei de vrajb oameni, toi suntei din Cmpineni<text:line-break/>Voi ai merita, grmad, s-o pornii la Mrgineni.<text:line-break/>Astea-s vorbe de un nobil? Ai tu snge boieresc?<text:line-break/>Tu, pare c-ai fi opinc: eti din neamu rumnesc!<text:line-break/>Auzi c s aib drepturi un mojic, un opincar,<text:line-break/>Rumnoiul de la ar, muncitorul,  un plugar!<text:line-break/>Mine-i zice c se cade i n Camer s-l bagi,<text:line-break/>i s eaz cu boierii cnd vorbesc despre iobagi!<text:line-break/>Tu, d-ai fi precum se cade, ca cocon i ca boier.<text:line-break/>Era s aibi stare astzi i poate i minister.<text:line-break/>Fui comandir n otire; nti avui escadron<text:line-break/>i p urm, dup asta, comandai batalion.<text:line-break/>i nti, i mai la urm, tu mblai tot cu cuvnt<text:line-break/>S nvei p soldat slujba: nici o coast nu i-ai frnt,<text:line-break/>Nu i-ai dezlipit ureche, n-ai scos ochi, de pr n-ai tras,<text:line-break/>Nici mcar cu bobrnace nu l-ai ciocnit n nas.<text:line-break/>Un osta,cnd va s bat, nu d douzeci i cinci;<text:line-break/>Strig: Toi undr-ofierii! dai pn vei da p brnci,<text:line-break/>Soldatului mnc-i hrana, leafa, nu-i da nici mondir;<text:line-break/>D-i de munc, d-i btaie, de eti zdravn comandir,<text:line-break/>Numai munca i btaia ine-n fru p un soldat:<text:line-break/>Ct l ii flmnd i-n munc, nu te temi de revoltat!<text:line-break/>Fui ispravnic la Brila, la un port cel mai frumos;<text:line-break/>Favorat i pltit bine, cu sperane spre folos;<text:line-break/>Dar, -aci tot ndrtnic: Tu vreai a administra<text:line-break/>Dup cum rezonul cere, dup contiina ta.<text:line-break/>D la dracu contiina i te-apuc de ctig!<text:line-break/>Las-te de propagant, las-te de cei ce strig.<text:line-break/>Ce-aveai tu, daca ranul, d-arenda npstuit,<text:line-break/>L-a-nelat negutorul i ciocoiu l-a cznit;<text:line-break/>C nu mai are opinc, n-o s aib ce mnca, <text:line-break/>Vino-i, omule,-n simire! Asta nu e treaba ta.<text:line-break/>Nu-i aicea stpnire? Nu snt prvili? nu e domn?<text:line-break/>Nu e ara o grdin? Eu m mir cum tu n-ai somn;<text:line-break/>Culc-te i dormi n pace subt aceti frumoi tufani,<text:line-break/>Las-i pung-asta deschis; cci acuma plou bani,<text:line-break/>Cum ploua crnai odat; starea-i faci din lucru mic;<text:line-break/>Astzi e tot meteugul: s tii s nu faci nimic.<text:line-break/>Ce-aveai tu s-opreti potvada, s nu lai pe negustori<text:line-break/>S mnnce sptmna protilor de muncitori,<text:line-break/>S strici vechile-obiceiuri, s pui a d ndoit<text:line-break/>Ci au jefuit opinca? Eti un om nesocotit.<text:line-break/>Voi sntei vrjmai ai rii -ai neamului boieresc;<text:line-break/>Vrei s mojicii nobleea cinstit p cal domnesc.<text:line-break/>Voi v-ai pus s stricai lumea i s spunei la ran<text:line-break/>C e i el om n lume, dopotriv cu un ban;<text:line-break/>Voi i barbe vechi, lsate prin timpi, epoci:., dar, s tac;<text:line-break/>Cci avei naturi ciudate; cele bune nu v plac.<text:line-break/>Ce-atta nemulumire! Ce hulii! Ce tot strigai!<text:line-break/>N-ai avut chiverniseal? Nu sntei naintai?<text:line-break/></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Care ali,att de tineri, ca voi au naintat?<text:line-break/>Ce voii s fii? Ia spunei.  Nemulumitor! ingrat!<text:line-break/>Vrei s fii tot cu cordonuri? Domni voii s fii alei? <text:line-break/>Dar, s mai vorbim grecete c s nu fim nelei:<text:line-break/>Ti! kesi thelis na ghinis ofendis? o, ho! o, ho!<text:line-break/>Alos tha ghini afendis, alos. To ksero ego</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4"><text:note text:id="ftn9" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>9</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
       <text:p text:style-name="P23"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aceste vorbe sunt zise de consolul Minciaki care prezida la facerea Regulamentului organic (n.a.). n traducere: Ce! i tu vrei s devii domn? Afar, afar! Altul va deveni domn, altul. O tiu eu.</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">.<text:line-break/>Dar, destul vorbii n pilde; s-i lsm la Dumnezeu;<text:line-break/>O s schimb acuma tonul: sta nu e felu meu.<text:line-break/>Tu erai profet odat: mi spuneai c-ati montaniari</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4"><text:note text:id="ftn10" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>10</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
       <text:p text:style-name="P23"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T4">montagnard (fr.)  muntean, denumire dat grupei membrilor Conveniunii care manifestau o poziie radical.</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">,<text:line-break/>Cnd li se va scoate masca, o s vz c sunt muari</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4"><text:note text:id="ftn11" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>11</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
       <text:p text:style-name="P23"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T4">mouchard (fr.)  spion.</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">.<text:line-break/>Ce ciudat combinare! Se opti c-n minister<text:line-break/>O s fie o schimbare, i c pn la vister<text:line-break/>O s se mpar ranguri, i, iat-i, plecai n jos,<text:line-break/>Toi se leapd de opinc ca ali Petre de Cristos.<text:line-break/>Mi-a pierit orice speran, stricai suntem foarte ru<text:line-break/>Nu-i Obteasc Adunare de cnd nu e unchiul tu.<text:line-break/>Publica prere nc pn-acum nu s-a format;<text:line-break/>Pilde nu sunt, tipar nu e, obiceiul e stricat, <text:line-break/>Ce speran de-ndreptare putem oar atepta?<text:line-break/>S privim la ruinare? Trebuie-a ne detepta.<text:line-break/>S gsim i noi vro arm; sau, cel puin, un azil.<text:line-break/>Ce ne ngrozim atta d-o gonire, d-un exil?<text:line-break/>Ce e ast amuire? Pn cnd s ludm<text:line-break/>Tot ceea ce nu ne place? Pn cnd s ne-nelm?<text:line-break/>Cel puin, o fapt bun, s-ncetm a defima,<text:line-break/>S-ncetm a-ntreba p-alii ce e bine-a luda,<text:line-break/>S-nvm a fi ai notri, s-nvm a ne gndi; <text:line-break/>O s pierdem, o s pierdem, pn cnd vom izbndi.<text:line-break/>S pim i noi cu lumea; avem timpul ajutor.<text:line-break/>S tim, cel puin, a zice: sta-i bun judector,<text:line-break/>Asta este bun ministru, sta-i bun de deputat,<text:line-break/>Asta poate fi profesor, -stlalt un avocat.<text:line-break/>Pn cnd, tot din grmad, o s tragem la noroc?<text:line-break/>Pn cnd, ca n bjenii, s n-aflm al nostru loc?<text:line-break/>Pn cnd ce a fost tata s fiu i eu, neaprat?<text:line-break/>Daca tata fu de treab, i eu sunt un om stricat, <text:line-break/>Daca tata, din protiv, fu om ru i ticlos,<text:line-break/>i eu am capacitate, poci fi rii de folos;<text:line-break/>Numai pentru ast vin, c el n-a naintat,<text:line-break/>Trebuie ca eu din locu-mi s fiu astzi deprtat?<text:line-break/>Sau, daca al meu printe, printr-un chip particular,<text:line-break/>A putut s-nainteze subt un domn de la Fanar,<text:line-break/>Oar, eu, care atuncea nc nu eram nscut,<text:line-break/>Am a lui ndemnare? Pentru toate sunt fcut?<text:line-break/>Ce sunt aste ranguri multe care nu se mai sfresc:<text:line-break/></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Conipist, pitar -attea care mai nu le brodesc;<text:line-break/>Vz c ies cte o mie p tot anu-n srbtori,<text:line-break/>i, de n-ei avea vre unu, nu poi nici s te nsori.<text:line-break/>E o boal lipicioas ce s-a-ntins ntre romni,<text:line-break/>Mai ru i dect holera: face oamenii pgni.<text:line-break/>S despoaie ziua-n ulii, prinii omor pe fii,<text:line-break/>Ca s moteneasc banii,  taxa unei serdrii:<text:line-break/>Un serdar, mcar la groap, dect via fr rang!<text:line-break/>S-i opteti c-l faci paharnic i i pune muma-n treang.<text:line-break/>Care oar e onoarea celor ce se poroclesc?<text:line-break/>Nu mai tii nici cum i cheam; nu tii cum s isclesc.<text:line-break/>Aci-i zic pitar, paharnic,  mine, ag sau clucer;<text:line-break/>Ieri tiai c-i zic postelnic i acum i zic vister.<text:line-break/>Nu mai spui d-al nostru Apolon ce striga: Sunt n zadar!<text:line-break/>Slbiciuni sunt aste ranguri! i acuma e pitar.<text:line-break/>Nu-i vorbesc d-ati profesori ce virtutea tlcuiesc,<text:line-break/>i apoi declar, din suflet, fr rang c nu slujesc.<text:line-break/>Ce m pune n mirare este numai un brbat<text:line-break/>Care-l tiu c este tare, nu e nicidecum stricat,<text:line-break/>Care-avu i cutezarea a trimite napoi<text:line-break/>Rangul ce i oferir, fr-a-l cere c-ali ciocoi,<text:line-break/>Ce declar simtimente i virtui de un Caton<text:line-break/>i s-arat,ntru toate, democrat d-ai lui Platon, <text:line-break/>Se-mbt i el dodat de ast otrvit nectar<text:line-break/>Al tiranilor? Ce dracu!  vz c i el [e] serdar.<text:line-break/>Ce sunt aste lungi cordonuri? Aste cruci plntate-n piept?<text:line-break/>Toi sunt oar de vnzare?  n-a voi s fiu nedrept <text:line-break/>Ei de sine i pun cruce, sau de alii-s la mezat?<text:line-break/>Sau, spre a li se ti preul, de stpni s-au, nfierat?<text:line-break/>Pentru c vz osebire; nu sunt toate tot un fel:<text:line-break/>Una mic, alta mare, -altele nici ntr-un fel, <text:line-break/>Cu coroni, ncolorate.  A dori acum s tiu,<text:line-break/>tia ce att le poart, ce-nsemneaz crucea tiu?<text:line-break/>Stiu ei pentru ce o poart? tiu ei ct o pngresc?<text:line-break/>tiu ce mare este crucea i cum o nimicnicesc?<text:line-break/>tiu c cel ce poart crucea e apostol, mucenic,<text:line-break/>Cavaler al Libertii?  Mai stai, oameni de nimic!<text:line-break/>Odat, era i crucea simbol sfnt, simbol frumos;<text:line-break/>Dar acuma, cine-o poart, este Iuda lui Cristos.<text:line-break/>Cine ia acuma crucea? Cel ce tie sugruma;<text:line-break/>Sau acel ce-n cmpul vrajbii mai muli oameni va trda.<text:line-break/>Dar acei ce primesc semne de pe la mai muli tirani,<text:line-break/>Care, pentru i-n protiv sunt la cei dinii tlhari,<text:line-break/>stora ce-am zice oar?  De vnzare, sau vndui?<text:line-break/>i, la care dintre dnii? Unuia, sau la mai muli?<text:line-break/>Cat orice stat s aib un mijloc a rsplti<text:line-break/>i, din contra, iar s aib altele a pedepsi;<text:line-break/>ns trebuie gndire spre a nu se profana<text:line-break/>Nici pedeapsa, nici rsplata; trebuie a combina<text:line-break/>Ca i una i ceilalt s poat contribui<text:line-break/>Oarecum ca s mai dreag pe acel ce le-a primi.<text:line-break/>Orice premiu de rsplat e czut, e profanat<text:line-break/></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd s-a dat acelor oameni care nu l-a meritat.<text:line-break/>Idealul ntr-un premiu n veci preurile-a dat:<text:line-break/>Dafinii sunt buruiane cnd nu tii cin i-a purtat.<text:line-break/>Se cuvine i pedeapsa tot aa a cumpni,<text:line-break/>Ca s fie ct i vina; trebuie a gndi<text:line-break/>Ca pedeapsa s serveasc oarcum a corija,<text:line-break/>A mai ndrepta morala, nu a o mai degrada.<text:line-break/>n aceste argumente dou neamuri izbutesc:<text:line-break/>America pedepsete i inglizii rspltesc,<text:line-break/>ns nici un stat c-al nostru n-a tiut a se gndi<text:line-break/>Cum s-i strice el poporul.  Oar nu ne vom trezi!<text:line-break/>Cel ce a furat gina e tot astfel pedepsit<text:line-break/>Ca i cel ce tlhrete toat viaa nelipsit.<text:line-break/>Cei ce-au jupuit poporul sunt tot astfel rspltii<text:line-break/>Ca i cei ce-au servit rii -au tiut a fi iubii.<text:line-break/>Sau, mai bine, chiar din contra, cei oneti sunt exilai,<text:line-break/>i tlharii-n capul rii onorai i ludai.<text:line-break/>Cnd ating aceast coard, s m crezi, m revoltez<text:line-break/>i cnd vz c-aa-o s mearg, sim c m nfiorez,<text:line-break/>neleg c-ar fi mai bine s fiu ceva mai sceptic,<text:line-break/>S m ndoiesc de toate i s nu mai vz nimic.<text:line-break/>Un: tiu i eu! sau: ce-mi pas! s fie tot ce rspunz<text:line-break/>La oricare ntrebare, pentru oriice abuz,<text:line-break/>S m-nchiz n vre o cas, i, pe gnduri rtcind,<text:line-break/>S stau c-un poet n mn, cnd dormind i cnd citind:<text:line-break/>Pe-o hrtie poleit fapte mari s nscocesc,<text:line-break/>S scriu imnuri, dedicaii la cei ce ne stpnesc.<text:line-break/>S fac o apologie, s scriu un panigiric<text:line-break/>Acestor pitici gigantici i l-ali oameni de nimic.<text:line-break/>Dar ce faci cnd i un dimon care vine a-i striga<text:line-break/>C prin ru se scoate rul, c nu trebuie-a arta<text:line-break/>Viiul nici n printe, c-ai nevoie s goneti<text:line-break/>De aproape criminalul, eti silit ca s izbeti<text:line-break/>P tlhar d-a drept n fa; cum c, pentru un boier<text:line-break/>Nu e alt ndreptare dect un Robespierre?<text:line-break/>Viu s m deschiz la tine;  poate c e un blestem!<text:line-break/>O Idee ce m roade, i, aceea ce m tem,<text:line-break/>Este frica cum c-n. Via-mi n-o s vz a-i rzbuna<text:line-break/>Aste trupe dezarmate! N-o s vz a se-nchina<text:line-break/>Capetele pngrite la opinci de muncitor;<text:line-break/>N-o s vz steanul nostru a-i fi el legiuitor!<text:line-break/>Credina mea mi spune c ast timp ne va veni;<text:line-break/>Dar, pn atuncea, oar, voi putea i eu tri?<text:line-break/>Nu cumva va fi trzie ca Mesia</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3"><text:note text:id="ftn12" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>12</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
       <text:p text:style-name="P23"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vezi Ioan Evanghelistul 1415 (n.a.).</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">ce-ateptm?<text:line-break/>Nu cumva ne minte rul, ca s fac s-l rbdm? <text:line-break/>Fie, cci pn atuncea misia mi-o mplinesc:<text:line-break/>Pn cnd n-oi lua fierul, pana mea nu-mi prsesc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Eram rpit atuncea </text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I4"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Eram rpit atuncea cnd te-am vzut a plnge,<text:line-break/>i cerul, pietatea, priveam cum se resfrnge<text:line-break/>n lacrimile tale.<text:line-break/>Ferice, am zis, e bardul, cnd sunete gsete<text:line-break/>A combina acorduri ce-n inimi prelungete<text:line-break/>Preludurile sale!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cci, crede, viitorul i trmbia veciii,<text:line-break/>Ce-mbat nc-n via pe fiii armoniii,<text:line-break/>Eu rece le privesc.<text:line-break/>Dar a simi gndirea-mi p-o frunte de fecioar<text:line-break/>C trece cu-orice not, c harpa-mi o-nfioar<text:line-break/>E tot care doresc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Oh! S-mi privesc ideea n ea cum se resfrnge,<text:line-break/>C spiritu-i o simte, cum inima-i se strnge<text:line-break/>O lacrim a stoarce;<text:line-break/>Cum buza ei se mic vrnd a-neca suspinul,<text:line-break/>Cum lacrima n ochii-i ntunec seninul,<text:line-break/>Spre cer cnd l ntoarce;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i a simi c simte, i a vedea c vede<text:line-break/>Icoana dureroas ce bardul ntrevede<text:line-break/>Cnd este inspirat;<text:line-break/>S sim n extaz gndu-i, s-o sim c contmpleaz<text:line-break/>Nuana cea mai mic cnd coarda mea turbeaz,<text:line-break/>Hulind vre un pcat:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S vz nflorind roza pe crinii fecioriei,<text:line-break/>Ca cerul cnd s-aprinde de focul veciniciei<text:line-break/>Ce-apune n departe;<text:line-break/>Tuleiele pe fa-i simirea cum nvie:<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Precum p-un lac zefirii nfiorai adie<text:line-break/>i-n mii de unzi mparte;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S tiu c al meu nume, btut de rutate,<text:line-break/>Triete-n suvenirea-i ca n eternitate,<text:line-break/>Ca-ntr-un azil ceresc;<text:line-break/>S tiu c a mea harp n inim-i rsun,<text:line-break/>Dorina-mi i suspinul se urc mpreun,<text:line-break/>Ca-n snul ngeresc;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i-n lacrim-i durerea-mi ncet s se priveasc,<text:line-break/>Ca-ntr-o fntn slcii i bolta cea cereasc;<text:line-break/>Ca ntr-o mare norii;<text:line-break/>Ca dnsa n oglind; ca lebda n ap;<text:line-break/>Ca-n unda unei grle un mal care se sap;<text:line-break/>Ca-n ochii ei amorii; </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Atunci, atunci eu aflu i Cer i Vecinicie;<text:line-break/>Atunci m fur vise pe dulce armonie;<text:line-break/>Atunci sunt ncntat;<text:line-break/>Atuncea al meu suflet se-nal n tcere;<text:line-break/>Atuncea a mea coard din nou mai ia putere;<text:line-break/>Atunci sunt strmutat!...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II4"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar te-am vzut a plnge i-n alt ntmplare,<text:line-break/>Dar am vzut c faa-i i face sil mare<text:line-break/>S poat a zmbi, <text:line-break/>Ca zori n zile rele de tomni ntunecoase;<text:line-break/>Ca raza unui soare prin ploi vijelioase<text:line-break/>Ce stau a ne izbi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i am privit pe chipu-i ascunsa ta durere<text:line-break/>i m miram d-atta trie i putere,<text:line-break/>D-attea nfruntri:<text:line-break/>Precum privesc botanici o plant care crete<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cu mii insecte-ntr-nsa, i nu se ofilete,<text:line-break/>St mndr-n apsri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Am admirat natura n oricare-i micare:<text:line-break/>Deschis am privit cerul n oricare-i ctare.<text:line-break/>n tot suspinul tu.<text:line-break/>M adnceam n gnduri: De ce oari buntatea<text:line-break/>E prad rutii! De ce oari pietatea<text:line-break/>E prad celui ru!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De ce oari frumuseea e prad laitei!<text:line-break/>De ce oar dreptatea e prad nedreptei!<text:line-break/>Cine-mi va da cuvnt?<text:line-break/>De ce iubirea focu-i tot n dureri resfrnge!<text:line-break/>De ce simirea geme! De ce un nger plnge<text:line-break/>Aicea pe pmnt!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">-am ateptat pe gnduri, doar mi s-a da cuvntul<text:line-break/>Urla n vas vaporul! Sufla n pnze vntul,<text:line-break/>i Dunrea curgea!...<text:line-break/>Aa se fierbe omul n gnduri pieritoare;<text:line-break/>Aa ne-a purta soarta pe vremea trectoare<text:line-break/>Ct lumea va inea!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Ermitul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ce geniu te mpinse, om trist, nenorocit,<text:line-break/>S-ajungi n ast stnc unde coco nu cnt,<text:line-break/>i cinele nu latr, i iarna i mplnt<text:line-break/>Eterna-i locuin, i vara n-a rzbit?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Fugeai tu oari de lume, sau d-un duman al tu?<text:line-break/>Fugeai de tine nsui, fugeai de nedreptate,<text:line-break/>Ctai s afli pacea i snta libertate<text:line-break/>Pe unde nc omul n-a-mpins veninul su?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Cu oimii i cu vulturi ai vrut a locui?<text:line-break/>Cu vntul care geme, cu fiara ce mugete,<text:line-break/>Cu fagi de cnd pmntul, granit ce nu rodete.<text:line-break/>i s-a prut mai lesne c poi a vieui?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Mhnit ai fost, btrne, aci cnd te-ai oprit!<text:line-break/>Slbateca natur i stnc scorboroas,<text:line-break/>i peterea ce url, i rpa cea noptoas<text:line-break/>Au dat ecou mai blnd la sufletu-i rnit,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dect acele fee de tot fr amor,<text:line-break/>Dect acele inimi rcite n pcate,<text:line-break/>i sufletele-acelea, de patimi fericate,<text:line-break/>Ce nu le-ating nimica, nimic nu le mai dor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n peterea-i cea rece pmntul s-a-ncheiat.<text:line-break/>De doi buteni e ua de care e nchis,<text:line-break/>i patu-i, aternutul, e un frunzar de tis<text:line-break/>Mai verde dect vara de car-eti deprtat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O biblie -o cruce e-avutu-i simbolic:<text:line-break/>E Legea i credina. Din bolta cea negrit<text:line-break/>i verde d-umezeal, n vreme cumpnit,<text:line-break/>Lovete-o pictur p-un lesped granitic.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">E poate din izvorul ce trase Moisi;<text:line-break/>E poate pictura ce-n boal-i te adap;<text:line-break/>Te-adap cnd e vifor i nu-i poi cta ap;<text:line-break/>Cnd cotropesc troienii i nu mai poi iei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">E chiar un cronometru secund-a despri;<text:line-break/>i cade, trist, ca lacrimi din pleopele sclaviei,<text:line-break/>Ca orele fatale din mna veciniciei<text:line-break/>Ce omul le privete, dar nu le poate-opri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">D-aci tu poi mai lesne s-asculi pe Domnul tu.<text:line-break/>i acvila, ce-aint lumina cea cereasc,<text:line-break/>Va vrfuri ce-ating cerul, va muni s locuiasc;<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cmpia-i prea departe de Creatorul su,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i omu-al crui cuget triete numa-n cer,<text:line-break/>Ce fuge de mulime, cnd nc o iubete,<text:line-break/>i oamenii cu cerul a i uni voiete,<text:line-break/>i cat un Sinae la sntu-i minister.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i Crist se roag-n munte la Tatl-Creator.<text:line-break/>Profetul afl-n munte ce trebui s vesteasc,<text:line-break/>Ce trebuie s creaz i ce s nimiceasc;<text:line-break/>Mntuitorul lumii s-arat n Tabor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Eu m unesc cu tine: mi place s privesc<text:line-break/>Aceste vrfuri albe, mai nalte dect norii,<text:line-break/>Pe care schinteiaz cte odat sorii,<text:line-break/>Ce din cmpie-afund deloc nu se zresc!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">mi place s-ascult rul mugind ntr-un abis;<text:line-break/>mi place-a privi brazii n formi de piramide,<text:line-break/>Moliftul i cu tisa, ce malurile-nchide,<text:line-break/>Ca tari ceti n aer, spre cer numai deschis!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">mi place s-ascult vntul tunnd din mal n mal,<text:line-break/>mi place s vz capra srind din piatr-n piatr,<text:line-break/>mi place s-aprinz zeada<text:note text:id="ftn13" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>13</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
      <text:p text:style-name="P23"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T4">zad  arbore rinos.</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note>pe o ntins vatr<text:line-break/>i cerbul p-o sprncean s-l vz fr rival.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S stau la obria grliii de cristal,<text:line-break/>Mai rece dect gheaa, i-n unda-i cea mrunt,<text:line-break/>S vz suind un pstrov i lostria crunt,<text:line-break/>Mai iui dect sgeata, pe piatra de metal.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S-ascult la paseri triste ce noaptea se detept;<text:line-break/>S-ascult tempeste<text:note text:id="ftn14" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>14</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
      <text:p text:style-name="P23"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T4">tempest  furtun.</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note>negre departe-ntrtate,<text:line-break/>i prvlind copacii, torente-nfuriate,<text:line-break/>i vile s urle de un potop ce-atept.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>i trsnete n cremeni izbind nencetat<text:line-break/>S mple tot eterul de aburi de pucioas,<text:line-break/>S surpe n prpstii o stnc scorboroas,<text:line-break/>S zbiere pe ea ursul de groaz spimntat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i linitit n mine, cnd preajma vz turbnd;<text:line-break/>Mai linitit, mai pacinic dect ntr-o cetate,<text:line-break/>n care mii de condici i clase separate<text:line-break/>mi spun c este pace, cnd tot eu vz gemnd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">mi place s-mi las gndul s zboare neoprit,<text:line-break/>Ca acvila mrea cnd st o vijelie,<text:line-break/>Ce-i ia-n eter avntul, ctnd cu bucurie<text:line-break/>n strlucitul soare din cerul limpezit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">mi place s-mi las gndul s zboare nencetat,<text:line-break/>S zboare peste lume, s-absoarb-n veci n sine<text:line-break/>O fapt rea sau bun, s-o trag toat-n mine,<text:line-break/>Ca soarele bnd roua ce noaptea a vrsat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">mi place s-afund gndu-n al timpului noian,<text:line-break/>Al vremilor trecute, al celor ce-or s vie,<text:line-break/>i-n ele s renasc ca ntr-o mare vie,<text:line-break/>Cum spun c renasc vulturi n ape din Iordan.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Eu a dori cu tine aci s vieuiesc,<text:line-break/>S-mprtesc cu tine i gndul i vorbirea, <text:line-break/>Ast dar cu care cerul doteaz omenirea,<text:line-break/>i care anticritii pe buze ni-l zdrobesc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar nu te vz, btrne! Tu poate c-ai pierit<text:line-break/>Sub gheara vrunei fiare, ctnd cu ea-mpreun<text:line-break/>Vro rdcin moale, vro coaj-oricum mai bun<text:line-break/>Ca s-i rechemi puterea ce te-a fi prsit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Sau poate c-a fost timpul s vezi pe Dumnezeu<text:line-break/>n fa, cci eu aflu ca iarna c albisei,<text:line-break/>i tremurai ca frunza, la schit cnd te ivisei,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Ca s-i mai ceri tmie;  ca moartea-erai de greu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Oricum, ermit ferice, de nc eti p-aci,<text:line-break/>Eu strig i-i doresc pace; iar d-ai ajuns cu bine<text:line-break/>n corul cel de ngeri, m trage i pe mine,<text:line-break/>M trage, cci e timpul a nu m mai munci.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Fata de boier i fata de igan </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph">,,Comme elle est belle au soir! aux rayons de la lune<text:line-break/>Peignant sur son col blanc sa chevelure brune;<text:line-break/>Sous la tresse dbne on dirait,  la voir,<text:line-break/>Une jeune guerrire avec un casque noir!<text:note text:id="ftn15" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>15</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
      <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ct e ea de frumoas seara! pieptnndu-i sub razele lunii<text:line-break/>Prul negru revrsat pe gtul alb;<text:line-break/>Sub cosia de abanos, ai zice, vzind-o.<text:line-break/>C e o tnr rzboinic cu un coif negru pe cap!</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note><text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="4"/>ALFRED DE MUSSET</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I5"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vedei colo p-o piatr, n dos-unui oltar</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4"><text:note text:id="ftn16" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>16</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
       <text:p text:style-name="P23"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T4">oltar  altar.</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">,<text:line-break/>O fat-ngenucheat cu mini prea rugtoare,<text:line-break/>Cu fruntea ctre ceruri, cu fiarele-n picioare,<text:line-break/>Tremurndu-i buza i plngnd amar.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Vedei ct e de slab i ct e de frumoas!<text:line-break/>Ce galben albea, i talia ei tras<text:line-break/>Poi s-o coprinzi n mini!<text:line-break/>Vedei cea bucl neagr pe sn cum i undeaz <text:line-break/>Vedei ce gean crea i cum se-mpreuneaz<text:line-break/>Cu-a ei sprincene lini!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Vedei ce ochi vii, negri, i focul ce-au n ei!<text:line-break/>Vedei ce gur mic i ce trsuri plcute,<text:line-break/>Ce vetede s-arat! Pare c-ar fi trecute;<text:line-break/>Cine-ar putea spune care e vrsta ei?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Vedei cum st din gean-i o lacrim s pice!<text:line-break/>Auzi!... abia s-aude cuvintele ce zice;<text:line-break/>Oh! stai s-o ascultm!<text:line-break/>De ce nu asculi, Doamne, i la a mea durere?<text:line-break/>De ce nou, iganii, nu dai tu mngiere<text:line-break/>Cnd ie ne rugm?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Nu suntem i noi oameni ca ceilali ce-ai fcut?<text:line-break/>Nu suntem i noi oare fptura minii tale?<text:line-break/>De ce ne zice, crudul, fiine ale sale,<text:line-break/>Spune c noi suntem lucruri de vndut!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ce-oi fi greit eu, Doamne, de sunt acum n fiare?<text:line-break/>Cci am iubit o dat, au drept s m omoare?<text:line-break/>Dar ei de ce iubesc?<text:line-break/>De nu-mi este iertat iubirea,  ce mi-ai dat-o?<text:line-break/>De vatm simirea-mi,  de ce nu mi-ai luat-o?<text:line-break/>Ce-i lai de m muncesc?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd ati stpni la care ai vrut a ne-arunca<text:line-break/>Intr-n lcau-i, Doamne, ca ie s se-nchine,<text:line-break/>Le-aduci tu oare-aminte c asta nu e bine?<text:line-break/>Chinul ce ne face, nu e voia ta?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ce! pentru noi, iganii, tu n-ai fcut nimica?<text:line-break/>In loc s-avem sperana, noi n-avem dect frica?<text:line-break/>n loc a ne iubi,<text:line-break/>Ne osndeti, stpne, ca s trim n ur?<text:line-break/>Aa i-e-voia, Doamne? E dreapt-ast msur<text:line-break/>La alii a robi?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i cum am putea, Doamne, noi legea-i s inem<text:line-break/>Iubirea i sperana, i mil, rugi, credina,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Ne sunt oprite toate! Ne iei i chiar voina!<text:line-break/>Poi da ndatorire cnd drepturi nu avem?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ofta i vrsa lacrimi, sraca biat fat!<text:line-break/>Grbea s mearg iute cnd o chema s-o bat,<text:line-break/>Dar n-avea nici un spor;<text:line-break/>Cci fiarele-i sunt scurte, nu putea s alerge!<text:line-break/>Oh, ascultai, srmana! O ceart! cere verge!<text:line-break/>O bat de o omor.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II5"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Fetie norocite ce soarta v zmbete<text:line-break/>De cnd erai n leagn; pre care v iubete<text:line-break/>Aceia ce iubii!<text:line-break/>Rugai prinii votri, rugai-i s nu bat,<text:line-break/>S nu munceasc astfel pre srcua fat<text:line-break/>De tai nenorocii!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ea e de vrsta voastr,  ca voi de frumuic, <text:line-break/>I-e drag i ei pe lume! i nimului nu stric<text:line-break/>Cnd va a ntlni p-acela ce-o iubete!<text:line-break/>Ea nu tie s-i scrie,<text:line-break/>S-i nsemneze ora pe cnd poate s vie, <text:line-break/>l va cnd va veni.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cci nici el nu e liber cnd a voi s-o vaz;<text:line-break/>Cu mare grij vine, cu fric i cu paz;<text:line-break/>E rob -are stpn.<text:line-break/>De n-a iei la dnsul atuncea cnd o vede.<text:line-break/>El tare se mnie, i nicidecum n-o crede<text:line-break/>C-are stpn pgn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ea nu are saloane, ea nu are mijloace,<text:line-break/>Teatruri, s s-arate aceluia ce-o place,<text:line-break/>Concerturi i plimbri.<text:line-break/>S ias pn-n poart i-e toat fericirea;<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>S n-o vaz stpnii i-e toat norocirea,<text:line-break/>Cnd ia mbriri.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="III2"/>III</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Voi, cnd suntei acas, ieii ntr-un balcon,<text:line-break/>-alene, fr grij, cocheta ne-ngrijire<text:line-break/>V-ngroap p-un fotoliu n dulcea-v rpire,<text:line-break/>nvrtind pe deget un aurit lornion;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Simii anima voastr din ce n ce a bate<text:line-break/>La zgomot-unei droce, unui galop departe<text:line-break/>Ce-auzu-v-l ghicesc.<text:line-break/>Pe nesimite, mndre, privii pe om i calul<text:line-break/>Ce spumeg i ip s stea n loc rivalul<text:line-break/>Cu calu-i englezesc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Atunci, punnd lornionul, spre ei l aintai,<text:line-break/>Bgai de seam bine s nu fii nelate<text:line-break/>L-alegerea ce face o inim ce bate,<text:line-break/>Spune trebuina s v-nduplecai.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">ntocmai ca monarhul cnd merge-n btlie<text:line-break/>i-i vede cpitanii, ce stau cu bucurie<text:line-break/>Comanda a primi,<text:line-break/>i se gndete bine s nu se amgeasc<text:line-break/>Cu-alegerea ce face, -apoi s se ciasc<text:line-break/>Cnd timp nu va mai fi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O! ct mulumire avei cnd v privii<text:line-break/>ncongiurate-n cercuri de juni pe care-aprindei<text:line-break/>Ce vie bucurie, pe tain cnd le prindei<text:line-break/>Ocheada sau suspinul  i i vedei uimii</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd la clavir v punei rugate de mulimea<text:line-break/>Ce ncntai c-un zmbet; cnd toat tinerimea<text:line-break/>St mut-a asculta;<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cnd degitele voastre, lungi, albe, subirele,<text:line-break/>Alearg pe octave dnd fore tari i grele,<text:line-break/>i-ncep a detuna;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd cearcnul sub buza de un mrgean n foc<text:line-break/>Mrgritaru-i las pe snu-v s curg;<text:line-break/>Cnd pieptul vostru salt cu glasul ce se urc;<text:line-break/>Ochii-azvrl schinteie ce prin lustruri joc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd ndrzneul ager, ce ochii v-ntlnete,<text:line-break/>i las semicercul i vine, se lipete<text:line-break/>La spate, ateptnd<text:line-break/>Cnd s ntoarc foaia,  atunci se adnceaz<text:line-break/>Prin snu-v ocheada-i,  atunci, el nviaz, <text:line-break/>Voi v pierdei cntnd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar ns osebire e mare ntre voi<text:line-break/>i-ntre iganca voastr;  ea st i se pitete<text:line-break/>Cnd va voi s vaz pe cel ce o dorete; <text:line-break/>Se vd, i ei ndat s-ascund amndoi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ei nu au vreme mult ca s se tot gndeasc:<text:line-break/>L-e jale i l-e mil ca s se tot priveasc,<text:line-break/>i-ascund chinul, se-nel.<text:line-break/>E plin de vii rane, e slab, treneroas,<text:line-break/>i moare de ruine, cu toate c-i frumoas<text:line-break/>-iubit mult de el.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Se strng n brae numai oftnd, plngnd amar,<text:line-break/>Unind a lor suspinuri, unind ale lor flcri,<text:line-break/>Plngnd a lor junie, sorbind ale lor lacrimi,<text:line-break/>Blestemnd robia fr de hotar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i ct le e de scurt chiar ast mulumire!<text:line-break/>Ce scump este pltit! Amar chinuire,<text:line-break/>Srmanii, i atept!<text:line-break/>Ce trist e-al lor adio! se despresc cu groaz;<text:line-break/>Nu tiu ce-o s se-ntmple, de pot s se mai vaz;<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cci nu au nici un drept.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="IV1"/>IV</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Privii la igncua ce-acum nti iubete!<text:line-break/>Grbii a-i lua partea cnd crudul o muncete, <text:line-break/>Scpai-o din bti!<text:line-break/>Ea s-o ruga la ceruri viaa s v-ndulceasc,<text:line-break/>S v iubeasc lumea, i ca s v pzeasc<text:line-break/>S n-avei brbai ri!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Gndii cte o dat, cnd intr-ast copil<text:line-break/>n camerile voastre, pe tain sau de mil,<text:line-break/>Pe alte slugi rugind,<text:line-break/>i vede-attea lucruri la care se uimete;<text:line-break/>La ce pot s serveasc ea nici c bnuiete;<text:line-break/>Le-admir-n ea tcnd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd vine naintea unei psych</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3"><text:note text:id="ftn17" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>17</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
       <text:p text:style-name="P23"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T4">psyche (fr.)  oglind mare, mobil, n care se poate vedea cineva din cap pn-n picioare.</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">a voastre<text:line-break/>i-i vede goliciunea n nite trene proaste,<text:line-break/>Ce-abia se in de ea,<text:line-break/>ncepe de-i ia seama; se uit, se privete,<text:line-break/>i nu vede motivul ce o deosibete<text:line-break/>D-acela ce-o btea.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Privete bine chipu-i: ochi,frunte, mn, gur,<text:line-break/>Picior, piept,brae, mijloc i oricare trsur<text:line-break/>Fcut-a da plceri;<text:line-break/>Dar ns toate astea ntr-o complit stare:<text:line-break/>Zdrobite ru de bice i roase-adnc de fiare,<text:line-break/>Prlite de dureri!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i i nchipuiete ct i-ar veni de bine<text:line-break/>n lucia mtase, n blondurile<text:note text:id="ftn18" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>18</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
      <text:p text:style-name="P23"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T4">blond  dantel de mtase.</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note>fine<text:line-break/>i ntr-o catifea...<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Da-n visul sta dulce, un crud slugoi, obraznic,<text:line-break/>O mbrncete-afar.  Oh! ce blestem greu, groaznic<text:line-break/>Se revolteaz-n ea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd se combin-n minte-i a ei cumplit stare<text:line-break/>i fericirea voastr; cnd va ca s compare<text:line-break/>Ast trai ce v-osibesc;<text:line-break/>Cnd nu se domirete, ca ce s fie oar<text:line-break/>De se muncete astfel, ce vin o omoar,<text:line-break/>De ce o chinuiesc, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Oh! Vorba care trece prin limba minei sale<text:line-break/>nfioreaz cerul! Ar strmuta n jale<text:line-break/>i nsui pe Satan!<text:line-break/>Popoarele acelea ce-au suferit robie<text:line-break/>S-au, ters din foaia vieii: a cerului mnie<text:line-break/>Zdrobete pe tiran.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="V"/>V</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ferii-v, fetie, ca doar de-i scpa voi<text:line-break/>De grelele blesteme astor nenorocite<text:line-break/>Fiine asuprite -att de chinuite,<text:line-break/>mprotiv-acelui ce triete-n noi!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Vai de legiuitorul ce le nimicnicete!<text:line-break/>Vai de nenorocitul care le chinuiete<text:line-break/>Cu dreptul de stpn!<text:line-break/>Cristos Mntuitorul, cum spune-a noastr lege,<text:line-break/>Cnd va veni al doilea, oari cum i va alege<text:line-break/>Cretinul din pgn?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">El, drage, poruncete ca noi s fim toi frai;<text:line-break/>El a adus iubire, blndee, caritate,<text:line-break/>Credina-n rspltire i dulce libertate,<text:line-break/>Care le-o hrpete aceti neruinai!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Fiara apuc prada i-ndat-o i sfie;<text:line-break/>Cretinul, cnd ia robul, msoar-a lui mnie:<text:line-break/>&apos;L<text:span text:style-name="T13"> </text:span>omoar-ncet, ncet.<text:line-break/>Adun instrumenturi gsite n turbare,<text:line-break/>I le aplic rece, dar nu va s-l omoare:<text:line-break/>Va a-l privi schelet!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Gndii la copilia ce rii chinuiesc,<text:line-break/>Ce n-a gustat, srmana, plcerile vieii; <text:line-break/>Se trece n robie, i floarea tinereii<text:line-break/>Sub bicele de scorpii ati cruzi ce vetejesc</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Gndii la ea, sraca! Gndii c este smuls<text:line-break/>Din braul unei mume, spre-a fi etern expus<text:line-break/>S-o bat cine-o vrea!<text:line-break/>Prin curtea-v de grajduri, n pulbere, s zac<text:line-break/>Fr prini sau rude.  Flmnd, n-o mbrac,<text:line-break/>Nu I-e mil de ea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ea nu are speran a se cstori;<text:line-break/>S aib so odat, s fie i ea mum! <text:line-break/>Nu, fetie, nu rdei; nu vi s par glum<text:line-break/>Soarta-i ce n-o iart pn va muri!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">-atunci cnd interesul va s-o cstoreasc,<text:line-break/>Ea tie c durerea-i mai mult nc-o s creasc;<text:line-break/>Atuncea va simi<text:line-break/>-a soului robie, -a fiilor ce-or nate:<text:line-break/>O! ct plnge iganca cnd vede c pate<text:line-break/>Copilul ce hrni!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe ea o fac s cread c este de alt soi;<text:line-break/>S nu spere nimica, nimic pe ast lume;<text:line-break/>Etern s se roeasc de ea, de al su nume;<text:line-break/>Bnd a sale lacrimi, goal n gunoi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De-i este frig sau foame, ei o ncarc de fiare,<text:line-break/>i dau frmi de pne clcate n picioare<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>D-al slugilor rnda! <text:line-break/>Oh, Doamne!<text:line-break/>F stpnii, f-i, f-i s se gndeasc<text:line-break/>C ei sunt frai cu robii! i c-or s se uneasc n sntul tu loca!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Holera ciocoilor </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu ct mergem nainte,<text:line-break/>Libertatea-nainteaz,<text:line-break/>D holera n ciocoi;<text:line-break/>Tot ngn la cuvinte,<text:line-break/>A crti nu mai cuteaz <text:line-break/>Rnjesc cnd ne vd pe noi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ioite Poarta, Austria,<text:line-break/>Ioite consuli, diplomaii,<text:line-break/>Slugi n care credei voi,<text:line-break/>C salut Romnia,<text:line-break/>Ne nvit s fim ca fraii,<text:line-break/>Iubii, una ntre noi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S fii tot n capul rii,<text:line-break/>S fii tot n slujbe bune,<text:line-break/>Toate fie pentru voi.<text:line-break/>Fii voi boldul-naintrii.<text:line-break/>Legile a fi mai bune,<text:line-break/>Num-atta cerem noi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S triasc Romnia!<text:line-break/>S triasc libertatea!<text:line-break/>Nu mai sunt de azi ciocoi.<text:line-break/>S... triasc... la pustia!<text:line-break/>H... ch... egalitatea...<text:line-break/>Ce zisei c-o s fim noi?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Zi colea, cu voie plin:<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>S triasc Romnia!<text:line-break/>Nu e noi i nu e voi.<text:line-break/>M cam cearc-o holerin...<text:line-break/>Am o colic, pustia!<text:line-break/>Ce zisei c-o s fim noi?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">tim ce-i trebuie, cocoane,<text:line-break/>i de tuse i holer<text:line-break/>i de cte avei voi:<text:line-break/>Sau la cochii-vechi<text:note text:id="ftn19" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>19</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
      <text:p text:style-name="P23"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T4">cochii-vechi  mezat; tribunal de comer</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note>otgoane,<text:line-break/>Sau, mcar vreo zaver,<text:line-break/>Asta-i leac pentru ciocoi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Bucureti, 3 iulie 1848</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Idealul i pozitivul </text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I6"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd primvara vine pe cer i pe cmpie,<text:line-break/>Cnd aerul se mple de dulce armonie,<text:line-break/>Cnd crngul i grlia optesc ntr-un deert,<text:line-break/>Poetul atunci iese pe coasta ce rsun<text:line-break/>i inima-i, ca harp, sloboade-un mpreun<text:line-break/>La marele concert.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cotete rndurica, se-nal-n viersuri nou,<text:line-break/>Alunec pe iarba ce scnteie de rou<text:line-break/>i ager se-ntoarce, se pierde leinnd.<text:line-break/>Se gudur porumbeii, se-mbuc turturica,<text:line-break/>Alearg mielueaua, zmbete floricica,<text:line-break/>Sticlei i filomile se sparg pe crci cntnd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Acestea vd poeii cnd soarele rsare;<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cnd soarele de prier cu dulcea sa vlvoare<text:line-break/>l cheam s-l salute pe creasta unei vi;<text:line-break/>P-atunci, pe cnd bogatul s-adoarm abia poate, <text:line-break/>i-n somn, numai zstmpuri! Ce visuri speriate<text:line-break/>De griji i oameni ri!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd soarele-n domenuri de raze luminate<text:line-break/>Se-ntoarce ca eroul din lupte deprtate<text:line-break/>i-mprtie cldur i via i amor,<text:line-break/>Cnd brazde muncitorul, n trmbe nnegrite,<text:line-break/>ntinde n departe pe maluri nsmltite,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Precum artiti dau umbre la peisajul lor;<text:line-break/>Cnd ies pe btture, pe prispele lipite,<text:line-break/>Grmezi, grmezi copiii cu plete aurite,<text:line-break/>Cu grase piciorue, cu ochii scnteind;<text:line-break/>i mumele lor tineri, cu furcile n bruri,<text:line-break/>Privesc la pnze-ntinse pe margine de ruri<text:line-break/>Spuind i povestind;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd soarele apune pe vi i pe colnice;<text:line-break/>Cnd satul tot se mple de vaci i de junice;<text:line-break/>Cnd sare vieluii i ugerul e plin;<text:line-break/>Cnd rumene copile, flcii numai zale<text:line-break/>i rd cu dini de lapte, se trag de mini din cale,<text:line-break/>i spun cte o glum, i iau un mr din sin; <text:line-break/>Atunci, atunci poetul natura contempleaz.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Se mir i se-ncnt, i crede, adoreaz<text:line-break/>Cu pruncul i cu firea pe Tatl Creator.<text:line-break/>Bogatul ns-atuncea pogoanele msoar,<text:line-break/>Tot numr clcaii ce-l vd i se-nfioar,<text:line-break/>Gndind la dijma lor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De este vrun lac pacinic, de este vro pdure<text:line-break/>Btrin ca pmntul, ce n-a vzut secure;<text:line-break/>De este vro livede de flori i de miros,<text:line-break/>n care salt iepuri i presuri ciripete,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i prepelia pate, crsteiul erpuiete<text:line-break/>-insecte purpurate plec spicul undoios, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Poetul le privete cu-o sfnt bucurie,<text:line-break/>n oriice nuan citete-o poezie,<text:line-break/>Se las p-o visare, explic un. Mister. <text:line-break/>n vreme ce bogatul, strin l-ast plcere,<text:line-break/>Se uit cu ochi rece i calcul-n tcere<text:line-break/>n inima-i de fier:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ct d, n ierne grele, ast lac ce-a s sleiasc,<text:line-break/>Pdurea ce-a s taie, livezi,ce-a s coseasc.<text:line-break/>i camta ce-aduce cu sumele pe ani?<text:line-break/>Srac este bogatul cnd astfel calculeaz!<text:line-break/>Bogat este poetul cnd firea adoreaz!<text:line-break/>Srac este bogatul cu sacii lui de bani!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II6"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De e cte-o frumoas ce scnteie privirea-i,<text:line-break/>Ce-ncnt frumuseea-i, ce fermec zmbirea-i<text:line-break/>-al cror sn se salt d-o flacr d-amor;<text:line-break/>D-al cror organ dulce poetul se-nfioar,<text:line-break/>Bogatul le privete, se uit, le msoar,<text:line-break/>i spune, dintr-o vorb, ct face-amorul lor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De e un bun prieten ce-n dulcea sa iubire<text:line-break/>i uit interesul l-a altui fericire;<text:line-break/>Sau ar unde omul lumina a vzut;<text:line-break/>Sau sclav ce duce viaa sub bici, sub tiranie;<text:line-break/>Sau grbov care zace n lung agonie;<text:line-break/>Vdane ce pierd bunul -un reazim ce-au avut, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Poetul l-astea toate ptruns de grea micare,<text:line-break/>n palpit crud sloboade o lung suspinare<text:line-break/>i cerul cu-al su suflet optesc un sfnt mister,<text:line-break/>Cci ara lui pe dnsul la suflet l atinge;<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cci lacrmi de sclavie cuite-n el mpinge;<text:line-break/>Cci grbov, orb, fmeie din gndul su nu pier.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Bogatul ns spune i ara lui ct face,<text:line-break/>i sclavul ci bani taie. <text:line-break/>Lui grbov, orb, nu-i place<text:line-break/>Cnd astfel cred bogaii, sunt nsui chiar satani.<text:line-break/>Eu plng bogatul care n bani tot preuiete!<text:line-break/>Ferice e poetul ce plnge i iubete!<text:line-break/>Nemernic e bogatul cu sacii lui de bani!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="III3"/>III</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De este templu-n care trufa-arhitectur<text:line-break/>Se urc pe coloane d-adnc sptur,<text:line-break/>Se-ntinde pe sub boite ce timpul a lustrat,<text:line-break/>i unde-nscrie ruga antica-i maiestate;<text:line-break/>i plnsul i tmia, adnca pietate<text:line-break/>Locaul i-a-nsemnat;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Aicea unde-artitii, peneluri nzeite,<text:line-break/>Cobor Dumnezeirea pe lemne vechi sfinite<text:line-break/>i dau icoanei graiul din placa lor ieind;<text:line-break/>Aici unde se-nal mreaa poezie<text:line-break/>Din mii de guri vergine pe dulce melodie<text:line-break/>-eco o poart iar pe marmuri reci optind,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Poetul se strmut! i rde serafimii,<text:line-break/>Strluce zeitatea, amerin herovimii<text:line-break/>i capul su s-aprinde d-un foc dumnezeiesc! <text:line-break/>Bogaii i pun ochii pe candeli aurite,<text:line-break/>P-o cruce numai pietre, icoane-mpodobite,<text:line-break/>-un pre le hotrsc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd sun n iteatruri orchestre zgomotate,<text:line-break/>i-n loji, ovale iruri, prin lustruri luminate,<text:line-break/>Se-mplnt pe albe snuri zambile, amarant,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cnd tremur n spasmuri arcuul pe vioar;<text:line-break/>Cnd flaotul sloboade suspinuri ce-nfioar;<text:line-break/>Cnd trmbia vibreaz; fanfarele ne salt;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd rpide semnalul oprete armonia,<text:line-break/>Perdeaua se ardic i vine istoria,<text:line-break/>i veacuri mai uitate le-ntoarce napoi;<text:line-break/>Cnd scena unei crime, virtui ncet ne fur,<text:line-break/>Ne-amestec cu-Edipii, cu Bruii ce conjur<text:line-break/>i ei renasc n noi, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ah! Arta pe poetul ca farmec l nvinge!<text:line-break/>Cu Bruii el turbeaz, cu Iocasta plnge,<text:line-break/>i inima-i se mple de rane, de balsami; <text:line-break/>Bogatul, ns, preul intrrii socotete.<text:line-break/>Este poetul cnd arta l uimete!<text:line-break/>Srac este bogatul cu sacii lui de bani!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Impromptu</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph">Pe albumul D.C.I.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P15"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Precum, la o numire, o umbr trectoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ochiul fantaziei s-arat, licureaz,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i gndul de pe dnsa alearg un minut,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu crez c aste rnduri, ce scriu n strmutare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rostite d-al tu timbru, ce morii nviaz,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Or s m cheme-n minte-i, de unde-oi fi pierdut.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci, crede, c poetul, cnd sufletu-i dicteaz,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Imagina i las pe faa ce-a-mnegrit:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lectorul cnd o vede, atunci ea nviaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i vine, ca fantasm, deloc ce l-a numit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Impromptu</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph">Pe albumul D.C.K.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acel ce lng tine vrodat a trit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acela numai poate mai drept s-nchipuiasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i feele de angeli i viaa cea cereasc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nsui Creatorul de cine-i ocolit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ideea num-aceea c-n ceruri locuiesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tot astfel de fiine precum te vz pe tine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i c n ceruri merge acel ce face bine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu vz c m silete virtutea s iubesc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Improvizate la vederea unei berze negre </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">S poci opri durerea-mi i focul ce m arde</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lsai adunri, jocuri, i viu ca s jelesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe maluri, rpi tcute, d-ai mei acum departe,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca barza cea strin, cu ea s m unesc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu plngi, cernit barz, soia-i cea pierdut,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i semnul ntristrii pe pene-ai zugrvit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Jeleti a ta pereche, -oricine se strmut</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vzndu-te n doliu i-n traiul singurit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar eu, o, credincioas! Eu nu poci fi ca tine;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n crude suferine ce inima-mi o strng,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu trebuie s sufer, s rabd durerea-n mine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S m prefac la lume i-n veci s nu m plng.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ferice de acela ce poate-ncai s geam,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S strige n durere-i, s-i spuie al su dor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-aoela ce-l aude s-i poat da de seam,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S plng-ncai cu dnsu, de nu-i d ajutor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">1838, iunie 5</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">La d-na Elisabeta tirbei </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Blndeea, modestia, cretina caritate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De s-au numit virtute n lumea de Scandal,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De place Poeziei o pur pietate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De se onoar nc Amorul conjugal </text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eti bel atunci, doamn, n dulcea-i csnicie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n junele odrasle n care te aflm;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i admirm iubirea-i de mum, de soie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i faptele-i cretine le binecuvntm.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i Poezia astzi n sacra ei ardoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unete -aste note la imnul nlat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De dou sute voce din inimi de fecioare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-nva legea-n umbr-i i pilda ce ai dat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea vine s-i ureze cu vduve, orfane</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-i afl mntuirea la pragu-i cretinesc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S ie Domnul viaa-i, i faptele-i umane</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rsplat s-i aduc tezaurul ceresc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Aprilie 24, 1846</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">La d. Ioan Vcrescu </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Etern tot delsat s stea citera ta!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zefirii primverei, a dragostei zmbire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cntarea filomilei, a viselor uimire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu va mai imita?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sfritu-s-a amorul, sau danul s-a desprins?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pierit-au oari pstorii, a rguit oari cucul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n dealuri, n dumbrave nu circuleaz sucul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sau focul tu s-a stins?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-au vetejit oari timpii, rstimpii a-ncetat?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu mai suspin frunza, sau nu mai geme rul?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu plnge rndurica, nu murmur prul?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce! firea s-a surpat?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce! Acvila Daciei va sta fr Tirteu?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce! Teocrit adoarme? Durerea nu-l mai doare?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Plcerea nu-i mai place? Schinteia cnttoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-a-ntors la Dumnezeu?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce! Ai luat cu totul simirile lumeti?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Apusul, rsritul, natura nu-i zmbete?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cereasca armonie Apolon nu-i optete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd stai de te gndeti?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca harp-eolian, dai drumul a zbura</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cte-un acord n aer; i cnd ntreb de unde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De unde vine-ast sunet?  Deloc mna-i s-ascunde.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M las-a m mira...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">ns n darn s-ascunde, e sunet ce-neleg,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E de citer veche,  d sunete curate;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu e citer nou cu tonuri ngnate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce nu poci s le-aleg.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">E Muza chiar aceea ce a creat p-a mea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe care-am ascultat-o-n a mea copilrie;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce i-am rostit cntarea n toat-a mea junie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci prea mult mi plcea.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i recunosc preludul care d-attea ori</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M-a legnat pe vise, mi-a. Alinat durerea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-a rentors epoce sfinite de plcerea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n braele d-amori;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i recunosc acordul ca prin instinct firesc:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Precum cunoate-albina o floare priincioas;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Precum cunosc cocorii o clim clduroas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n care vieuiesc;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Precum, cunoate cerbul izvorul d-unde bea;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Precum cunoate orbul o raz ce-nclzete;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Precum cunoate pruncul pe muma ce l crete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd i e dor de ea;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Precum o turm simte un fluier de pstor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Precum pstorul simte un bucium sus pe munte;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Precum, dormind iubitul, ghicete p-a sa frunte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un srutat d-amor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">La d. P. Poienaru </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">(Cntat de pensionarii Colegiului St. Sava)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">naintea ta privete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bunule nvtor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prga care o rodete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spiritu-i combintor,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Este fapta minii tale</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Generaia ce vezi;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cresc ntr-ale ei anale</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dafinii ce meritezi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La a ei recunotin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu zmbete un minut:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E tribut l-a ta silin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E rsplat la trecut.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Istoria se ntinde</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Al tu nume a priimi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-aureola ce-l coprinde</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Peste secoli va luci.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">La maior Ion Voinescu II </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">     [1]</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Astfel tot striga-n Atena casta cea de eupatrizi<text:line-break/>Ce o cam zdrobise Solon; care ns-n eumolpizi<text:line-break/>nva mereu cu popii tainele a amgi,<text:line-break/>-atepta monarhul tare, toi pe el a nvli:<text:line-break/>S-i dea lui puterea toat, i intrndu-i n favor,<text:line-break/>S-l ntoarc cum le place i s i-o mpar lor.<text:line-break/>De aci, apoi, i-n Roma ast cast s-a ivit;<text:line-break/>-a avut -aci epoce; -aci iar a izbutit.<text:line-break/>Cci romanii tari i aspri, de ati greci se linguau,<text:line-break/>-orice viiu, orice crim de la dnii nvau.<text:line-break/>Astfel au lucrat pre tain la corumpii propagnd,<text:line-break/>Vrsnd fierea dezunirii, crime negre-ncurajnd.<text:line-break/>Iat imperiul se-mparte i ati nobili parazii<text:line-break/>Se formar dou cete, foarte bine chibzuii.<text:line-break/>Pre monarhi nconjurar i-i fcur lumea lor.<text:line-break/>Dup ce le ajutar ca s-i vaz precum vor,<text:line-break/>Se-mprir iar prin lume: unii mai fierbnd la sfini,<text:line-break/>Alii-n rasa vicleniei nscocind la sfini prini,<text:line-break/>Ucignd filozofia, manuscrisele arznd,<text:line-break/>Sau falsificnd n ele cte nu le era-n gnd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cel ce nu va s munceasc este-n veci nscocitor,<text:line-break/>Spiritu-i, n viclenie, totdauna-i creator.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cte rele n-aduser aste caste-n orice loc!<text:line-break/>Cte rtciri! ce groaz! ce pieiri! ce munci! ce foc!<text:line-break/>Religia pngrir, politica au smintit, <text:line-break/>Aste dou mari principii care omul a gsit<text:line-break/>Sufletul ca s-i mngie, i viaa nlesnind,<text:line-break/>S-i petreac traiul dulce. ns ati ciocoi ieind,<text:line-break/>Aste dou mari tiine le fcur instrument<text:line-break/>Lumea ca s o subjuge. Filozoful sau poet<text:line-break/>Nu putur s-i drame; cci, sau prinii ocolea,<text:line-break/>Sau le-mbria altarul ce p-ascuns crciumrea.<text:line-break/>n sfrit, veni tiparul;  ei pun mna, l hrpesc<text:line-break/>i ncep a-ntinde rul n tot neamul omenesc.<text:line-break/>S-au opus naintrii, raiunea au ucis;<text:line-break/>Ne-au acoperit trecutul smintind orice manuscris.<text:line-break/>Dar tiparul, cu ncetul, i ia dignitatea sa<text:line-break/>i se face arm tare n poporul ce-apsa.<text:line-break/>ncepu s-i biciuiasc de prin curi i monastiri<text:line-break/>-au pierit cu mare grab numa-n cteva izbiri.<text:line-break/>Numai slab rmi pe lng Devlet ivii,<text:line-break/>Se ineau de meserie: cnd ei gzi, cnd osndii.<text:line-break/>Cteva greceti provinii abia i putea inea;<text:line-break/>ara noastr ortodox i avut i trgea,<text:line-break/>Tot aci le intea ochiu i aci erau pltii,<text:line-break/>Cnd n crimele d-acolo ajungeau nesuferii.<text:line-break/>i ncetul cu ncetul i vedem a-nainta,<text:line-break/>Pre boieri, pre domni, episcopi, cpitani a dezarma.<text:line-break/>Eupatrizii din vechime se zic astzi evgheniti,<text:line-break/>i, pe vechile principii, ortodoci i monarhiti.<text:line-break/>i prescriu cteva versuri ca s poci a-i arta<text:line-break/>Cum se stira-ntre dnii i n ce chip se certa<text:line-break/>Pe frumoasa ara noastr. tii ca cini ce mriesc<text:line-break/>Cnd vd ali cini c apuc oasele ce ei ochesc:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">    ,<text:line-break/>     <text:line-break/>    <text:line-break/> , ,   ...<text:line-break/>       <text:line-break/>    ,   ,<text:line-break/></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">       <text:line-break/>       ,<text:line-break/>     ,<text:line-break/>      .<text:line-break/>      <text:line-break/>  , , <text:line-break/>       .<text:line-break/>       .</text:span><text:bookmark text:name="cite_ref-24"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_maior_Ion_Voinescu_II#cite_note-2" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T3">[2]</text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T4"><text:line-break/>Vrei s vezi dertciunea care-n noi s-a ncuibat<text:line-break/>Unde-i are origina?  Iat cine ne-a stricat:<text:line-break/>      <text:line-break/>        <text:line-break/>     ,<text:line-break/>     <text:line-break/>       ,<text:line-break/>     .</text:span><text:bookmark text:name="cite_ref-33"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_maior_Ion_Voinescu_II#cite_note-3" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T3">[3]</text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T4"><text:line-break/>Turcu-i privea cu rceal pn cnd se-mbogea:<text:line-break/>Firman! Le lua averea i pre ei i curea.<text:line-break/>Cariera lor fu asta, dar pe noi ne-au vtmat;<text:line-break/>Nu zic pentru jafuri, piedici, drepturi care ne-au trdat;<text:line-break/>Ne-au stricat i caracterul i au format ntre noi<text:line-break/>Casta rea, spurcata cast care o numim: ciocoi.<text:line-break/>Te miri i te ntrebi, poate, ce e vorba i ce cer,<text:line-break/>Ce-are a face cu ciocoiul acel vers al lui Omer?<text:line-break/>sta mi era rspunsul la inchizatori cnd vream<text:line-break/>S cer tribunal sau prvili, sau atunci cnd le numeam:<text:line-break/>Procedur, judecat.  Noi avem stpnitor!<text:line-break/>Cum o vrea stpnitorul!  Dai-mi un judector<text:line-break/>S tiu, care-mi este vina?  Un stpnitor avem!<text:line-break/>Cum o vrea stpnitorul!  Dar ce-am fcut? S vedem.<text:line-break/> Cum o vrea stpnitorul! st rspuns tot poftorit</text:span><text:bookmark text:name="cite_ref-42"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_maior_Ion_Voinescu_II#cite_note-4" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T3">[4]</text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T4"><text:line-break/>Fcu s-mi aduc aminte versul care ai citit.<text:line-break/>apte luni fui la-nchisoare cum alii n-au mai cercat;<text:line-break/>Un prizonier n Tunis, ntr-o stnc de pirat,<text:line-break/>Crez c-o via mai cumplit nu ar fi putut cerca;<text:line-break/>Mi-e i jale, mi-e i scrb amrunte-a-i arta;<text:line-break/>Cri, cerneal i hrtie nu puteam ca s zresc,<text:line-break/>mi era oprit cu totu i s scriu i s citesc.<text:line-break/>Nu puteam s vd pre nimeni, nici pre chiar paznicul meu;<text:line-break/>Numai sentinela mut care m-ainta mereu<text:line-break/>ntr-o umed cmar, strmt ct s m-nvrtesc:<text:line-break/>sta e arestul nostru ce corecie-l numesc.<text:line-break/>Infernalele torture ct colo s-executa:<text:line-break/>ipete, rcniri grozave, ce nenorociii da,<text:line-break/>Fur singurele voce ce-n ast timp am ascultat.<text:line-break/>Mir-te, c m mir i eu: am trit i am rbdat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cincizeci poate de tacriruri</text:span><text:bookmark text:name="cite_ref-51"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_maior_Ion_Voinescu_II#cite_note-5" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T3">[5]</text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T4">mi-au luat, neaprat.<text:line-break/>Ceea ce am scris n ele, s m crezi c-am i uitat.<text:line-break/>Unele erau frumoase, cci vedeam c nu plcea<text:line-break/>Comisarilor. Ce mndre sclmbri unul fcea;<text:line-break/>S-ntindichea, cltea capul cu un rnjet de schelet,<text:line-break/></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S spetea, zbrcea din buze ca pisica de oet.<text:line-break/>Cu toate-astea, nchisoarea are i ea ceva bun:<text:line-break/>E un nger ce mngie cnd fiarele-ncep de sun.<text:line-break/>Strmutrile-nchisorii se pot bine compara<text:line-break/>Cu acelea ce ne spune c deerturile da<text:line-break/>n profeii din vechime. Zile trei ct au trecut,<text:line-break/>Spiritul gsete cerul; omul tot s-a prefcut<text:line-break/>ntr-o altfel de fiin, n ceva mai ideal:<text:line-break/>Trupul su parc nu simte greutatea de-animal,<text:line-break/>Parc spiritul l-ardic acolo unde e dus,<text:line-break/>i, i spiritul i omul pare c-ar tri de sus.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O, ct se nel tiranii! Ei gndesc c-au izbutit<text:line-break/>S omoare-inteligina cnd la zbiri au poruncit<text:line-break/>S opreasc przii lucrul, sau lectura sau de scris;<text:line-break/>i ce trebuie de lucru cnd tot cerul i-e deschis?<text:line-break/>Ct se amgesc cumpliii; cci se tem, cci se sfiesc<text:line-break/>S rmn cu ei nsui; pentru c ei se-ngrozesc<text:line-break/>Cnd rmn cu al lor cuget, se gndesc c-unu-i martir<text:line-break/>A s-aduc nchisoarea vreo furie sau delir! <text:line-break/>Amgire! netiin!  P-l de vrei s pedepsii<text:line-break/>Osndii-l s v vaz, num-atuncea izbutii.<text:line-break/>Cunoti, cred, destul de bine aste ore de visri<text:line-break/>Cnd n aromire omul uit asprele cercri<text:line-break/>i realitatea toat o drm ca de mal,<text:line-break/>i pe aripi d-alt lume, plan ntr-un ideal,<text:line-break/>i fantasmele aievea ce de fa ne strmut,<text:line-break/>Scene tinere, frumoase, ce n via am avut,<text:line-break/>Scumpele fiine-acelea cari odat ne-a-ncntat,<text:line-break/>Vin pe rnd, ne-aduc aminte cte-un zmbet, un oftat,<text:line-break/>Cte-o lacrim curat din izvorul clduros,<text:line-break/>Dintr-c inim fierbinte n delirul amoros,<text:line-break/>n plceri ncnttoare i uitare n amor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ori din cte daruri Domnul dete unui muritor,<text:line-break/>Suvenirea e mai dulce. O! de cte ori gustm<text:line-break/>Fiecare din plcerea ce n via-ne cercm!<text:line-break/>Pn i nenorocirea, orele cele amari,<text:line-break/>Lacrime, necazuri, grije i dureri cele mai tari,<text:line-break/>Suvenirea le-ndulcete n domenu-i, cnd le-a prins.<text:line-break/>i e mai ferice omul, mintea-i cnd le-a reatins.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Tu cunoti acele visuri ce se cerc a ne rpi<text:line-break/>P-aripe legntoare, i-i fac sil a zmbi<text:line-break/>Patimilor ce ne roade, slbiciunilor ce-avem.<text:line-break/>Dar cnd ne uitm cu totul, cnd n ceruri ne credem,<text:line-break/>Atunci rul se deteapt, vede cum c l-am uitat,<text:line-break/>i-i nfige cruda-i ghear i mai ager, mai turbat.<text:line-break/>Tocmai cnd zburam pe vise, gzii mei cnd mi uitam,<text:line-break/>Cte-o javr slut-n u-mi m fcea de trsream:<text:line-break/>ntlneam ctri de m a vre unui zbir pitic,<text:line-break/>Sau vedeam pind spre mine vrun muard paralitic.<text:line-break/>S m crezi c num-atuncea, eu, scrbit, am blestemat<text:line-break/>Pe fenicianu-acela cui n creieri a intrat<text:line-break/>S invente nite semne, ca prin ele s putem<text:line-break/>Opri sunetul vorbirii i ideea ce avem.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cea mizerie sublim naintea mea trecea<text:line-break/>i aievea a ei scene una-una mi venea:<text:line-break/>Aci Torquato Tasso brau-n fiare ncordnd,<text:line-break/>Spumega nchis n temnii a lor boite aintind:<text:line-break/>Non avendo candella per scrivere i suoi veri!</text:span><text:bookmark text:name="cite_ref-61"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_maior_Ion_Voinescu_II#cite_note-6" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T3">[6]</text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T4"><text:line-break/>Milton iar, fr vedere, l priveam cnd a vndut<text:line-break/>Pentru zece livre-sterling ast colos: Raiul pierdut;<text:line-break/>-un librar cruntat n gnduri, l vedeam cnd numra<text:line-break/>Foile nemuritoare, spre a nu se nela.<text:line-break/>Camoens, gol n spitaluri, vedeam bolnav c zcea,<text:line-break/>Primind mila de la orbul ce pentru poet cerea;<text:line-break/>-acest nobil rob dar tnr, lng patul su lipit,<text:line-break/>Sta ca cnele ce geme lng-al su stpn iubit.<text:line-break/>i Cervantes iar, n lips, stnd p-un pat de lemn mai gol,<text:line-break/>ntinznd o mn slab ctre-un rece espaniol;<text:line-break/>i Lesage, cu plete albe i de fiice nsoit,<text:line-break/>De mhnire i de boal nencetat tot chinuit,<text:line-break/>Se tra ca s-i gseasc o colib a-l umbri,<text:line-break/>Pine ca s dea soiei, cpti cnd a muri.<text:line-break/>Chiar Corneille, la care toate scenele se-nchin,<text:line-break/>Era-n lips de fiertur, dup cum ne-a spus Racine.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dryden grbov, alb de vrst, n neajungere murind,<text:line-break/>l vedeam n disperare-i cerul, stelele privind,<text:line-break/>Rtcind pe-astrologie s se poat mngia<text:line-break/>De a lumii nedreptate, ce-aa ru l preuia.<text:line-break/>De-aci iar, n Irlanda, ntlneam pe-acel Spencer<text:line-break/>Singur, fr lcuin, sprgnd ceaa-acelui cer, <text:line-break/>Rosalinda-n veci pe buze-i, capul lui de fee plin, <text:line-break/>Vai! i nici un pic de pine! Vondel, crui se nchin<text:line-break/>Olandezii, mort de foame: treisprece poei n cor<text:line-break/></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vedeam c-l duceau la groap.  Orici i-au luat un zbor,<text:line-break/>Cei mai mari, ilutri oameni, rar e cnd s-a ntmplat<text:line-break/>Cte unul ce n via-i fu de soart aprat.<text:line-break/>Vedeam dintr-un pod de cas pe Samuel-Royer, tras,<text:line-break/>Mort de frig i nemncare. Poetul lui Hudibras,<text:line-break/>Butler, mort n srcie. Floyer-Sidenham i Rushworth,<text:line-break/>ncrcai, tri n fiare. Malfiltre, i el mort<text:line-break/>De foame. Rousseau, acela, l vedeam a s-omor<text:line-break/>n ideea c-o s-ajung a ceri, a se tr.<text:line-break/>Gilbert nghiind o cheie, neavnd pistol, cuit,<text:line-break/>Moare-n podul unei case flmnd, bolnav, prsit<text:line-break/>Din cauza srciei; moare fr a gusta<text:line-break/>A vieii mulmire, i pe care o cnta<text:line-break/>Fr ca s o cunoasc. l auzeam recitind:<text:line-break/>Au banquet de la vie, infortun convive,<text:line-break/>Japparus un jour et je meurs;<text:line-break/>Je meurs, et sur la tombe o lentement jarrive,<text:line-break/>Nul ne viendra verser des pleurs.</text:span><text:bookmark text:name="cite_ref-71"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_maior_Ion_Voinescu_II#cite_note-7" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T3">[7]</text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T4"><text:line-break/>i murea pe buz-i glasul, ochii se stingeau intind.<text:line-break/>Chatterton, cnd bea otrava, l vedeam cum i rumpea,<text:line-break/>Ardea scrierile sale i-n crceie reci crnea,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Corpul su ca s se vnz, spre a se putea plti<text:line-break/>Trei ghinee, plata casei unde Bel abia-l primi.<text:line-break/>Pare c-mi era de fa:<text:line-break/>He was violent and impetous to a strange degree</text:span><text:bookmark text:name="cite_ref-8"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_maior_Ion_Voinescu_II#cite_note-8" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T3">[8]</text:span></text:a></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n minutul cnd Belfort,<text:line-break/>Ca favor, i zise slug al celui nti fecior.<text:line-break/>Vedeam mna sngeroas crudului Robespierre<text:line-break/>Artnd spre eafodul ce primea pe Chnier,<text:line-break/>i poetul blnd i dulce  sau al doilea Theocrit <text:line-break/>Strnge fruntea sa i strig, simind ora c-a venit:<text:line-break/>Mourir! et pourtant javais quelque chose l!...</text:span><text:bookmark text:name="cite_ref-9"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_maior_Ion_Voinescu_II#cite_note-9" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T3">[9]</text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T4"><text:line-break/>Pentru asta mori, srmane, pentru c aveai ceva!<text:line-break/>Ar fi fost cu mult mai bine s rmie unde-era<text:line-break/>Cea schinteie de lumin ce m face s blestem<text:line-break/>Scrisul, care ne vdete la tirani ca ce suntem.<text:line-break/>Rigas, ast Tirteu modern, al Greciei bard, profet,<text:line-break/>S sfrate-n agonie... Melancolicul poet<text:line-break/>Gaullois, pe care Hugo, spre ruine-i ne-a vestit,<text:line-break/>Autorul ntristrii -al Comediei-Lumeti,<text:line-break/>Se sfrate fr martor. Pellico, prin nchisori,<text:line-break/>D Italiei suflarea-i, cnd ea zace-n srbtori.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i n care parte-a lumii va gsi azilul lui<text:line-break/>Ast ilot etern al lumii ce nu e al nimului?<text:line-break/>Parie-n societate, kauker n particular,<text:line-break/>Se tortur de trei goane ce n-au nicidecum hotar!<text:line-break/>Tiranii se tem de dnsul i n fric-le-l strivesc,<text:line-break/>Filozoful l mepriz,</text:span><text:bookmark text:name="cite_ref-10"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_maior_Ion_Voinescu_II#cite_note-10" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T3">[10]</text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T4">speculanii l ursc.<text:line-break/>De la Omer simbol vecinic al ursitei de poet,<text:line-break/></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn-n zilele de astzi,  acest secol, ast schelet<text:line-break/>Gol i negru al icoanei unui sim material, <text:line-break/>Un poet, vrjma puterii, cum o zice i Pascal,<text:line-break/>Avu-n veci rivali vrjmaii adevrului. Gonit<text:line-break/>n tot locul de putere, fu-n tot locul biruit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i d-om arunca privirea peste timpi de la-nceput,<text:line-break/>Vom vedea un lan de chinuri printre care au trecut<text:line-break/>Ati martiri, de cnd e lumea. Temnie i sugrumri,<text:line-break/>Goana, lanul au fost plata l-ale lor cereti cntri.<text:line-break/>Precum lebda cea trist vesel e num-atunci<text:line-break/>Cnd viaa asta las, ca cum ar scpa de munci,<text:line-break/>Astfel i poetul geme: viaa lui e de dureri;<text:line-break/>Lumea-i este lui exilul, cerul este-a sale-averi.<text:line-break/>Oamenii-l gonesc n via; dup moarte, i se-nchin, <text:line-break/>Dup moarte e-a lui via,  ct triete e-ntr-un chin.<text:line-break/>Preursit martir de ceruri adevrul a cnta,<text:line-break/>A urma n sfinte misii -interesu-i a uita,<text:line-break/>El e-un simbol cu via al credinei cretineti,<text:line-break/>Las bunurile lumii ca s ia plceri cereti;<text:line-break/>Parc dincolo de lume ar fi viaa ce-a lsat;<text:line-break/>Parc-ast loc e o osnd pentru vre un vechi pcat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O, Platon! pricep prea bine pe poet de ce-ai gonit<text:line-break/>Din republica aceea care i-ai nchipuit!<text:line-break/>Cred prea bine c poetul e un spirit, e un vis<text:line-break/>Rtcit din vre o sfer, sau i ntradins trimis<text:line-break/>S imite Creatoru-i. Fr-a da vre un alt spor,<text:line-break/>Se hrnete din ptulul care-i umple un popor.<text:line-break/>Cnd i va pieri modelul, n-are-atunci ce copia;<text:line-break/>Cnd ambarul i s-o-nchide, nu mai are ce mnca.<text:line-break/>El s-aseamn prea bine paserilor care vin<text:line-break/>Ca s ne dezmierde numai printr-un viers, care se-nchin<text:line-break/>Celui care le trimite: ele-i cnt n vocea lor,<text:line-break/>Se nutresc n vreo livede -a lucra deloc nu vor;<text:line-break/>Nu vor, pentru c nu tie: ele fac ce-au nvat,<text:line-break/>Ceea ce le-a-nvat Domnul cnd aicea le-a-ndreptat.<text:line-break/>Tu nu faci privighetoarea ca s cnte cum vei tu,<text:line-break/>Nici o bufni s-i lase vocea-n care ncepu.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Oare barza care vine pe-a ta cas a cuiba,<text:line-break/>Nu-i pltete destul, Platon, preajma-i cnd va cura<text:line-break/>De juvini? -a da exemplu de via la ai ti? <text:line-break/>Barza-i ciocnete erpii, i poetul pe cei ri.<text:line-break/>Cnd o rnduric vine s-i zideasc cuibul su<text:line-break/>Pe sub straini sau n preajma largului palat al tu,<text:line-break/>Nu-i pltete i ea oar cnd la geam i va veni<text:line-break/>S leine cntnd ziua, dimineaa a-i vesti?<text:line-break/>Fiece poet aicea are misiunea sa;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Fiecare i-o-mplinete; ncetai a disputa!<text:line-break/>Tasso de Montaigne se rumpe i tu sfii pe Omer;<text:line-break/>Pascal toat poezia, i Saint-Just pre Chenier. <text:line-break/>Filozofi! gndii mai bine! i chiar voi suntei poei;<text:line-break/>V numii precum v place, ns nu tii ce suntei.<text:line-break/>Lumea este poezie, ca i Politia ta;<text:line-break/>Osebirea-i c poetul se exprim-n limba sa,<text:line-break/>ntr-o limb de magie care ngeri o vorbesc;<text:line-break/>Oamenii de ea se-ncnt, fiarele se mblnzesc;<text:line-break/>Limba-n care toi profeii au vorbit cu Dumnezeu:<text:line-break/>Limba care da eroii prin organul lui Tirteu;<text:line-break/>Care reformeaz cerul, care lunii a reformat,<text:line-break/>Care-a liberat popoare, ceruri mii a populat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar, mai de cnd e lumea, un poet nu fu pltit;<text:line-break/>ns, ori n ce epoc a fost mult mai mulumit<text:line-break/>De pe ct vedem acuma: nainte mergtor<text:line-break/>Artelor celor frumoase i de cult nscocitor,<text:line-break/>Pe cnd lumea era jun, pe cnd anima domnea,<text:line-break/>El, ce-n ideal i-e viaa, ntlnea orice dorea;<text:line-break/>Dar cnd inim-amorete i cnd capul face tot,<text:line-break/>Cnd principiu-i interesul, a tri poei nu pot.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">D-om vrea s lum vechimea, cnd materia domnea,<text:line-break/>Cnd simualismul singur chiar virtuii poruncea;<text:line-break/>Cnd virtutea se da lesne unui bun luptaci vrtos,<text:line-break/>Unei frumusei vzute -unui corp mai mldios,<text:line-break/>Cnd Io sau cnd elenii, armii, naii pustiind,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Da n Elisei eroii pe care-i vedea murind;<text:line-break/>Cnd eroii chema zeii, ca s bea din cupa lor,<text:line-break/>Zeii coborau din ceruri ca s dea al lor favor<text:line-break/>Rpitorilor de fiice i de case sprgtori;<text:line-break/>Cnd un Mar, o Vineri, Bachus erau mari crmuitori,<text:line-break/>i Amfion, Anacreon crnurile cnd cntau;<text:line-break/>Aspasia, Cleopatra, pe brbai cnd ncntau,<text:line-break/>Sardanapali, Luculi, Neroni, ati regi, ati cezari,<text:line-break/>nsemnar-acele epoce de plceri fr hotar; </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n acel amestec mare de plceri n pipiri,<text:line-break/>n acel contrast gigantic de virtui i rtciri,<text:line-break/>n varietate-aceea, un poet ntmpina<text:line-break/>Un Olimp ca s-l inspire, un ilot a-l ntrista,<text:line-break/>O cunun s-l nale, sculptor a-l eterniza,<text:line-break/>O Frine ca s-l nvie -o Lucre a stima,<text:line-break/>Olimpice s-l asculte i un stad a mai scurta,<text:line-break/>Discoboli s ntreasc -un atlet a-ncuraja,<text:line-break/>Circul fumegnd de snge, irul tigrilor turbai,<text:line-break/>-un Cezar, turbnd de poft, privind robii sfiai.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i n secolii de mijloc, timpi morali i sufleteti,<text:line-break/>Ast epoc ntins de virtui moraliceti,<text:line-break/>Cnd blndeea, caritatea,  aste fiice-a lui Cristos, <text:line-break/>Cldeau numai pe Speran, acest cult aa frumos:<text:line-break/>Cnd un Atanase vine, un Ioan, un Augustin,<text:line-break/>Idealiznd virtutea ntr-un nume de Cretin;<text:line-break/>Cnd cu crucea se armeaz Europa-n Saint-Bernard<text:line-break/>i valuri pornesc de oaste sub Philippe i sub Richard;<text:line-break/>Cnd Saint-Louis e pe scen; cnd Guesclinii se iveau;<text:line-break/>Cnd truverii, trubadurii armiile crmuiau;<text:line-break/>Cnd cavalerismul strig n Roland i n Bayard;<text:line-break/>Armele lucesc i sun pe un maur sau lombard;<text:line-break/>Cnd materia-i d spiritul prin strivirea lui Pascal<text:line-break/>i martirul triumfeaz, Cristos nu are rival;<text:line-break/>Pe cnd simul amorise, cnd comand Bossuet,<text:line-break/>Cnd se reformeaz Cerul,  n faa unui poet<text:line-break/>Vin icoanele grmad i se simte inspirat.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Acum Dante, Milton, Tasso nu e lucru de mirat;<text:line-break/>Atalia i Estera, i Tancred i Polyecte.<text:line-break/>Vin, rsar, se nasc de sine ca s fie subiect.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n epoca noastr ns, nceput de Voltaire,<text:line-break/>Spiritualismul cade, se ngn-orice mister:<text:line-break/>O crepuscul! dar care?  Tlmcii-o dup plac;<text:line-break/>ntrebai pe sectatorii ai lui Smith, Condillac;<text:line-break/>Cci acuma este vorba ca s fii folositor,<text:line-break/>S-nlesneti nedomirirea, i-n ctig nscocitor.<text:line-break/>O, poet! Vino! Ia-i harpa! Vino a te inspira<text:line-break/>De machina care-o face oarecii a se mica!<text:line-break/>Pune-mi algebra n versuri! Cnt-mi un manufactor<text:line-break/>Ce iei falit asear! Spune-mi ce-a rmas dator!<text:line-break/>Las circ -anahoreii, turnuri, lupte i asprimi.<text:line-break/>Las tot entuziasmul din barbarele vechimi;<text:line-break/>Las-onoarea i credina! Vino ici a-mi calcula:<text:line-break/>Acia-mi n care parte e mai bine a bga?<text:line-break/>Las pe tiran s-alerge i pe rob a suferi;<text:line-break/>Las vduva s geam -orfelinul a muri;<text:line-break/>Las s se lupte-n aer Jupiter i cu Titan;<text:line-break/>Las sfinii s se roage la Cristos sau la Satan. <text:line-break/>Vino ici de-mi spune mie, cum a face s ctig<text:line-break/>Dou sute la o sut, fr fric s m frig.<text:line-break/>Spune-mi ce societate poate a-mi asigura<text:line-break/>Un venit pe toat viaa  i ct am a numra?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O! vrst btrn-a lumii! Secol rece, amorit!<text:line-break/>Anticrist, fr-ndoial, e de mult aci venit!<text:line-break/>Pe cnd magi, brahmini, cabirii, consfiniii demagogi<text:line-break/>Invitau -oprea poporul luminaii astrologi;<text:line-break/>Cnd profeii fa-n fa sftuia cu Iehova;<text:line-break/>Cnd i vile i munii l-al lor semn se despica<text:line-break/>i plecau pe nori cu corpul nzeiii pelerini, <text:line-break/>n epocile acelea d-antici faraoni divini,<text:line-break/>Un pontif i lsa sceptrul ca s cnte psalmii si,<text:line-break/>S-i confese-a sale crime, s blesteme pe cei ri.<text:line-break/>Cnd ncununai cu dafini Pindarii se prembla<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Prin Olimpicele lupte, ode, imnuri a cnta;<text:line-break/>i Filipii, Hieronii se dau jos din tronul lor<text:line-break/>S se lupte cu atleii din poporul privitor;<text:line-break/>Cnd n Panteon artitii faptele lor expunea,<text:line-break/>Zeuxis nvia lemne prin elenii ce vorbea;<text:line-break/>Cnd Fidias zeitatea ntr-un Joe cobora,<text:line-break/>Praxitel mplnta graii ntr-o piatr ce spa,<text:line-break/>Un poet se-nclzea lesne admirnd un Partenon,<text:line-break/>Admirnd vre o coloan-nlat de Hersifron,<text:line-break/>Un ntins amfiteatru, sau ospul strlucit,<text:line-break/>Srbtorile vestite, sacrificiul de-ngrozit,<text:line-break/>Acel lux att de mare de femei, de sclavi, de zei,<text:line-break/>Adunrile armate ce-i ncununa pe ei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n secuii de mijloc iar, seculii cei cretineti,<text:line-break/>Seculii de meditare -ai virtuilor cereti,<text:line-break/>Cnd Cristos desfiineaz mrimea de pe pmnt,<text:line-break/>Poeii, n loc de muz, priimesc spiritul snt,<text:line-break/>Las plcerea simual; sunt de ngeri privitori;<text:line-break/>i las lira i iau harpa,  sunt n cer locuitori.<text:line-break/>Eliseii i Parnasul se prefac n Paradis;<text:line-break/>Olimpul se pustiaz, cerul tot rmne vis,<text:line-break/>Unde rtcesc poeii.  O! ce mult a favorat<text:line-break/>Poezia cretinismul! alt epoc n-a dat<text:line-break/>Orizont att de mare spiritului poeticesc,<text:line-break/>Dect, cnd a aflat omul c e cetean ceresc,<text:line-break/>C ast loc e de cercare; nu e mare, nu e mic<text:line-break/>naintea-Eternitii, c viaa e-n cer; nimic<text:line-break/>Din ce-avem aicea nu putem lua cu noi,<text:line-break/>Cum c numai Caritatea va-ndulci viaa d-apoi.<text:line-break/>Cu ct geograful nostru poate fi mai nvat<text:line-break/>De<text:span text:style-name="T15">-</text:span>acela al vechimii; cu ct a naintat<text:line-break/>ntre noi astronomia, cu att i Dant i Tass,<text:line-break/>D-om privi mai de aproape, putena zice cum c-au tras<text:line-break/>Mult mai nalt i poezia dect Qmer i Virgil,<text:line-break/>Cum Racine dect Sofoclu, Corneille de Eshil,<text:line-break/>-ati ali ce n-au protivnici nici ntr-un alt period;<text:line-break/>Shakespeare de Euripidis i Milton de Esiod.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Dar ce-ar fi putut s fac d-ar fi fost cretin Omer;<text:line-break/>Ce-ar fi fost un Rai n mn-i, cnd s-ar fi vzut n cer</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ce-ar fi fost Ierusalimul, armia de cruciai<text:line-break/>Ce se vars-n alte clime, pe jos, prin cruce armai;<text:line-break/>Oceanele de lume, ce deert un continent,<text:line-break/>Bei d-un snt entuziasm, aprini toi d-un simtiment,<text:line-break/>Trec pe mri, pe muni, nisipuri, ca i pe cmpii cu flori,<text:line-break/>Uit i foame i odihn i se las, ca nite nori<text:line-break/>P-un pmnt de alt lege,  ast sujet e gigantesc;<text:line-break/>Ce-ar fi fost, tratat de Omer, ci or spune se greesc.<text:line-break/>Acum ns cnd rzboiul e de interes silit<text:line-break/>i cnd orice-osta ntr-nsul este-un salahor pltit;<text:line-break/>Cnd orice entuziasmuri ainteaz tot la bani;<text:line-break/>Cnd orice mister n lume nu mai are-ai si profani;<text:line-break/>Cnd bani sunt toat plcerea; bani credina; bani amor;<text:line-break/>Cnd patriotisimu-i bani; cnd pe bani neamuri s-omor;<text:line-break/>Cnd muzele i pierd cerul; cnd Apolo s-a surpat;<text:line-break/>Cnd nu se sfinesc poeii i profeii a-ncetat;<text:line-break/>Cnd poetul sau pictorul, arhitectul sau sculptor<text:line-break/>E silit a-i tocmi ziua ca cel mai prost muncitor;<text:line-break/>Cnd pictorul ntre ngeri a-ncetat a se numi, <text:line-break/>n timpii cei ri de astzi anevoie a gsi<text:line-break/>Un Omer sau un Apolon; un Tasso sau on Bramand,<text:line-break/>Un Dante sau un Tibardi; un Milton sau un Dorland.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Trist soart-a poeziei, ce Gilbert a preludat<text:line-break/>Pe cnd ncepea epoca-n care Voltaire ne-a bgat:<text:line-break/>Malheureux qui se voue aux nymphes du Pamasse,<text:line-break/>Sil ne possde pour richesse<text:line-break/>Quun grand coeur et son Apollon!</text:span><text:bookmark text:name="cite_ref-111"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_maior_Ion_Voinescu_II#cite_note-11" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T3">[11]</text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T4"><text:line-break/>Prea lungii ast scrisoare. Vrnd s-i spun ce am pit<text:line-break/>Din cauza ciocoimii; vrnd s-i spun c-s surghiunit<text:line-break/>n Camtceatka Rumniei, ntr-o hord d-otentoi,<text:line-break/>ntr-o capite druid unde cer s vezi nu poi,<text:line-break/>-unde Teutates s-aude prin copaci btrni zbiernd,<text:line-break/>Primind ritul cel de groaz de la erimii turbnd,<text:line-break/>Unde oameni pitagorici zac pe tabernaculi bei,<text:line-break/>Unde oimul i vulturul se scald vara n nemei,<text:line-break/>M-apucai s-i fac pomelnic de poei ce-au rposat<text:line-break/>i s-i spun attea lucruri ce-n pustie am visat. <text:line-break/>Vezi! m scap de satirici; cci Alexandrescu, crez,<text:line-break/></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-o scorni ca lui Apolon: c-nchiz ochii i visez.<text:line-break/>Dar, de vrei s-i spun -aievea aci-n exil ce gndesc,<text:line-break/>Gndesc la epoc-aceea care n-o s-o mai gsesc:<text:line-break/>La amicia cea franc cnd erai nensurat,<text:line-break/>La acele lungi libaii din frumosul celibat,<text:line-break/>n care entuziasmul mai pe toi ne ilectra<text:line-break/>i urrile-aveau farmec n acei ce le-asculta.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="Note6"/>Note</text:h>
   <text:list xml:id="list254119595" text:style-name="L1">
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P26"><text:bookmark text:name="cite_note-16"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_maior_Ion_Voinescu_II#cite_ref-1" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T2"></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu este bine ca un monarh s stpneasc mulimea.</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P27"><text:bookmark text:name="cite_note-25"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_maior_Ion_Voinescu_II#cite_ref-2" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T2"></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se afl n Fanar un arhonta numit Luca, de neam cobortor din cer. Bogat, are maldre de aciuni n inuturi mari i vestite, puse la adpost. Dup ce a adunat comorile lui Cresus, n fanariotul Pera, dincolo de Dunre, acolo unde aurul nglbenete obrazul hedonitilor ca sulful, s-a ntors n sfrit, putred de bogat, la Fanar i la voluptate, ca Lucullus al strvechilor romani. Purta haine felurite dimineaa i seara. Avea cciuli nenumrate, lucitoare, mari i, plimbndu-se mereu prin grdina lui Tomazos, era urmat de servitor cu un bra de ciubuce.</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P27"><text:bookmark text:name="cite_note-33"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_maior_Ion_Voinescu_II#cite_ref-3" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T2"></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Niciodat nu s-a ntmplat s mi se nfierbnte ntr-atta sngele  nici chiar atunci cnd Fotie mi-a adresat n scris njositorul cuvnt srac de tot, n loc de prea fericit, i nici chiar atunci cnd fostul stpn al Elasanei m-a pomenit, pe mine postelnicul, dup Gheorgachi; pe mine, boier mare, dup un boierna.</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
