    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P27"><text:bookmark text:name="cite_note-61"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_maior_Ion_Voinescu_II#cite_ref-6" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T2"></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Neavnd lumnare pentru a-i scrie versurile.</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P27"><text:bookmark text:name="cite_note-71"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_maior_Ion_Voinescu_II#cite_ref-7" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T2"></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">:La ospul vieii, nefericit conviv,<text:line-break/>M-am artat o singur zi i mor;<text:line-break/>Mor, i pe mormntul la dare-ajung cu-ncetul,<text:line-break/>Nimeni nu va veni s verse lacrimi.</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
