    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P27"><text:bookmark text:name="cite_note-111"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_maior_Ion_Voinescu_II#cite_ref-11" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T2"></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">:Nefericit acela ce se ncredineaz nimfelor Parnasului,<text:line-break/>Dac nu are alt avuie<text:line-break/>Dect o inim mare i pe al su Apolon!</text:span></text:p>
