   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>La muza mea </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Bucureti, 1847, noiembrie 15</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnt, o, Muz! Cnt, o, Muza mea cretin?<text:line-break/>Pe antihriti, pe impii</text:span><text:bookmark text:name="cite_ref-13"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_muza_mea#cite_note-1" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T3">[1]</text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T4">pe omul ce suspin<text:line-break/>i cheam-a te-asculta.<text:line-break/>Pe coardele-i sonore vibreze Libertatea,<text:line-break/>i toat armonia s-i fie Egalitatea,<text:line-break/>i mila fie-i legea, i Pacea inta ta.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Prostituate muze le du la pietate;<text:line-break/>Lucete ntre ele i d-le demnitate,<text:line-break/>Delirul de profet.<text:line-break/>Societatea geme,  i psul omenimei,<text:line-break/>Durerea de confrate, ntmpinul cruzimei<text:line-break/>E misia prescris Cretinului-Poet.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aci s stai, o, Muz! d-aci te aripeaz,<text:line-break/>D-aci s dai semnalul; -adun,-mpreuneaz<text:line-break/>Erantele</text:span><text:bookmark text:name="cite_ref-25"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_muza_mea#cite_note-2" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T3">[2]</text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T4">schintei!<text:line-break/>O facl f din ele, o facl de lumin;<text:line-break/>nal preste lume acea lumin lin,<text:line-break/>Recheam-n datorie modernii Prometei.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n dezunirea noastr, ntoan, Muz, glasu-i!<text:line-break/>ntinde armonia pe unde trece pasu-i,<text:line-break/>i f a asculta<text:line-break/>i sclavul i despotul, i slabul i cel tare,<text:line-break/>Motivul nfrirei n toat-a ta cntare,<text:line-break/>Anuniind pre Domnul ce vine-n urma ta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Bogatului, ce strnge cu mult lcomie<text:line-break/>Semnturi, cireade ce-neac-a sa cmpie,<text:line-break/>Grnare pmnteti,<text:line-break/>i spune c tot spicul, cu care miluiete<text:line-break/>Pe un srac ce plnge, rodete, se-nsutete<text:line-break/>n cmpuri empiree, n holdele cereti.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Sracilor zi iar: Pe ast pmnt voi trecei;<text:line-break/>V poart grija Domnul, i ct aci petrecei<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Voi credei i rbdai.<text:line-break/>Nu pizmuii bogatul ce seamn i strnge<text:line-break/>Rznd de munca voastr, rznd de cel ce plnge<text:line-break/>Iertai-l voi pre dnsul i-l binecuvntai.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu ncrirea urei nu v-ndoii mihnirea;<text:line-break/>i la durerea voastr n-adogai cirea<text:line-break/>Ce vine dup ru.<text:line-break/>Unii-v n Domnul, sfinii-v cu mila;<text:line-break/>Sracul n iubire i uureaz sila, <text:line-break/>Ea-i rcorete mintea i-ndur corpul su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Unirea-mbrbteaz, Unirea mntuiete,<text:line-break/>i mila, i amorul, popoarele-nfrete, <text:line-break/>V ajutai! Iertai!<text:line-break/>Iertai i pe bogatul orbit de lcomie,<text:line-break/>Iertai i pe tiranul turbat d-a sa mnie,<text:line-break/>Vegheai, pndii minutul i nu v spimntai.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Combate, Muz sacr, combate egoismul<text:line-break/>Care viclean s-ascunde i ia patriotismul,<text:line-break/>Ia nume de cretin<text:line-break/>S poat s-amgeasc. Te du fr sfial<text:line-break/>La cei ce stau pe tronuri, le spune c se-nal<text:line-break/>Cci unul este Domnul, i frai ci i se-nchin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Fii mndr n tot timpul i cnt n tot locul.<text:line-break/>Pe unde auzi plngeri i crunt este norocul,<text:line-break/>Te-oprete consolnd;<text:line-break/>i orice chin, durere, i orice apsare<text:line-break/>mpac i alin cu sacra ta cntare;<text:line-break/>Depune tu sperana n omul suspinnd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Amenin, inspir pe cei ce ne fac lege;<text:line-break/>ntmpin cu trsnet o mn sacrilege<text:line-break/>Friei omeneti.<text:line-break/>i poezia toat, gndirile-nzeite,<text:line-break/>Pe care Provedina nencetat trimite,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Misionari de pace, misionari cereti,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Adun mpregiuru-i; alai</text:span><text:bookmark text:name="cite_ref-34"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_muza_mea#cite_note-3" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T3">[3]</text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T4">un mpreun,</text:span><text:bookmark text:name="cite_ref-43"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_muza_mea#cite_note-4" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T3">[4]</text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T4"><text:line-break/>Un imn la Mntuire, ca o vestire bun<text:line-break/>C vine Dumnezeu.<text:line-break/>A doua Lui venire d-aproape ne sosete:<text:line-break/>Profei! prelude harpa; cci iat-l se ivete<text:line-break/>i Rul se ascunde la glasul Lui cel greu.</text:span></text:p>
