    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P29"><text:bookmark text:name="cite_note-34"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_muza_mea#cite_ref-3" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T2"></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">ala  a nla.</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P29"><text:bookmark text:name="cite_note-43"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_muza_mea#cite_ref-4" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T2"></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">acord armonic (dup fr. ensemble).</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
   </text:list>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">La prinesa C. Trubetzcoi </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Bicoi, 1844, septembrie</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Castelul se gtete, prines generoas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Srbarea-i nominal n salve-a saluta,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i bardul ce se-nspir la faa-i graioas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ton a sa harp i cere-a preluda.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">D-i voie, castelan, vasalii s-i adune,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i coardele-i sonoare, ce ru i le-a-ntinat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu ei aci s imne i-n preajm s rsune</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Recunotina mare ce-n ei i-ai meritat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Orfanii vezi-i grupe, cci cer ca la o mum,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i grbovii mai colo pe care ocroteti,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu vduve, sracii ce relele consum,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aduc n hor tributul i rog ca s-l priimeti.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iubit-n capital i-n cercuri adorat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin spirit i tiin n toate tii domni!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Clcaii i se-nchin cu inim curat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i bardul privegheaz cununi a-i mpleti.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci e o norocire eroul i femeia</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd afl pe poetul veghind n giurul lor</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A ilustra o fapt, a le opri ideea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A o para cu dafini s mearg-n viitor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Venii, clcai! dai roat l-a salvelor vlvoare l</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Strigai ct strig harpa-mi: ura la ast pahar!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Triasc Cleopatra, a Romniei floare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Triasc, adorat de voi i de Cezar!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">La Romnia </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Paris, 15 avrilie 1856</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="P25" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I7"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Deteapt-i, Romnie, orgoliul strbun,<text:line-break/>C iat sun ora, i geniul cel bun<text:line-break/>S mbie nceput-a pe tot pmntul tu.<text:line-break/>Danubu-i rupe vlu i jugul su cel greu:<text:line-break/>n Euxin rsufl ca un imens izvor,<text:line-break/>Cu patru brae lupt s-ajung la Bosfor.<text:line-break/>i pe Carpai s-ardic btrnul Uria<text:line-break/>Ce doarme, de sunt secoli, pe vechiul su lca.<text:line-break/>E geniul Daciei, e zeul tutelar<text:line-break/>Ce, din ruine-afunde, al Daciei hotar<text:line-break/>Se scoal s msoare c-un milion de pai;</text:span><text:bookmark text:name="cite_ref-14"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_Romnia_(Bolliac)#cite_note-1" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T3">[1]</text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T4"><text:line-break/>S vaz de curg fluvii p-antideluvi fgai,<text:line-break/>Eterne santinele, menii a ocoli<text:line-break/>Titanii muni Bastarnici, Mar unde se ivi<text:line-break/>Pentru ntia oar. Acvila, tresrind,<text:line-break/>Vede pe Soare-Mithra c-i cat surznd...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II7"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Oprete, Soare-Mithra! Aci fu templu tu<text:line-break/>Cel mare i teribil, i Cocheonul greu,<text:line-break/>i zarabii-tereii, i dacii pileai,<text:line-break/>Discipolii lui Zamolx,pioii si jurai!...<text:line-break/>Privete aste fee prlite de dureri,<text:line-break/>Acoperind cu trene slbite mdulri,<text:line-break/></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ieind de prin bordeie afunde n pmnt<text:line-break/>Ca fiarele slbateci! Rostete un cuvnt;<text:line-break/>Numete-le strbunii: pe Decebal, Traian,<text:line-break/>Ion Aan, Buril, Corvin, Mihai, tefan;<text:line-break/>Zi vorba: Libertate! ctnd n faa lor,<text:line-break/>i vei vedea ndat pe Marele Popor!<text:line-break/>Vei recunoate, Soare, daca romnii vin<text:line-break/>Din fiicele lui Zamolx i fiii lui Cuirin;<text:line-break/>De e poporu-acela ce pe Danub jura,<text:line-break/>Pornind la btlie: De nu va triumfa,<text:line-break/>S nu-i mai vaz ara!</text:span><text:bookmark text:name="cite_ref-26"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_Romnia_(Bolliac)#cite_note-2" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T3">[2]</text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vezi de poi semui<text:line-break/>Aste mree fee, ce rul chinui,<text:line-break/>Cu-i de btu pe Ciru, Darie, Lisimac,<text:line-break/>Pe Filip -Alexandru; privete-i de se trag<text:line-break/>Din Dromihet i Sarmis, din Decebal cel brav,<text:line-break/>Teribil Romii, care, dect a cdea sclav,<text:line-break/>Bu cu cupa plin veninul pregtit.<text:line-break/>O! nu, nu zice, Soare, c dacii au pierit!...<text:line-break/>Mai lung veselie nu s-a srbat n veci<text:line-break/>Ca la concuista dac: O sut douzeci<text:line-break/>i trei de zile Roma, n jocuri, srbtori,<text:line-break/>Zecimi de mii da morii, alei gladiatori,<text:line-break/>i fiare diferite la unsprezece mii.<text:line-break/>Att erau de groaznici ai lui Zamolxe fii!<text:line-break/>Ei se-nfrir numai cu-ai lumii stpni,<text:line-break/>i dacii i romanii nscur pe romni.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="III4"/>III</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Nepieritoare gint ce i-a apropiat<text:line-break/>Ce-avu mai mare-n sine Poporul mprat<text:line-break/>i dacul cel teribil care nu se temea<text:line-break/>D-alt dect numai cerul pe el de va cdea.<text:line-break/>Neam care niciodat nu lsa un moment<text:line-break/>Fr-a lupta s fie liber, independent.<text:line-break/>Btu attea ginte, ce a le numra<text:line-break/>S-ar osteni i mintea a mai le recita.<text:line-break/>Ori cnd i ori cu cine romnul se btu,<text:line-break/>Pe cnd era el liber, ruinea nu avu.<text:line-break/>D-ajunse, prin sistemul unei uori robii,<text:line-break/>S-i uite existena, tradiiile vii<text:line-break/>Ce cresc n generaii prin multe recitri<text:line-break/>i ne transmit torente a bunilor puteri,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Fcnd eroi prinii, strbunii uriai,<text:line-break/>Care, plantai pe ceruri, privesc ai notri pai<text:line-break/>i in n veci poporul, mpins d-al su trecut,<text:line-break/>S frunte viitorul; d-ajunse ast popor<text:line-break/>Prin lunga jefuire, prin lips, chinuiri,<text:line-break/>Vicleana dezarmare -attea njosiri<text:line-break/>Fcute chiar d-aceia ce-odat-l invita;<text:line-break/>D-ajunse-n ast stare, Soare, nu te mira:<text:line-break/>Adesea, un nor numai n fa-i s-a ivit<text:line-break/>i toat-a ta splendoare se pare c-a pierit.<text:line-break/>-au fost i timpi d-aceia, cnd iarna greu grina,<text:line-break/>n care-uitase lumea chiar existena ta.<text:line-break/>Tu ns eti acelai, i acuilonii trec,<text:line-break/>Azurul te arat i vieile se-ntrec,<text:line-break/>Din planta submarin i pn la erou,<text:line-break/>S vie s admire splendoarea ta din nou.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="IV2"/>IV</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Fatal fuse ziua n care pronun<text:line-break/>Mihai acest servagiu i-n el i ngrop<text:line-break/>i neamul i pmntul, i-ntinse negrul vl<text:line-break/>Pe toat Romnia! D-atunci acest Babei<text:line-break/>De ginile barbare i umilina grea,<text:line-break/>i nepsarea crud i ciocoimea rea.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="V1"/>V</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ca floare neumbrit sub cerul arztor,<text:line-break/>Femeie nenclzit de tnrul amor,<text:line-break/>Copii pe care muma deloc n-a mngiat,<text:line-break/>Aa poporul care trecutul i-a uitat<text:line-break/>Se uit mprejuru-i i vede tot strin,<text:line-break/>i pierde contiina i se ndur-n chin;<text:line-break/>C-n lips de iubire i-n veci n traiul ru,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Omul devine fiar, uitnd i Dumnezeu,<text:line-break/>i ar, i familii, uitnd i chiar pe el.<text:line-break/>Uitarea-i netiin; netiind nu poi iubi,<text:line-break/>i neiubind nu aperi; nu te-aperi, nu vei fi.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="VI"/>VI</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De la Mihai ncoace n darn ai luminat<text:line-break/>Mree Soare, ara! n darn ai revrsat<text:line-break/>A ta cldur dulce p-ast roditor pmnt!<text:line-break/>Se vietau prinii, clipeau cte-un moment,<text:line-break/>Dar demonul urgiei cerul de tot bloca<text:line-break/>i rul, n largi unde, pe patrie vrsa.<text:line-break/>Manaful fr fric se npustea turbat,<text:line-break/>Neamul, vrjmaul Romei, de foame leinat,<text:line-break/>Grec, aru anticristul rupea, nepedepsii,<text:line-break/>i ar -individe, de liberti lipsii.<text:line-break/>Pe sclav n jefuire lesne l poi mna.<text:line-break/>S prade i s-omoare, dar ns-a apra<text:line-break/>Onoarea lui i ara, un sclav nu va putea;<text:line-break/>i sclav era romnul cnd altu l btea.<text:line-break/>Bunul fugea din ar; i fiii ei, rebeli,<text:line-break/>i speculau onoarea la peitori vicleni.<text:line-break/>Sunt timpi cnd nu mai poate nici chiar Mihai cel Brav!<text:line-break/>Cci Patrie nu este unde poporu-i sclav!<text:line-break/>Dar vine o idee ce popolii adopt,<text:line-break/>Un Lazr i un Tudor, un patruzeci i opt<text:line-break/>Lucete ca un fulger n neamul adormit,<text:line-break/>Deteapt letargia, i iat-l mntuit.<text:line-break/>Idolul ce pierise, Patria, e pe cer;<text:line-break/>i cultul ei, n inimi, printr-un divin mister,<text:line-break/>Revars n torente credin i amor,<text:line-break/>Din ceptici vin fanatici; pentru ea se omor.<text:line-break/>Zambila deodat o vezi a nvoita<text:line-break/>Cnd raza ta cea dulce spre dnsa va cta.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="VII"/><text:soft-page-break/>VII</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O, ct eti de frumoas i jun, ara mea!<text:line-break/>Brunet prsit ce rul chinuia!<text:line-break/>O, ranele de fiare i sunt de tot adnci:<text:line-break/>Te-au chinuit cumpliii pe ct ai fost pe brnci!<text:line-break/>Dar Francia, Englitera, Sardinia s-au prins<text:line-break/>S-i dea rpit stem. Un fulger din Paris<text:line-break/>A spart a tale temnii. Acum, c te-au gsit,<text:line-break/>Te recunosc de sor, uitnd ce-ai suferit.<text:line-break/>Te scoal n picioare, vorbete-n glasul tu,<text:line-break/>Vorbete fr team c-ascult Dumnezeu!<text:line-break/>Aint-i i-i nghea daca-i mai vin lingi,<text:line-break/>Mravi fr onoare, ceva pltii cli<text:line-break/>i-or vrea s-i cear mna pe care au trdat.<text:line-break/>Fiica Romii ori ia popol, ori va snge de-mprat.<text:line-break/>Zestrea ei acum e mare, stema i s-a legiuit,<text:line-break/>Fiii ei acum sunt liberi, braele s-au nmulit.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="VIII"/>VIII</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Punei apte zctoare de Cotnar i Drgani<text:line-break/>i ntindei mas lung pe prul din Focani!<text:line-break/>Punei Acvila i Uru lng lancea lui Cuirin,<text:line-break/>Mar i Ceres ne protege! Umplei cupele ou vin!<text:line-break/>Fie una Romnia-i tot fiul ei romn!!!<text:line-break/>Prini latini! Regina jun va un so, nu un stpn</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="Note8"/>Note</text:h>
   <text:list xml:id="list3903573313" text:style-name="L3">
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P30"><text:bookmark text:name="cite_note-18"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_Romnia_(Bolliac)#cite_ref-1" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T2"></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eutrop., Breviarium historiae Romanae, lib. VIII,  II  Sextus Rufus, Breviarium de victoriis et provinciis, VIII (n.a.).</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:bookmark text:name="cite_note-27"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/La_Romnia_(Bolliac)#cite_ref-2" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T2"></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Junius  Philargyrius, Georg., II (n.a.)</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
   </text:list>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>La un copil</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un copil, odat, mic ca domnia-ta,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-i iubea prinii i i asculta,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd i zise tatsu s mearg la coal,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El plec, ndat, dar cu mna goal.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unde-i este cartea? Ce te nebuneti?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dascalu-o s-ntrebe: pe ce-i s citeti?...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bieelul, lene, se tot scrpina,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se-nvrtea prin cas, nu-t ce tot cta.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar n sfrit pleac cu inima rea, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Plngea, srcuul;  cartea-i prea grea!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mergnd el alene, cu capu-ntr-o parte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cscnd pe sus gura, i cade-a sa carte;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un cioban o vede i-ndat-o i ia.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El i zice: Ia-o, s m scap de ea!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu voi s-nv carte; voi s fiu cioban,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Orice-ar fi mai lesne, mcar i igan!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar de ce, copile? ce vorbeti aa?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i zice ciobanul, dndu-i cartea sa.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci nu tiu eu carte! ce bine ar fi!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acum a fi altfel! altor n-a servi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Silete, copile, carte a-nva,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci, cnd vei fi mare, tu te-i bucura.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Om, cal, chiar furnica, cte fiini sunt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Toate fac o treab aici pe pmnt;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cine st din lucru numaidect piere;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Viermii fac mtase; albinele, miere;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cinii pzesc turme; oile ne-mbrac:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Omul dar se cade i mai mult s fac;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i, fr-a ti carte, omu-i dobitoc;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Toate-nainteaz i el st pe loc. </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe igani, vzut-ai, cum altu-i muncete?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe rani, sracii, cum i biciuiete?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">tii cauza ce e, de au ast parte?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci sunt orbi, srmanii, i cci nu tiu carte!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce fcu copilul, ce se socoti,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Strnse cartea bine, la coal porni;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu mai fuse lene, dascalu-l iubea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-ntr-un an de zile  scria i citea.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>La C*** </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu dulcea-i poezie, ca tine de frumoas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Srut acum hrtia pe care-a odihnit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O mn pnditoare de rim-armonioas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i care d sperana n sufletu-mi mhnit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ferice de acela ce poate s te vaz,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd rzi i cnd eti trist, deteapt i cnd dormi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Asupra lui s-atepte acea cereasc raz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce scap pntre pleop-i, cnd gata eti s-adormi!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ferice de acela ce poate s te-auz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Scond un glas de nger, ce pn-n cer l sui,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n via ta simire, ce faa-i va s-ascunz,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S poat nelege c scapi numele lui!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ferice de acela ce poate s respire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Etern acelai aer pe care tu l scoi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-etern tot la picioare-i, s poat s-i inspire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acea comptimire ce tu depui n toi!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ferice de acela ce va putea vrodat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-aprinz a ta verv a ne mai da un rnd</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De dulce poezie, d-o rim-aa bogat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">D-idei aa sublime p-acelai stil curgnd!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">La *** </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De unde vii, siren, aproape d-aste locuri?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eti fiic tu a mrii? din spum te-ai nscut?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eti fee? nereid? ceretile-oare focuri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eterul sau pmntul pe tine te-au crescut?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aproape d-aste rmuri, a Dunrii mflare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te-aduse din vrun munte? te-a tras din ocean?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-e misia s fermeci? prin dulcea ta cntare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu vii s revoli inimi? lucrezi tu pe vrun plan?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ast palat de aur, pe vrful stui munte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Priimeti din cer relaii? zefirii te servesc?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu vii, cum vz, cu vara, Satan cnd cade-n lupte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din ceruri heruvimii pe demoni cnd gonesc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eti Flora? eti Pomona? sau Ceres? tu n-ai nume?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu viu pn la altaru-i s-aduc vre un prinos;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu voi s aflu bine de cnd eti tu n lume;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vei imnuri? vei vrun templu? sau toate-i sunt prisos.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stpn-n aste prejme, tu vii s lai tradiii!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S faci locuitorii a povesti la foc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C este-o zeitate,  i alte superstiii, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce cnt, umbl noaptea, s-arat-n acest loc!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe cal,  ei or s zic,  o vezi undnd vro vale</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La cmp iar se arat s-ndemne-un muncitor;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De multe ori, pe sear, o vezi c-i iese-n cale,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te-ntreab d-a ta stare, de eti vrun cltor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din ochi-i sar schinteie i nu poi s-o vezi bine;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea are haine altfel, iar nu ca la ora;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De dnsa cnd te-apropii tu n-ai minile-n tine;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De spum-i este gtul i minile de ca!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea are multe semne-cu care se arat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n fa-i rar romnul s poat a cta;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Femeie nalt este, de mn duce-o fat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-o vezi mai mult sub coast la umbr a cnta.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atuncea st i vntul, s bat nu mai poate; </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca cremenea stau toate i eti silit s taci;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici pasere s-aude, i glasul ce ea scoate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i d fiori prin oase i nu tii ce mai faci!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ei bine! astea toate eu tiu c-or s se fac,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i multe generaii, acel ce-a fi micat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De patimi sau restrite, n visu-i a s-i plac</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S afle de la tine ce soart l-a clcat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fetia a s roage s-i dai n vis pe mire;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Plugari or s te cheme spre brazde-a le cta;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btrna, n descntec, la lucruri peste fire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe tine-a s te strige minuni a arta;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar mie, ce-ndoiala mi-a fost singura moarte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i crui adevrul i place-att de mult, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">mi place-a ta natur s aflu, s-explic foarte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-apoi s crez n tine, s mor n al tu cult!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>La *** </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ct sunt gelos, ***, cnd tiu c azi eti pus</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-i lai sursul dulce la ci te felicit!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La cte vederi astzi ei fi tu oari expus,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ci, l-a ta ochead, se crede fericit!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acele roze fragezi ce lai ca s se vaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe faa ta ca crinul, la oricare-al tu pas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acele bucle negre, ce-adesea lai s caz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe snu-i de zpad, cnd scoi frumosu-i glas;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd geana ta cea lung o lai s se uneasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu cea de corb sprncean, la care Mihail</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-adaoge s-ar teme chiar linia-i cereasc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i s-i prefac-ar face Madona Rafail;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acea ctare dulce, ce vecinic schinteiaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ochii ti cei negri, n care-mpresc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Doi sori ce n-au eclipsuri i care nviaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Chiar inimi mpietrite sub ei cnd se gsesc;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Modesta ta micare, accentele-i ce-ncnt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe oricare fiin de orice caracter,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i toat frumuseea-i ce-n inimi se mplnt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd tiu c est-expus la un ntreg parter, </text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-alerg mi vine-ndat, s nu gndesc la lume,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S zbor din aste maluri, s-ajung n cercul tu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S strng pe buze-mi mna-i urnd la al tu nume,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S iau p-ascuns un zmbet i srutatul tu.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">La **** </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Pe un album</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pentru c vrei, copil, s m nscriu aci,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i spui c eti frumoas fr cochetrie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C i ascunzi simirea cu mult modestie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i c i faci amicii fr a ngriji.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">tiu bine, pn-acuma, vergina-i auzire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu este veninat de nici o linguire;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar eu, tributar vecinic al nevinoviei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Admirator, prieten blndeii, modestiei,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">ntinz hrtia asta n loc de tabernacol</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-ador cuttura-i n care, ca-n oracol,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Explic, vz fericirea a celui ce-a veni</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu tine-a se uni.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Lepdatul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ce! sta-i e morala i asta-i a ta lege,<text:line-break/>S blestemi pe aceia ce zici c-ai ajutat?<text:line-break/>Prin facerea de bine, doctrina-i va s lege<text:line-break/>Etern ntr-o sclavie pe cel ce-a apucat?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Virtute este asta? E facere de bine<text:line-break/>S chemi un om din cale, zicnd c-l foloseti,<text:line-break/>-apoi s-i ceri viaa, s n-aib trai de tine,<text:line-break/>Etern n toat lumea s-ai drept s-l ocrti?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i dac tu, de sine-i, mpins d-a ta credin,<text:line-break/>Plteti o datorie cnd tii c eti dator,<text:line-break/>Oari poi tu pentru asta, n bun contiin,<text:line-break/>S tragi n judecat pe cei ce-i uit p-a lor?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Virtutea este-o tain ce rar se dezvlete;<text:line-break/>E chiar instinct ce nate cu omul virtuos;<text:line-break/>ndeamn-a face bine, rsplat nu priimete<text:line-break/>-acel ce-i spune fapta etern e viios.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Nemernic! Mai nemernic dect acel ce simte<text:line-break/>Un pre, o rspltire n contiina sa,<text:line-break/>i-alergi btrna limb, i care etern minte,<text:line-break/>Ca fierea strns-n tine, n alii a vrsa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pierdut nu este-acela ce nc este-n sine,<text:line-break/>Nici este slug-acela ce-ncepe cum tu zici;<text:line-break/>Acela este slug, ce minte ca i tine,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Ce cugetul i-l vinde i linge cum tu lingi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ori care e pcatul ce-i face-acum mustrare?<text:line-break/>Zi, care este culpa ce-acuma te-a turbat?<text:line-break/>E cugetul tu nsui ce-a-a ta turbare;<text:line-break/>E chiar Cristos acela de care-eti lepdat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Din ci cu-a tale lacrimi ce ai etern gtite,<text:line-break/>Pgne, spune unu pe care-ai cunoscut,<text:line-break/>Care-a crezut, sperjure, viclenile-i cuvinte;<text:line-break/>i care, pn-n urm, n-a fost i el vndut?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Vnzrile adun-i, o, Iud lepdate!<text:line-break/>Se vd, pe frunte-i, iat, aci s-au nfierat<text:line-break/>n sarbdele pete de fulgere-mplntate.<text:line-break/>Rabd, de poi, oglinda ce-i strig: elerat<text:note text:id="ftn20" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>20</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
      <text:p text:style-name="P22">fr. <text:span text:style-name="T1">sclrat</text:span>, ticlos, capabil de crim, perfid</text:p></text:note-body></text:note>!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Asta e bunu-i nume: vnztor! Tu l tiai<text:line-break/>De cnd cu negrii idoli, cu care ai tratat<text:line-break/>Vnzarea rii, Iudo! a rii ce tu n-ai;<text:line-break/>Dar lumea te cunoate, i d-aia ai turbat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Strigoi ce dup moarte sugrumi p-i de iubeai!<text:line-break/>Daca era pierzare n locul ce mbeli,<text:line-break/>De ce mugeai n somnu-i i te ncolceai<text:line-break/>Strignd: aci e raiu! Voiai s ne neli?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Tartuf<text:note text:id="ftn21" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>21</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
      <text:p text:style-name="P22">Tartuffe, personaj al lui Molire</text:p></text:note-body></text:note>! Viclean clugr! Ce-ngni evanghelismul<text:line-break/>Nu; nu i-e timpul sta; te du d-unde-ai venit;<text:line-break/>Pe buza-i infernal, ce spurci cristianismul?<text:line-break/>Te-afund-n ntunerec, de unde ai ieit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Apostat! Spune-odat, ce i-ai fcut credina?<text:line-break/>De ce te-ascunzi de lume? Ce! boala-i n-are leac<text:line-break/>Cci ai trdat misterul; cci i-ai mncat credina,<text:line-break/>Te-ai prefcut, atee, din oarec liliac.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Te du, profit nc, mai specul -acuma,<text:line-break/>Prilej mai iat -altul ca s apuci un os,<text:line-break/>Deschide-i ochii ns; din el exal ciuma,<text:line-break/>i d-o mnca i puii-i s duc la iad prinos.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O, ct oi s rz iar aflnd de pe la lume<text:line-break/>C-acel cui lingi piciorul, te lupi ntr-al su nume,<text:line-break/>Furi te simte-n somnu-i c, tremurnd de fric,<text:line-break/>Rpezi i-n gtu-i noaptea o ghear de pisic!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu mult este mai nobil un dobitoc slbatic,<text:line-break/>Ce nate n pdure cu-al rului instinct,<text:line-break/>Dect un om nemernic ce-n adunare pacinic<text:line-break/>Trndu-se tot muc, ca cel mai prost insect.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Un om fr iubire, ce nu tie ce crede,<text:line-break/>Ce astzi s nchin l-acel ce ieri huli,<text:line-break/>De via nu e vrednic; dar nici acel ce-l pierde,<text:line-break/>Onoare aa mare nu poate dobndi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Un vierme e n tine, sperjur d-a treia oar!<text:line-break/>i roade-acum rrunchii c-ai vrut s-i faci comoar,<text:line-break/>Vnznd pe vinovaii ce tii c n-au putere<text:line-break/>Ca s-i rspunz, gdeo, l-a ta nelegiuire.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Acei ce vezi n somnu-i c vin s te sugrume,<text:line-break/>Sunt draci, ai ti tovari, ce zbier, i fac sermon<text:note text:id="ftn22" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>22</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
      <text:p text:style-name="P6">sermon (fr.)  <text:span text:style-name="T12">predic , discurs cretin, figurativ </text:span>dojan<text:span text:style-name="T12"> plictisitoare</text:span>.</text:p></text:note-body></text:note><text:line-break/>Voind s-i ia suflarea ntr-al Satanii nume,<text:line-break/>i dac n-o pot face e cauza, demon,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">C-a ta spurcat gur a dat o srutare<text:line-break/>Acelor brbai vrednici, ce-acum te-au oropsit;<text:line-break/>i sufletu-i s ias, n neagra sa turbare,<text:line-break/>P gur-i nu cuteaz, cci este-afurisit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iar soarele ce vine de draci ca s te scape,<text:line-break/>Este Cristos, srmane, cultul cel sfnt, ceresc:<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Lsai-l pre el, zice, de ce-l silii s crape;<text:line-break/>Nu tie ce-i se face! i dracii se-ngrozesc.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Maria din Bezdat </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Balad</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph">Cerul se deschide n noaptea de Boboteaz,<text:line-break/>i atunci dobndete fiecine orice va cere.<text:line-break/>Eres popular</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I8"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Maria cea blaie,<text:line-break/>Frumoasa din Bezdat,<text:line-break/>Iubea pe Niculae<text:line-break/>i vrea s-l ia brbat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Prinii o simise<text:line-break/>C ea cam des pierea,<text:line-break/>i-n crng o cam oprise<text:line-break/>D-a merge la viea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Zburdalnica copil,<text:line-break/>Cnd vitele intra,<text:line-break/>i da cu mult mil<text:line-break/>Pupatul ce-i pstra.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar ns biata fat<text:line-break/>Nu vru a mai rbda;<text:line-break/>Bunichii ei s-arat<text:line-break/>i-ncepe-a se preda:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ah! Bun btrnic,<text:line-break/>Pe Niculae iubesc;<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>De maica-mi este fric,<text:line-break/>i-a vrea s-l ntlnesc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Eu tiu c tu eti bun<text:line-break/>i nu tii vicleug;<text:line-break/>S mi-l aduci pe lun,<text:line-break/>Ai tu vrun meteug?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i ce fel? astea toate<text:line-break/>Din inim le zici?<text:line-break/>Taci, fiic! nu se poate:<text:line-break/>Tu vorbele i strici.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Degeaba, btrnic,<text:line-break/>Eu nu poci s-l ursc,<text:line-break/>F-mi mcar orice fric,<text:line-break/>Eu tot o s-l iubesc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu el nu te asameni<text:line-break/>n orice chip mcar:<text:line-break/>Eti fat tu de oameni,<text:line-break/>i el, un prost vcar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">M rog, de Niculae<text:line-break/>Tu astfel nu-mi vorbi;<text:line-break/>Chiar turcii s m taie,<text:line-break/>Eu tot l voi iubi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Aa o fi, feti;<text:line-break/>Dar el e prea srac<text:line-break/>i e de proast vi,<text:line-break/>Mcar c i-e p plac.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ei bine, eu la tine<text:line-break/>Acuma nu-l mai cer;<text:line-break/>Mai rabd cum poci n mine<text:line-break/>i-l cer eu de la cer.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Atept la Boboteaz,<text:line-break/>Cnd cerul e deschis,<text:line-break/>i Domnu-o s m creaz<text:line-break/>-o s mi-l dea n vis.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II8"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Btrn-alearg-ndat<text:line-break/>Cu mum-a se gndi<text:line-break/>n ce chip biata fat<text:line-break/>S-o poat amgi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Eu tiu, i zice, bine<text:line-break/>S-o scap din ast ponos.<text:line-break/>Acum te las p mine<text:line-break/>S isprvesc frumos.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ct vine-aceast.sear<text:line-break/>Cnd ceru e deschis,<text:line-break/>Se culc fat-afar,<text:line-break/>S vaz ce-i e scris.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Btrn-afurisit,<text:line-break/>Pe-al casei nvli,<text:line-break/>C-a rilor ispit,<text:line-break/>edea sub co piti.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Blaia frumuic<text:line-break/>Deloc ea nu dormea.<text:line-break/>i toat numai frica<text:line-break/>Acel minut pndea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S vaz la vreo parte<text:line-break/>Pe Bunul Ziditor,<text:line-break/>S-l roage-a-i face parte<text:line-break/>De dragu-i soior.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Un fulger lumineaz,<text:line-break/>i ea pe brnci czu;<text:line-break/>Un glas o-nfioreaz<text:line-break/>i moartea i vzu:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Nu, fat; nu mai cere<text:line-break/>Pe un vcar brbat!<text:line-break/>i-ndat, din tcere,<text:line-break/>Un ipt a scpat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Prinii toi afar<text:line-break/>Se-azvrl din aternut;<text:line-break/>Spre bab-acum s sar,<text:line-break/>S-o sparg mai au vrut.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Alearg la copil,<text:line-break/>La rodul lor iubit,<text:line-break/>Voiesc s-o scoale-n sil;<text:line-break/>Dar ea a i murit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Prini, bgai de seam,<text:line-break/>De-alegeri v ferii,<text:line-break/>De eres v fie team,<text:line-break/>C-asemenea pii.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Maria</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Corabie frumoas! Te du, te du, grbete?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe rmuri deprtate alearg, prevestete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C lesne-aa nu moare un neam ce a trit;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C tirania poate un om s prpdeasc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar viaa unei naii nu poate s sleiasc:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn-n sfrit. Dreptatea etern a biruit;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd vei ajunge bine n porturi deprtate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i alte neamuri mndre, crescute-n libertate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vor vrea s te ntrebe de numele ce pori,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atunci tu pavilionu-i s-l lai s flfiasc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S spui c al tu nume e lesne s-l ghiceasc:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E scris n istorie p-ale mrirei pori.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar vrnd s te ntrebe de au vro-ncredinare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i daca n pmntu-i nu cerc vro strmtorare, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu spune-le c neamu-i nu tie vicleug,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-i este prunc comerciul, nu-s reguli aezate:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar este drept i pacinic, i fr rutate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mcar c n-avu condici, mcar c fu sub jug.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Robitul cnd i sparge obezile odat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i peste-ale-nchisorii trii se mai arat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atunci mai ager este, atunci e mulumit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atunci i place cerul, dorina lui s-aprinde;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-atunci, cu anevoie n curse se mai prinde:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Experiena-nva pe cel ce-a suferit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Le spune c pmntu-i e ar generoas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Srac-n meteuguri, dar clima-i e vroas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Produce mii de bunuri ce pot a-i mulumi;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C lnuri scoate bune, mtsuri minunate;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bogate are holde de feluri de bucate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i n-or s se ciasc n ea cnd vor veni.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pduri c are-ntinse cu mult lemnrie;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C munii ei ncuie o mare bogie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar rar sunt care tie comorile din ei;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O pescrie mare, i vinuri de minune;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cirezi i turme grase, cci are dulci pune;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i faguri de zpad, in, cnep i piei.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Adaog la astea c ara-i nu hrnete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici fiare veninoase, nici plant ce-otrvete, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ei, expui naturii, nimic n-or ptimi.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pdurile ei, spune, n-au umbr-omortoare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Livezile-n ghizdee, n-au ierbi otrvitoare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Urs-alb, hien, tigru, viperi n-or ntlni.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stejarul, ulmul, pleopul i bradul n veci verde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Corn, frasinul, aninul ce vrfu-n nori i pierde, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ei singuri fac cunune pe trmbele de muni.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mistreul, cprioara i mii de cerbi i ciute</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ruri de cristaluri se plec ca s se uite</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La pstrovi ce se joac cu lostrie cruni.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">C sunt, le spune, liberi la orice vntoare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C boalele nprasnici nu pot s mai omoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i hrana vieii-oricine prea lesne va gsi;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C foametea aicea abia se povestete;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C frica de rzboaie prini nu ngrozete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i rnile-i cumplite, ei nu le vor simi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Corabie frumoas! Te du, te du, grbete!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe rmuri deprtate alearg, prevestete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C lesne-aa nu moare un neam ce a trit!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C tirania poate un om s prpdeasc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar viaa unei naii nu poate s sleiasc:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn-n sfrit, dreptatea etern a biruit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Meditaia I: nlciunea ndejdii</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Sfnt Ndejde, fiica cerului! Tu ce eti venit a astmpra turbatele furii ale nenorocirii! Tu ce ne aperi de toate npustirile dezndjduirii, artndu-ne n veci viitorul plin de fericiri!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Tu, a crii priveghere daca un minut ar lipsi din lume, negreit cerul ar rmnea fr slvitori, pmntul fr motenitori, i toat fiina cuvnttoare ar umplea numaidect ncperile Tartarului. Tu te cobori din snul cerului n inima nenorocitului scrbit de nemulumire, l mngi i-i ari ceririle lui, ca cum ar fi gata s le apuce mine... Dar, vai! mine al tu nu are sfrit; fgduielile tale, presrate ntr-un spaiu nemrginit, ntocmai ca zburtoarele fantome ale nltoarelor vise, fug numaidect ce noi gndim c le-am prins...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Ei bine, attea veacuri n-au putut a nimicnici puterea ta? A putut fermecul minciunilor tale cel amgitor a nla i marile inimi ale acelor vestii brbai ce au spimntat pmntul? O, ct trebuie s tremure cineva mai mult de tine dect de moarte! Moartea, dnd numai o lovitur, odihnete pe nenorocit. Tu l faci s cerce nzecit acea lovitur la toat nlarea, i cu toate acestea mngietoarea-i ghear l pstreaz ca s-i mai dea i altele; i necndu-i simirile n abisul minciunilor tale, slobozi a lui credlitate pn la cele mai mari fericiri, numai ca s fie mai veninat durerea, cnd, ridicndu-i dupe ochi vlul ce nu-l las a cunoate adevrul, l-o vedea departe de dnsul.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">O, oameni, fiine n veci supuse astei desfrnate pu- teri! voi ce v gndii mai fericii dect cele ce voi stpnii! voi v ngmfai socotindu-v peste puterile ce-i bat joc de voi! Stai!... Venii-v-i n simiri! Vedei c nu sntei nimic mai-nalt dect o jucrie a acetii cum- plite zeiti!... Ea v arat comorile, fgduindu-v cu ele toate bunurile i chiar nemurirea, i voi, bei de r- tcirea crii sntei sujet, alergai, jertfii prieteni, prini, fii, ca s ctigai un product al globului ce a produs i pe voi; v arat slava, i voi, ameii, orbi, nfurai in vlul ce nu v las s vedei sfritul celor asemenea vou, dedai napoi ceea ce ai strns pe pierderea aproa- pelui vostru ca s-o ctigai, -apoi, tocmai cnd sntei aproape a v gndi fericii, iat, ngerul ornduit a nu lsa s v apropiai de aceea ce nu e dat vou, vine, v sugrum, v rpete de lng acelea dupe care -atunci cnd nu mai sntei oftai...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Voi intrai n vecinica nesimire, i pomenirea voas- tr abia se ine pe ruinele monumentelor ce <text:soft-page-break/>v rdic ur- maii votri, asupra crora, lsnd ca o motenire lipi- cioasa orbire, s ded n urmaii votri, i fac s se mire de voi, i rvnind la ale voastre nesocotine, s se sileasc i ei, cu asemenea cruzimi i vrsri de sngiuri, a ardica ca voi, -aa ale voastre unite cu ale lor i cu ale urma- ilor lor, s slujeasc numai spre a arta viitoarelor veacuri ticloia voastr i mplinirea scoposului astei fatale zeiti, care, npustit asupr-v, cu un bici de scorpii, v-a mpilat s muncii voi pn la cea dup urm rsuflare.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Meditaia II: Ceasul al treilea dup miezul nopii </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Lin tcere, balsam vindictor al turburatelor suflete!... Tu, al cria plcut nectar, favorit inimilor simitoare, deteapt inerea de minte, ne bucur repetndu-ne mulumirile ce n trecut am gustat, i artndu-ne viitorul ca un veac aurit, ne fgduiete ntr-nsul dobndirea celor mai mari fericiri!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Toat suflarea tace! toat fptura viseaz n pace plcerile ce au a le gusta mine!... Nimic nu turbur somnul cel dup urm al norocitului, pe care ziua l ateapt ca s depuie n mna-i muncitoare uneltile hranii!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Abia cnd i cnd cntarea cocoului sau ltratul vreunui cine vine s bat auzul nenorocitului prsit de somn...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Dulce tcere! Cine a tiut a se folosi de tine i n-a gsit nzecit mulmirea, ce fiii chinurilor cu attea osteneli o caut n baluri i ospee de mare cuviin? Care, de nenorociri apsat, alergnd la al tu liman, n-a aflat ntr-nsul azilul cel mai adevrat?... Tu veri n inerile inimi acea dulce melanholie, ce adoarme cumplitele furii ale nenorocirii; i fcnd s curg n ele un mol tmduitor, asemenea pacinicului pria al grdinilor, odihneti simirile obosite de cumplitele varieti ale soartei, ntocmai ca un milos stpn ce, descurndu-i calul czut de osteneal i de arsura zilii, i desface toate chingile, l bate p spate c-o mngietoare mn -l sloboade n rcoarea nserrii a pate troscotul cel rcoros al cmpiilor...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">O, ct este de plcut ntristarea ce tu aduci!... Omul, deprtat de tot zgomotul lumii, ntr-armat cu fgduielile ndejdii, zboar pe aripile idolului su la scumpu-i objet; i nchipuiete poziiile n care s-ar fi aflnd, repeteaz vorbele ce i-a zis, rspunsurile ce a luat, face o plcut critic slabului neles ce scoate din ele, numr cutturile ce a ctigat de la ea, oftrile ei, vorbele ce se repeta n delirul cel dulce, le d o color dup voia lui, i face o idee de ceea ce gndete acum; i ncntat n fermecul plcerii, ngnat de un somn ntrerumpt, ateapt un vis care vine i-l arunc n braele ei.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Meditaia III: Nencredinarea n prieteni </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Dulce prieteug! nger trimis din ceruri spre a uni pe oameni prin comptimire! Tu ce ne deosibeti din slbaticile fiare! Tu ce ne nmuleti fericirile fcnd s le gustm de attea ori de cte ori le dobndesc aceia cu care tu ne uneti, i ne micorezi durerile, fcnd s le mprim cu dnii! Tu eti un alt soare duhovnicesc, ale crui raze purttoare de ndejde, ncredinare i netemere de fiinele mpotrivitoare, nclzete sufletele acelora n care intr. Cine te-a cunoscut pe tine i n-a mrturisit c eti venit numai a reprezenta pe atotputernicul? Cine, gsind n acela ce el a vrut un sentiment nsuflat de tine, n-a mrturisit c eti o icoan ce ne nfiezi aievea fericirile ce religiile dau credincioilor? O, ct snt de plcute darurile tale!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Tu la svrirea unei mici jrtfe ce ceri de ia noi ne dai nepreuite comori...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Tu zici: Iubii-v ca s fii fericii, i fr zbav plteti cu prisos fgduielile tale celor ce te-au ascultat... O! Dar de ce fgduielile tale cele sfinte, blnzi, nevinovate i neprimejdioase, s fie mai nesocotite dect ale ndrcitului, aspru, vinovat i primejdios neprieteug... El zice: Vrjmii-v, ca s v sfie o vecinic crud nenorocire, i iat-l gata a plti cu dobnd fgduielile sale. Dar tu ne uneti cu cerul; lanurile tale in un sfrit raport ntre inimile generoase i ntre ngeri... Tu ne aliezi n sfrit cu nsui Dumnezeu...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Noi fr porunca ta nu facem nimic bun i nimic iari ru cu voia ta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Ei bine, dar pentru ce eu s nu m mprtesc din comorile tale?... Ce fel! pentru mine nu este nici o inim care s pstreze n snu-i o scnteie din tine? Eu singur fui osndit a tri fr prieteni? Ce fel! Inima-mi tare, fieroas, fr cuvnt nu se ncrede la nimeni din ci m ncongiur... Snt ei oare toi nevrednici de credin, ca acela ce odat m amgi?... Ei se arat triti, simitori la durerile mele, ei nscocesc felurimi de petreceri, mi-arat mii de nevinovate plceri, ca s m smulg din absorbirea vinovatelor gnduri, ei se ntristeaz vznd c m topesc n aria delirului sfiitor; jur c vor fi prtai la durerile mele, jur c cu primejdia lor mi vor ajuta... Ei! dar ei jur numai pn atunci pn n-or cunoate covrirea patimilor mele. Poate fi oare ntre ei vreunul cu atta tineree pentru mine care s priimeasc de bun voie parte din durerile mele, s priimeasc n el un vierme fr somn i s-i dea inima prad stui foc mistuitor? Ei m iubesc numai pn atunci pn cnd m socotesc c doresc fericirea lor; m mai pot ei iubi oare cnd m-or cunoate al lor rival?... Negreit c nu. Ei bine, s zic c prieteugul nrdcinat n inima lor i va sili s jrtfeasc -acel dulce simtiment, ca s foloseasc pe un iubit prsit de noroc, va putea gelozia mea a mpri cu dnii un foc prin care sim, rsuflu i fr care n-a putea tri un minut? Voi putea eu mprtia un simtiment sfnt, ce m nsufl, mi-arat bunul cel nepreuit i m povuiete la fericirea cea adevrat, n vreme cnd gelozia-mi aprins fierbe c nu are acea putere electric a-l strnge dup unde l vede mprtiat, ca s-l adune tot la sinei?... Ce folos mi poate da oricare, de-mi va afla focul ce m mistuiete <text:soft-page-break/>ntocmai ca ceaa cea groas vlul pmntului cel alb de zpad, i m crete totdeodat cu dulcea ambrozie, ce zeitatea oarecnd i alese spre hran?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Mai mult negreit nu voi ctiga dect de la rivali o ur, ce totdauna este dat lor, de la indifereni batjocora, de o molicioas slbiciune, i de la prieteni o mil fr putere a m ajuta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Nu, oricare din astea voi ctiga, mi va fi mai nesuferit dect nsui moartea; nu, mai bine s m sfresc dup cum m-am nceput, n chinuri, n spumegoasele valuri adogate de vijlia nenorocirilor, dect s m dau sujet criticii desfrnatei omeniri.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Meditaia IV: Sinucidul </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Stpn preaputernic, creator nemrginit, tu, mprat al totului ntreg!... Pentru ce ai nrdcinat n inima mea ast veninoas nemulmire? Pentru ce pe mine numai ndejdea nu m poate nla? Ce tulburri grozave!... ce simtimente necunoscute m sfie de cum m-am pomenit n lume! Cumplit stpn!... Ce neiertat pcat a putut face pruncia mea de le-ai npustit dodat cu junia a m sfia! Printe preaslvit! Aste grozave tulburri fur ornduite a m priimi n lume? Ori a trebuit a se nate dodat cu mine? Dumnezeu adevrat! Daca fr ele nu m puteam nate, dac p-st amrt pmnt eu nu-mi puteam gsi fericirea, de ce m-ai nfiinat? care aa mare trebuin fu a m nate? ce te sili a-mi tulbura odihna ce gustam n snul nesimirii, pn a nu te cunoate, i a-mi da un trup, un suflet, ca s fie prad pmntetilor chinuri... Era trebuincios atomul meu la podoaba stui glob? Lipsa lutoasei mele mbrcminte putea opri armonia universului?...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Ei fie! rnosul meu trup fu trebuincios a-i mobila nemrginitul palat; lipsa slabei mele nelegeri putea s micoreze nalta slav ce ceri de la zidirea ta; cu un cuvnt, trebuia eu s fiu. Apoi neatrnata-i voin m fcu fr a mai ngriji de soarta mea? Neneleasa-i putere1, numit provedin, s lenevi a mai ngriji de fericirea mea? ntmplarea m arunc n voia ursitei, fr nici un fel de condiie? i lipsete dar ie cugetul ce jucriile tale porunceti s-l aib, nct vrei a nfiina un norocit. Nimica, spre a-l lsa n voia valurilor ticloiei? Este de crezut ca printeasca-i ngrijire s fac ru unde nu poate face bine? Daca nu vreai, sau nu puteai a m mulmi, de ce, lundu-mi moartea, mi-ai rdicat i aceea ce n via nu mi-o poi da? Eu nu te-am rugat a-mi da fiin; p mine nu m-ai ntrebat la hotrrea ce ai fcut pentru zmislirea mea; prerea mea, de ar fi fost ntrebat, negreit c n-ar fi priimit via de o zi mcar; de mi-ar fi fost ncrcat de toate coroanele lumii, negreit c n-a fi schimbat acea linitit nesimire, nici chiar cu scaunul tu, daca i p el ar fi trebuit s fiu viu!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">O, fatal fiin! Care snt bunurile ce vrei s m faci a crede c mi-ai dat? Tot ce mi-ai dat pentru slava ta mi-ai dat; simiri mi-ai dat ca s m mir de mrimea ta i s cunosc ticloia mea; hran, ca s poci tr o via trndav i monoton, iar pentru scoposul tu. Ce mi-ai dat pentru fericirea mea? Soare? nu m nclzete. Schimbarea timpurilor? nu m mulumesc. mplinind toat voia ta, necunoscut nou, ce o s-mi dai mai mult dect astea? Fiindu-i mpotrivitor, ce-o s-mi iei mai mult dect ce mi-ai dat? vederi? auz? simitate? Tot ce mi-ai lua, mi dai; c rectig o parte din odihna ce aveam mai nainte d-a fi, n-oi s mai poci simi cldura soarelui? n-oi s mai vz schimbarea timpurilor? n-oi s mai auz armonia zburtoarelor? De astea toate nici acum nu m bucur: pentru mine, ori negur, sau senin, or var, sau iarn, ori zgomote, sau armonie, snt totuna.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Apoi s crez iari c tu poi a m mulumi i nu vrei!... Nu tiu; poate c i tu spnzuri de acea soart de care spnzur totul! poate c i tu cerci ca i noi nemulumiri! poate c i tu eti supus vreunei puteri mai nalte dect tine, necunoscute mrginitei noastre ptrunderi! Ce s zic! Sau c glasurile noastre, umilite i rezvoltate, nu pot ajunge pn la nalta-i lcuin!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Apoi iari, daca fiina-i umple totul, daca nemrginita-i ntindere coprinde toate, daca tu eti stpn al soartei, preaputernic, milostiv i bun, ce te oprete d-a asculta duioasele gemete ce natura ntreag scoate subt apsarea nesuferitei nenorociri?... Ce te oprete a precurma dureroasele ipete ce s rzgomoal, rzbubuie n acest dert, din rrunchii suferitoarei omeniri?...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Vezi iroaiele lacrmilor cum curg n templurile tale; vezi la picioarele minitrilor altarelor tale ngenucheat omenirea, ca s-i roage a trimite la scaunul tu, prin cdelnia lor, tmia i fierbintele lor rugciuni; vezi pe aceti cuvioi, propoveduii ai ti, alei prin monumenturile ce ne-ai lsat, umilii la apsata omenire, lcrmnd naintea tabernaclului tu, cernd cu mna pe semnile credinei lor a trimite i pe pmnt parte din fericirea, ce toat nesaiul tu o pstreaz numai pentru tine...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">O, Dumnezeu slvit, printe i stpn, ziditor preaputernic al totului ntreg! Deschide poarta vecinicilor trii; ascult glasul ce s rtcete, neputnd a strbate pn la tine, trimite mna-i prea darnic a m scoate din labirentul chinurilor... Printe preadrepte! Aridic-m n azilul tu, trage-i napoi raza ce ai depus n mine; smulgem din groaznica tortur a agoniei! Vino, cu o moarte prea grabnic odihnete-mi tulburatul suflet; sparge-i printr-nsa ntunerecul ce-l <text:soft-page-break/>neac, vezi-l cum te caut dezndjduit! Trage-l n scnteietoarele lumini ce i strlucesc lcaul! ntoarce-i ochiul mrinimos asupra fiinii mele! Umilete-te! mbriaz o slab neputincioas creatur!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Vezi-o spimntat, ngrozit n gheara ursitei! Vezi-m n genunche, smuls, sfiat dedesubtul bolilor tale!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Tremur!... Printe!... Of!... puteri nu mai am!... ziua s ivete iar, nevoile se deteapt, i cerul nc nu s-a deschis. O, cruzime! tiran nenduplecat!... Urechea-i nesimitoare nu se apleac dect numai la concertele cntreilor i organelor; tu nu-i tulburi a ta trndvie ca s asculi ipete jalnice; nu, vitri, lacrmi, gemete, pe tine nu te umilesc, crude!. Inima-i tare nu se mic, nu s atinge de mil; tu nu repriimeti ntristarea ce odat ai deprtat de la tine.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Rscoale-se zbieretele astor nimicite fpturi, rezvoalte-se ipetele viermilor mrginii; stavila ce am pus puterilor e destul de departe de triile mele. n zgomote atmosfera lor, pn pe rndu-i fiecare va ntoarce mprumutata rn de unde a luat-o; n tarele mele boli, nici mna lor, nici glasul nu va putea rzbi n veci. Ah! De ce nu poci s rzbesc la tine! Cum a ti s-mi rzbun! A scpa cel puin lumea nenscut nc; a usca izvorul efemerilor tale lucrri, ca un potop m-ai vedea stingnd focul, ce, plin de venin, ai pentru nvierea nevinovatei nesimiri! Ah! dar asta... Este o zadarnic cugetare; asprul despot a tiut a se asigura. Suflete nenorocite f pstreaz i afar din mine dreapta ur ce ca o motenire i las cu jurmnt. Deprteaz-te de dnsul ct vei putea, fugi de ngrijirea lui; vezi-l pregtindu-i ndoite fiare dect acestea care i le sparg eu acum! Vezi-l pizma p nemurirea ta, cum te ateapt a-i da o rol mai grea, mai ostenitoare dect asta care i-o precurm eu; vezi o alt form ce-i este gtit; vezi-l cu o mn slobod la mpreala chinurilor, cum grmdete n ea necazurile i te ateapt a te mpovra cu dnsa... Dar, necjit suflet! fugi de dnsul... Fugi ct vei putea... i unde poi fugi? n care azil poi scpa de dnsul? n care ocean? n care gaur te poi apra de sugrumtoarea-i ghear!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Of! sufletul meu nu-l voi putea scpa!... Ah! stpn nestrmutat! D-i, de este n mna ta, d-i i lui moartea. Destul! Mulumete-te cu chinurile ce sufer n mine. Destul! Oprete-te de a-i mai da un trup!... Dar ctre cine vorbesc! cine m-aude? O, rtcire! Rugciunile mele totdauna absurde nu se vor asculta n veci? Cine alt mi poate da i mie, i sufletului meu odihna, dect eu? Eu nsumi numai mi poci da fericirea ce cer de la el; sufletul meu, de va putea, urmeze-mi; dar, eu numai; acum cnd mna-mi sinucid, grbind fulgerul morii, i va ntoarce napoi darul ce, fr s-i cer, mi-a dat... eava vulcanic ce nenorociii cei mai-nainte de mine a nscocitr nu <text:soft-page-break/>este n mna mea? Plumbul, stpnul morii, n-ateapt micarea degetului meu? Ce mai atept?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Adio, prieteni, muritori nenorocii! Urmai-mi; umplei-v-i evele; nflcreze-se grindina de plumb; aprinz-se silitra; turbeze Etna, verse-se Vezuvul. Ardei... Drmai... Pustiii pmntul... V jur... V jur pe odihna morii: urmai-mi... Urmai...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Meditaia V: Nlucul sau <text:span text:style-name="T1">Peste un an</text:span> </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">An, ce-n tot minutul mi-ari lungimea ta! treci, grbete ale tale timpuri!... Sfrate, du-te cu ale mele chinuri! Fugi, trte cu tine a mea rstrite -al meu apstor!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Zi, ce peste un an mi-ari naterea mea! salt, nal-te din al anului r. i p-ale tale aripi, cu a doua-mi ursit, ardic-m din iad. Soarelui vestete c a cerului lumin, de azi semnat, este dator a-mi da; spune-i c cu moartea n zadar m-amerin n al lui zbavnic curs. Viaa-mi se renate, cerul nu voiete a-mi rmnea da- tor, el a mea durere oprete -al meu instinct vestind, n- dejdea mi sdete d-al su prea mare dar. Iar daca na- tura ntreag, pizma p-al meu de zeu noroc, mi va grbi sfritul pn a nu-l gusta, atunci tu iari spune-i c-acel prea scump odor, pe piatr-mi consfinit, eu l a-tept n cer. Adaog-i c-atuncea cnd n-oi mai fi trind, el tot s-mi mai vesteasc al ei prea dulce nume; i p-ale sale raze purtnd al meu amor, s-i duc, s-mi aduc n tot rondu-i cte un sincer raport.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">i tu, cuget, ce ai puterea n tot omul muritor! tu, ce spre mustrarea crimelor te-nfuriezi! du-te, alearg pn ai vreme; strig, spune-i pn triesc; vestete-i a mea moarte, neputina d-a tri, spune-i c ea poate a m scpa; mai adaog-i c tie, poate bine, dar nu vrea. Iar de vei vedea-o trist l-ale tale imputri, tu atunci oprete-i gura i m las a muri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Dar tu, mormnt, cnd, rece, al ei dar vei priimi, atunci tu n ea sdete un suvenir nestins: spune-i c -n moarte, subt tine adncat, eu pentru ea -aci, n veci snt neschimbat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">i tu, puternic stea, cnd eu grabnic oi pieri, formeaz-i dintr-ale mele zile, de timpuriu pierdute, o mulumit via; mprtie-i ntr-nsa acea fericire ce mie-mi hotr. Dar ns n tot locul, n tot lucrul ce-o gndi, adnc tu sap al meu nume, n toat urma ce-o pi.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Meditaia VI: nserarea </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Bradul cel mndru se nceat n munii Carpai. Norii se joac cu al lui mldios cretet i zefirul nundeaz verdeaa de la tulpina lui cea nestrmutat. Pleopul cel argintuit flfie ale lui late frunze. Zgomotul vlcelii face s se auz falnicile sale vrsri n conrspunztoarele vi i spumegnd se prvlete din rp n rp pn la trufaul ru. Undele Prahovii coboar toat varietatea cerului n adnca prpastie, i erpuind, abia albesc subt o neagr stnc ce le nghite nencetat. Soarele, ruinat i rnit totdeodat de frumuseea interesantei, blaiei lune, neputnd sta fa dulceii acelia ce totdauna fuge de dnsul, s-ascunde dinainte-i, lsndu-i numai lumina ce-i este dator; i mreaa fecioar, mpotrivindu-se negrului ntunerec al nopii, cu un pas lin, pompos i plin de dulcea, se nal din orientul su. nc se vd sngeraticii muni de aburi, nrubinai de murindul foc al soarelui, cnd Vinerea, repezit peste orizon n toat strlucirea ei, se nrival cu dumnezeoaica cinstii. Neputincioasa noapte, rsipit, nedestoinic a se mpotrivi biruitoarei ei, i ascunde nvinsele-i umbre i subt cel mai mic copcel.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">O, nalte lucrri, secreturi grozave, ce, puse naintea curiozitii noastre, ne fermec simirile numaidect ce ndrznim s le judecm...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Mare Dumnezeu! de ce nu poci, lsndu-mi pmnteasca hain, mpreun cu conurile, p ast rece stnc, ca un fulger meteor s zbor prin st hrnitor vzduh n lcaul fericirii, i slujind mprejurul scaunului tu, s privesc d-acolo luptile vnturilor, armonia sferilor i tot ceea ce visez aici?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Iat ceasul n care fiul morii sun al su plumbos sceptru i i ntinde ocrotitoarea-i mant peste asudatul muncitor. Asta este ceasul n care al meu suflet detept, cutnd p-al su stpn, se aint ntr-o lume care ochilor nu este iertat a vedea. Acum eu, pn a nu-mi da nc somnul, plata ostenelilor de ziua, viu singur n ast nlime, ca s-mi fac religioasa nchinciune ctre al meu -al totului Dumnezeu pe ast rcoros cretet al globului, viu singur a-mi face datoria ctre stpnul meu...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Misterioas putere, ce vii a-mi deschide drumul, prin care sufletul meu zrete p-al su Creator! Tu ce-mi spargi norul care m desparte de dnsul! D pn n ale lui auzuri sincerile-mi mulumiri de bunurile ce-mi dete pn acum, i fierbintele rugciuni a mi le da i p viitor...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Printe, tu, ce luminnd ntunerecul nesimirii, sprgnd adnca tcere a haosului, formai ast pompos univers, numai pentru a cuvntului fericire! Tu, ce, depuind n focoasa-mi simire raza duhovnicetii lumini, mi artai n tot lucru al meu simbol! Priimete din a ta nalt lcuin recunotina ce mica-i fiin i trimite de viaa ce i-ai dat! Priimete slaba strigare a tarei credine ce i nal din ast singurtate cu apusul unui soare din care i druii! Priimete respectul cu care optete numele tu!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:soft-page-break/>Iat ceasul n care, zburnd pe aripile credinei mele, ajung fa n fa a ntmpina nevzuta, dar de fa n ochii-mi putere ce m face a tri!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Bun stpn, tu, ce pentru a mea fericire lucrai atta! ine a mea ntregime, ce din rrunchi, pentru a sa nelips, mulumiri, adnci recunotine i trimite. Lucrul, simbolul fiinii mele! priimete din a ta nalt lcuin recunotina ce mica-i fiin rezemat pe ast piatr i trimite din viaa ce i-ai dat. Priimete slaba strigare a tarei credine care i trimite ntre apusul i rsritul astor dou ndrepttoare fclii ce-i druii.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Meditaia VII: Amorul </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Cnd atotputernicul stpn, sprgnd tcerea nimicu- lui, unelti universul i fiinele lui, despri i o parte din nenvinsa-i putere i o trimise zicndu-i: Du-te, coprinde toate zidirile vieuitoare i nensufleite, ntemeiaz n ele unirea i f-le a te cunoate stpn. -aa acest suflet al naturii, zburnd din nlimea cerului, se ntinse n tot coprinsul nemrginit; depuse n toat fptura cte o scnteie din flacra torii sale i o sili a se nchina lui. D-atunci acest seme, fatal Dumnezeu, despicnd vre- mea, nainteaz n capul anilor, poruncind veacurilor s-i mpodobeasc triumful. Tot universul, de cnd rsufl natura, i s-a supus; nici un muritor nu s-a gsit att de n- drzne ca s i se mpotriveasc; legile lui snt destul de primejdioase, sfriturile mplinirii poruncilor lui destul de amari, ns acest mprat al sufletelor, acest dumnezeu al simirilor tiu a-i acoperi veninul su subt masca celii mai dulce plceri, i momind credulitatea ticloasei omeniri pn la vrsta cea dup urm, i scoate masca, i ridic vlul, i o face prada recelui mormnt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">O, putere, ce-n tot lucrul sdii mrimea ta! Tu ce-n soare, n lun, n stea, n cuvnt, n necuvnt, tu ce-n vz-duh, pmnt i ap vrsai al tu venin, tu nu ai vreun sfrit? Toat zeitatea, i chiar dreptul creator, de multe ori i-n multe locuri fu necunoscut; dar tu n toat vremea, n om, n dobitoc, n tot locul, n tot veacul apururea s triumfezi? Zeu spurcat, ce-n a ta curs lumea-ntreag o trti!... Cer nedrept, ce l-a lui cruzime atta ne-ai supus, tu, ce attor rele, furii, simitoare batere ne zidii! Vezi n turmele-i un duh ce se scutur, se salt dintr-ale voastre nedrepti, ce s-ardic, se folosete d-al su puin cuvnt, ce cunoate, vede -alearg la absoluta fericire; se bucur, se mndrete d-un azil ce i gsi; se nal, se duce, zboar i de voi i bate joc.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Meditaia VIII: O sear de primvar la Colintina </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Suflai, o, dulci zefiri! suflai aicea iari,<text:line-break/>Suflai p-st verde cmp, viat</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3"><text:note text:id="ftn23" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>23</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
       <text:p text:style-name="P22"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Via  a da via, a nsuflei.</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">acum de voi!<text:line-break/>Suflai pe ast vale, ce variat-n flori<text:line-break/>De roditori copaci, m-mblsmete-aci.<text:line-break/>Suflai pe ast und, ce lin se ncreete,<text:line-break/>Suflai pe a ei pnz, ce-ncet se nfoar,<text:line-break/>Suflai p-o-nverzit coast mparfumat,<text:line-break/>Ce vecinic cununeaz acest limpede lac.<text:line-break/>Suflai p-st verde ir de tei mirositori,<text:line-break/>Suflai p-st neted cmp, nrubinat l-apus,<text:line-break/>Suflai pe st drum neted, suflai drept pe o cale<text:line-break/>Ce merge colo-ntins l-acel palat frumos.<text:line-break/>Aci p-st pavilion ce st-ntre lac i tei,<text:line-break/>Ca n lca al vostru vedei-m-i viind.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Eu viu, copaci, aici<text:line-break/>Cu lira-mi l-ati zefiri,<text:line-break/>Ca ajutat de dnii</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">S poci trimite-o od<text:line-break/>La cel ce v sdi</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4"><text:note text:id="ftn24" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>24</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
       <text:p text:style-name="P22"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aici i n continuare se refer la fostul domnitor Grigore Ghica, nmormntat n 1835.</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar, zefiri! La voi viu,<text:line-break/>La voi i iat-mi coarda<text:line-break/>Cum toat-n deteptare<text:line-break/>Numai p el visnd<text:line-break/>i-adaog puteri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Adiai, dulci zefiri!<text:line-break/>Venii n ast sear<text:line-break/>A flfi dasupra<text:line-break/>P-ast falnic monument.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i cu al filomilei<text:line-break/>Acel variat glas,<text:line-break/>Cntai o od lin<text:line-break/>L-acel mormnt preasfnt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Cntai a lui virtute,<text:line-break/>Cntai a lui dreptate,<text:line-break/>Ce plin de mrime<text:line-break/>n cer se nsemn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Sculai cu al lui nume<text:line-break/>Noroadele i lumea<text:line-break/>Ce subt a lui umbrire<text:line-break/>Fericele-au gustat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Nu v sfiii vrodat<text:line-break/>Ale-stui brbat fapte,<text:line-break/>Ce nu se sting cu moartea,<text:line-break/>Prea falnic s cntai.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iat-m eu n rontu-mi<text:line-break/>i dau acum tmia<text:line-break/>Ce-o vz mergnd d-a dreptul<text:line-break/>Pe frunte-i a fuma.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i el iat-l d-acolo<text:line-break/>Cu braele deschise<text:line-break/>Ca s-mi primeasc vine<text:line-break/>Ruga ce eu i fac.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Prin el acum cu cerul<text:line-break/>Vorbesc d-al lui ferice<text:line-break/>Ce dup el aicea<text:line-break/>Cu-al nostru l uni.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Auzi-l i d-acolo<text:line-break/>Cum stranic poruncete.<text:line-break/>Trimite-aici dreptatea<text:line-break/>S se-ncuibeze-n noi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Spunei c al su scaun<text:line-break/>Aci dasupra noastr<text:line-break/>n centrul miezei-zilei<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Vecinic i-a ntrit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cntai, -ecoa voastr<text:line-break/>Zboare, mearg-a se uni<text:line-break/>Cu armonia sfnt<text:line-break/>Ce umple-al lui auz.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cntai, la veacuri spunei,<text:line-break/>Spunei c vecinici marturi,<text:line-break/>Ct va tri pmntul,<text:line-break/>n veci l vei cnta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">C-odat aici un domn,<text:line-break/>Vrjma al nedreptii,<text:line-break/>Via c-un veac de aur<text:line-break/>n st norod tristat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i spunei la tot omul<text:line-break/>Ce soarta-l va-ndrepta<text:line-break/>Aci n preajma voastr,<text:line-break/>S calce-acest pmnt,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Spunei c-acel prea mare<text:line-break/>Brbat, rumn de snge,<text:line-break/>Ce-o lume-a fericit,<text:line-break/>Acum aicea st.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Subt ast rece piatr,<text:line-break/>Aci p-al su pmnt,<text:line-break/>Al Rumniei reazm<text:line-break/>Se-aaz adormit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar ns-a lui virtute<text:line-break/>Cea-n stele desinat<text:line-break/>i p pmnt viind<text:line-break/>Slujate de model.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">A ei curat fa<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>De aur, neptat,<text:line-break/>Brileaz dup dnsul<text:line-break/>n veacuri a-l numi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ferice de acela,<text:line-break/>Poet sau i istoric,<text:line-break/>Ce c-un brbat c-acesta<text:line-break/>Putu a se-nsemna.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i fr-a lua titluri<text:line-break/>Ce neagr pat nate,<text:line-break/>Ca ngeri drepi trecur<text:line-break/>n veacuri a se-nscri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ferice i d-acela<text:line-break/>Preanorocit norod,<text:line-break/>Ce la crmaci c-acesta<text:line-break/>Inima sa i-a dat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Vaz n el tiranii<text:line-break/>Prea marea-le ruine<text:line-break/>i spre-a lua iertare<text:line-break/>Aci caz-n genuchi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i dintre stele vaz-l<text:line-break/>Cum ochii-aici i-aint<text:line-break/>i contiina blnd<text:line-break/>Cum st la dreapta lui.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cum n a lui via<text:line-break/>P vremea-acea de foc<text:line-break/>Se strduia el singur<text:line-break/>O lume-a mulumi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i subt o lege blnd<text:line-break/>De dreapt-oblduire,<text:line-break/>Tot nmuiat n dafini<text:line-break/>n inimi guvern.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>D-auzi n capital,<text:line-break/>Numele lui rsun;<text:line-break/>Auzi, n ara toat,<text:line-break/>Pe urm-i tot jelind.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i zidurile astea<text:line-break/>Ce-n ele lumini nasc<text:line-break/>Vor spune-n multe veacuri<text:line-break/>C el le-a-ntemeiat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n ulii, n spitaluri,<text:line-break/>n inimi de sraci<text:line-break/>C-un sfnt tipar ast nume<text:line-break/>Va fi n veci spat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Strigri l-a sa rn simirea-mi scoate-acum.<text:line-break/>Iat-o e aintat, vie, toat-nfocat,<text:line-break/>Se salt s detepte, acum n miezul nopii,<text:line-break/>i prejmile s-aduc p piatr-a se-nchina.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Sonet l-a sa virtute rsun coard-acum,<text:line-break/>D-o nfocare sfnt auze-o bubuind.<text:line-break/>Spre-a-i nvia rna, lira-mi toat n munc<text:line-break/>Strig i iar rstrig, chemnd numele lui.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n monumenturi zgomot s-aude detunnd...<text:line-break/>i-n apele dorminde, n irul ast de tei...<text:line-break/>O eco vie vine, sunnd numele lui...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Triasc! auzi ea zice. Triasc! n vnt iar,<text:line-break/>Triasc! n cer s-aude. Triasc! iar n mal,<text:line-break/>Triasc! tot rsun, n veci numele lui...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Desprirea</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Lin, tritor miros din bolta senin s rvars n pieptu-mi ce, ocn de dureri, ofteaz dup-o <text:soft-page-break/>urm sfinit de aceea ce nu mai este aci! Galbena lumin a lunei eclipsite vars n mine trista-i umbr ce m-apas. Aci n snu-mi veted vine s-mi aduc lumina-i ce n-o sim! Tcerea afund acum vine s ndoiasc al meu amor fraged ce n veci eu am hrnit! Iat-aci pstorul, pe crja-i rzemat, doarme n turma-i dulce dincolo din ru; un car colo n vale p verde dejugat, ocolit de focuri i de rani culcai, st strejuit numai d-un cine deteptat ce latr, rspunde celui din ochi detept... Iat pavilonul ce ea i alesese. Iat malul colo ce ea ncunun. Aci ochiul zilii de dnsa ludat apuse n departe, dup-acel mal rpos; d-aci sfinirea-i ieri, de ea bine zis, plec s vesteasc Sirena ce vzu; ieri deteapta und, ce acum departe a ajuns, trecu cu al ei nume pe grabnicul su ru. Iat colo piatra pe care ea azat, trist, toat n gnduri, prea dulce suspina. O, dulce rcoare, ce urma-i parfum! Sfnt, rcoros senin, ce eu nu poci gusta! unde este aceea ce ieri te nbia? Ce taci? Spune, Noapte, ce face ea acum?...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Ei bine! numele ei l tiu! Eu nu voi un nume ce toate mi-l rspund, eu nu voi icoana-mi ce-n umbr-mi e n veci; eu voi numai o tire de ceea ce ea acum n pace gndete, cnd eu departe snt...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Ah! ea poate acuma, n braele de so, strnge pe acela ce nu a fost al ei, dar eu, neroditor, n lume rtcit, ca prundul acesta ars de piatr, nisip, trsc subt cer trupu-mi, ce, putred de dureri i n veci n chin oftnd, ca moate a ajuns!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Scump objet, ce n lume eu nu te poci avea! nger ce n mine crarea ai aflat! Floarea omenirii -a sexului tu! Steaua lirii mele i viu-mi Dumnezeu! Eu nu mai poci n ascuns acum s te iubesc, nu mai poci n tain acum a te slvi? Strig, o spui de fa, c tu eti care n lume, tu eti ce n via pe mine astzi ii! Prieteug, amor, religie, respect, virtutea ntreag n tine am cunoscut!!! Legile tale mi plac! Fiarele-i snt scumpe! Pieptu-i, buntatea, i gura-i e nectar! Ochii ti ca pacea, verzi de tineree, aprind foc n pieptu-mi i setea d-a-i privi! Tu eti ce n lume cerul mi ari! Tu ce n tot locul eu vz necontenit. O, sfnt fiin, ce raiul mi vesteti! Dulce zeitate ce sufletu-mi ncni! De ce nu poci cu tine n lume s fiu! S vz a ta ctare, s sorb a ta suflare, s uit reaua-mi soart, pe pieptul tu s mor?</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Meditaia X: Moartea </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">nger grabnic al tarelui cabinet! Sol urcios al iesmosului lca! Negru ministru al tribunalului rspltitor! Repede fulger purttor de-ntunerec! Noptoas, spimnttoare, nevzut sgeat ce desfiinezi fiinele! Unde duci tu vieele ce scoi din trupuri? Pe care pmnt transpori aceea ce nu tii purta? Cu ce mijloc poi tu duce cu tine acea lumin a crii fa tu n-o poi vedea?...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Blestem groaznec, rspltitor pcatului lui Adam! Pentru tine muncile neosteninde; ie <text:soft-page-break/>fgduielile-i, cu tine odihna ntunerecului. Fugi, sfiete-te de cel ce te urte; deprteaz-te de cel ce nu te cheam; tremur de puternica lumin ce vezi n mine. Nu, nu este nici o vreme, nici un ceas n care s fii chemat. Odihna-i nu o voi, fericirea-i nu-mi trebuie. Fantom spimnttoare! Groaznec hrpitor de fericirea ce cerul drui nesimirii! Trate-te, pustiile fie al tu lca. nceteaz odat de a-i nvrti nfricoata coas prin mpopulatele vetre; vezi sfiat rmia ce lai lng prada ta; auzi duioasele rcnete ce-i urmeaz urlnd; auzi prinii, fiii, fraii, prietenii nenorociilor sugrumai de tine cum te blestem; vezi c nu este nici o form subt care s fii dorit; fie-n biruine, fie-n nenorociri, n dezndejde, n rzbunare, n fericiri, n averi, n neaveri, tot o icoan pori!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Ei bine! asta e moartea. Apoi s poate ca dreptul creator s hotrasc la tot omul a ei necesar fa, fr s contribuiasc la a lui fericire? Se poate vecinicul Tat, blndul oblduitor acela, s hotrasc la toat fiina acest groaznec pahar, fr-a vedea un tot aa mare bun ntr-nsul? Nu, nu, Stpne, ce vecinica moarte ai omort! Chibzuirilor tale celor sfinte nu este fiin care p drept s le poat mputa. Nu, Printe! st nestrmutat hotar! ntre valoroasa, vremelniceasc via i ntre vecinica ta nemurire trebuia negreit s fie. Nu, tu nicidecum nu vei primi a pune ast urcioas putere ca s nghi pentru totdauna, n vecinic nesimire, duhovniceasca acea lumin, ce singur, de buna-i voie, druieti fiinelor. Nu, ea nu are mai mult putere dect s fac o prefacere. Asta nu e moarte, este un paznic ce ne transpoart n nemurire din curitorul loc ce l numim lume, n care sntem venii numai s ne splm de nesimire, ca s putem trece n a ta vecinicie; asta nu e via, este un puin mai luminos loc dect nesimirea, prin care, curindu-se de ntunerec, sufletele ce nviai s poat trece n vecinica nemurire ce li se hotr, fr-a cerca acea greutate ce cearc ochiul nchisului subt pmnt la cea dinti vedere a soarelui. Dar, oameni! acolo ne e locul cel hotrt de Dreptul, acolo, de fa cu nevzutul aici Printe, vom cunoate adevrul care att de ntunecat ni s povestete aici, subt felurimi de neadevrate descrieri! Dar, Doamne! taie-mi frica de st singur mijloc prin care poci dobndi ce-mi fgduii! F simirile mele a preui ast bun, ast sfnt instrument ce aa lesne precurm chinurile i vars adevrata fericire!...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Meditaia XI: Schimbarea soartii </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Soarele dulce acum rsare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n pieptu-mi veted ce-abia suspin;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Luceafr falnic acum pate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n drumul negru ce m-a crescut.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aur lin acum se vede,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Negura piere n car-eram;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin raza zilii via-mi simire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acum zrete drumul la cer.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dureri! necazuri! din snul vostru</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Al meu ferice acum eu aflu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din voi eu traiul din cer lsatul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din voi eu tritea-mi acum primesc!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah! Fac cerul ca aste chinuri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce pn-acum am suferit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca nite visuri ce nu s-ntoarce,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca rul grabnic piar-n trecut.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu ele rele; cu ele patimi;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu ele noaptea din car-ieii;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Via dulce, via lin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Via nou acum s gust.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Chinuri, pedepse, acum departe</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Le vz ca valuri ce se rscoal,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se lupt, se salt ca s nghit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe dezbarcatul cnd e la port.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Meditaia XII: Declaraia </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Verde pnz nsmlteaz rcoroasele dealuri. Trufa, stejarul, ca un mprat al arburilor, flfiie amerintor. Luna, ca o insul de flcri, izbete plin n albitele unde ce o mpart nzgomotate. Stelele toate, nestrmutate, pzesc armonia ce li s hotr...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Iat una pic! Fi-va doar a mea?...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Coboar-te, negru meteor! strivete-i nenorocitul!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Dar ce! un nor se nal de-a dreapta-mi. Negru ca un munte de plumb, neac luna! nfulgerat de trsnete, tun i rstun n bolele d-aram. Tun, i c-acele din iad organe, lung rzbubuie n muni. Eco le-nsoete i, ca urlet de cutremur, rsurl n pieptu-mi obosit!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Cdea-va el p mine? Caz, c eu l primesc! Dar ce glas s-aude?... Un cobitor mister mormie n uriaa stnc...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Destul! mi zice, las vinovatele gnduri. Trebuie s-l ascult? iNu! nu, mpeliat mister! sta e norul ce m ine n ast vin! sta e, i trebuie s se sparg-odat! Dincolo de el e luna-mi, i eu trebuie s-l despic! M duc! Dar ce! trsnet dodat scap din tartara negur, nnemerit izbete n cremenea stncii, cu trosnet o sfrm i iat-o n buci...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:soft-page-break/>P mine ochea ast trsnet!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Fie! cremenea vecin s sfrm, dar hotrrea-mi, mai tare dect ea, rmne nestrmutat! Ca Mar nfuriat alerg s-mi omor rstritea! Astzi, dar astzi negreit, precum o soart de Tantal, astzi, sau clcnd iadul ce m-neac gust cerul cel adevrat, sau ca acel obraznic Gigant gsesc vecinicul Tartar,  m duc!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Ei bine, iat am ajuns, iat ceasul, iat cerul, iat iadul, vai! fiori din unghii pn-n cretet m petrec numaidect! Mai nesimitor dect trsnit stnc, rmi ncremenit!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Ceasul e aproape a trece, i eu, slab, fr putere... cer ajutor...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Meterul Manole </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Manole, Manole,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Metere Manole,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zidul ru m strnge,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ioara-mi curge,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copilau-mi plnge.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Manole, Manole!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vara toat stau la munc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Meteri ci n ar snt;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iarna lucrul tot se stric,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Osteneala merge-n vnt.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Toat lumea e-n veghere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i s mir n tcere.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Neagul-Vod poruncete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i s jur-n Dumnezeu:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sau c zidul se-ntrete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sau c mor cum e mai ru;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci e chiar o dievolie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mnstirea s nu ie.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Meterii se-nfiorar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-ncepur-a se gndi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum s fac s nu moar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci ei mine n-or mai fi.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Neagul-Vod ce vorbete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Negreit c se-mplinete.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Meterul Manole-ncepe</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iscusit a le vorbi;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci el singur se pricepe</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce ispit poate fi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De se surp peste gloat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-au lucrat o var toat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">De cuvnt s am eu parte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Meteri buni, m ascultai!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Omenie aib foarte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fiecare dintre frai:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cere zidul o muiere,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca s-i fie-ntemeiere!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mine-n zid s se zideasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mcar care din femei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce va fi s se iveasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu merinzi, la soul ei!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Meterii se spimntar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-ochii-n jos cu toi lsar.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stai pe loc! i fr fric,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu credin s jurai!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C din voi nici unu stric</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fapt-aceasta ce-apucai!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La primejdia obteasc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Trebuie unul s jrtfeasc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sufletu-i s se uneasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu al Iudii la un loc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i rina-i n-o priimeasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici pmnt, nici vint, nici foc!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Blestemat fie-n vecie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cel ce-o spune la soie!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ei cu toii se jurar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum c taina nu o vnd</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i apoi se-mbriar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fr-a zice vrun cuvnt;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar, sunt muli d-i fr fric</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-astzi jur, mine stric.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu nevasta fiecare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ncepu a se vorbi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S nu vie cu mncare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn seara va murgi.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar Manole-a ei venire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O ls la norocire.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Meterii se mai adun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn-n ziu, la zidit;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-ucenicii mpreun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Toi cu toii au venit!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ns tuturor l-e fric</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A zidi, cci iar se stric.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Soarele ctre amiaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ncepu a-nainta,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i Manole-atunci s-aaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De unelte a-i cta:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Frai, ncepem a zidi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci sntem n miaz zi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Punei mna pe mistrie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Calfe, ucenici idem,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci se vede o soie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu ti-a cui din ci sntem.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Calea toi o aintar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar pe loc s-astmprar.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci e Ua, credincioas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Meterului cel cinstit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce soia-i cea frumoas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La frie a jertfit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De cnd ea se mritase</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un an numai apucase.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O lu de mn-ndat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i pe zid o ntrept;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum s stea apoi i-arat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-a zidi se apuc.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fie dragoste sau fric,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea cuvntul nu i-l stric.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ceilali meteri n mirare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Toi cu groaz l privesc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i stau toi n deprtare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci aproape nu-ndrznesc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd el dulce i vorbete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cu grab o zidete.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ast glum nu e bun,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Manole, iubitul meu;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te gndete c sunt mum</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i c cresc pe fiul tu.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar Manole tot glumete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ct poate se grbete.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn la piept el o zidise</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ea dulce i cnta,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zidul tare o strivise</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ea-n lacrmi nota.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar acum se isprvete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zidul mai o covrete.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Asta fuse lecuirea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zidul d-a putea inea;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i d-atuncea mnstirea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ncet d-a mai cdea.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vnt, cutremur n-o smintete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ua-n zid o sprijinete.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Neagul-Vod cheltuise</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Toat-averea, s credei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-nc nu se isprvise</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mnstirea ce vedei.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se bocete ca muiere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i Manole i tot cere.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Doamna Despa atunci scoate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din urechi ai si cercei;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Na, Manole, de se poate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prinde tu ce tii p ei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Numai vezi de aurete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mnstirea -isprvete.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd Manole de pe cruce</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Darul merse d-i lu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dan i Iau-ncet se duce,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Scara-n mii c sfrm.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pizma tot la rele nate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i pe frai i vrjmate.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Meterul n turburare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aripi ndat-i lucr,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-avnt cu o zburare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-uite colo mi-i pic.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stana lui cea mrmurit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ne d ap lmurit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">O cltorie </text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I9"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Era frumoas seara-n acea cltorie!<text:line-break/>Ce gnduri dulci viseaz, ce plan de veselie<text:line-break/>i face-un cltor,<text:line-break/>Cnd ntmplarea-l duce ca s cltoreasc<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cu chiar acea fiin ce-ncepe s iubeasc<text:line-break/>i va-i jura amor!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Mult timp acum trecuse de cnd nu mai iubisem<text:line-break/>Eram la toate rece i harpa-mi prsisem;<text:line-break/>Uram orice-ntlneam;<text:line-break/>Dar cerul ne pstreaz cte-o fiin nou,<text:line-break/>Cu care ne ntoarce cnd o arat nou<text:line-break/>Sub forma ce iubeam.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Aa trimite rou ce ud, rcorete<text:line-break/>O floare vetejit de-aria ce-o prlete,<text:line-break/>-o-ntoarce napoi.<text:line-break/>Dar, pentru toat fapta-i se ine, se pstreaz<text:line-break/>Pe tain cte-o rou, prin care renviaz<text:line-break/>i plantele i noi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">El totdauna are o aur-ncropit<text:line-break/>Cu care s-nclzeasc natura amorit<text:line-break/>De crudul Achilon;<text:line-break/>Prin stele el d faruri acelui ce plutete<text:line-break/>Pe valuri furioase, -atunci cnd rtcete,<text:line-break/>I-ardic pavilion.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II9"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Aura ce-mi da via era o rsuflare<text:line-break/>Numai parfum i balsam: gndeam c printr-o floare<text:line-break/>Rsufl un zefir.<text:line-break/>Ochii ei mi erau fari; snul ei, pavilionul;<text:line-break/>Eu o priveam pe dnsa ca un diadoh tronul:<text:line-break/>Triam ntr-un delir!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O s m cerc a spune ce fel de frumusee<text:line-break/>Avea ast fecioar; dar unde gsesc fee!...<text:line-break/>Ctai n lord Byron,<text:line-break/>La ovreieti armonii: acolo se gsete<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Portret-unei evreice; prea mult se potrivete<text:line-break/>Fecioara de Sion</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu tnra-mi vergin. Nici Eufrat, nici Iordanul,.<text:line-break/>Nici soarele cel ager ce-a-mpodobit Libanul<text:line-break/>Nu crez s fi produs<text:line-break/>Mai vii ochi i mai negri. Platanul nu pstreaz.<text:line-break/>Pieli mai curat; Coranul nu viseaz<text:line-break/>Huria ce-a propus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Nici cu un pr mai negru, nici cu organ mai dulce;<text:line-break/>O zn mai plcut la fii ce-or s se culce, <text:line-break/>n somn,  nu le poftim.<text:line-break/>Cine-a produs-o, nu tiu; hurie sau perie,<text:line-break/>tiu c gndesc la dnsa, i sim o bucurie<text:line-break/>Eu i zic heruvim.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="III5"/>III</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T8">Noi ncepusem drumul i mergeam spre apus.<text:line-break/>Se-nchise rsritul, i numa cte-o raz,<text:line-break/>Slab i tremurnd, se ntorcea s vaz<text:line-break/>O urm ce lsase soarele ce s-a dus.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Muni de rubin, unde monarhul s-ascunsese<text:line-break/>Ca s priveasc luna, n preajm-le-ntinsese<text:line-break/>Doi ntini oceani<text:line-break/>De purpur i flcri, unde plutea mulimea<text:line-break/>Ostroavelor de aur. n urm-albea desimea<text:line-break/>De aburi n troiani.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Luna,-n convoi de stele, se nla p-un cer<text:line-break/>Albastru, sfiicioas, ca un monarh fecioar<text:line-break/>Cnd priimete sceptrul ce i ncredinar;<text:line-break/>Astfel venea Diana s ia un emisfer.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Gonea ncet din urm umbrele rtcite<text:line-break/>Care-i cta azilul pe sub vi zugrvite<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cu felurimi de flori,<text:line-break/>Unde juca zefirii. Mirosea universul.<text:line-break/>Privighetoarea nopii-i dregea subt frunz viersul.<text:line-break/>Plcerea da fiori,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd pasrile zilei p-a nopii deteptau;<text:line-break/>Cnd se-ntrecea potaii n fuga cea mai mare;<text:line-break/>Cnd munii i colnicii fugeau n urm tare<text:line-break/>i cnd strigri n coruri pdurea spimntau,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Zna-mi fugea-nainte, eu fugeam dupe dnsa;<text:line-break/>Izbea d-a dreptu-n mine rsufletul dintr-nsa.<text:line-break/>De ce-nti s m mir!<text:line-break/>Ea-i ntorcea adesea capul s m priveasc:<text:line-break/>Prea c este-o nimf, o nimf cmpeneasc,<text:line-break/>Gonit de-un satir!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">O diminea pe malul lacului </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">1836</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Frumoas diminea! Suflarea-toat tace!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Abia privighetoarea, c-un glas rsuntor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S turbure cuteaz o solemnel pace,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd somnu-i aa dulce la omul muncitor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Glbuia auror de purpur urmat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Albete nverzita dumbrav de anin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i stele licurinde abia se mai arat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin umbrele ce noaptea pstreaz n senin.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n lacul dinainte-mi, un cer se adnceaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i las pe oglind-i abia a mai luci</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fcliile murinde sub pnza ce albeaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Al nopii ntunerec ce-ncepe a fugi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">D-a dreapta-mi stau Carpaii ascuni afund n cea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din aburi cu ncetul ncep a se ivi;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zpada lor cea veche, ce vara n-o dezghea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i suie-n cer troienii, sau st a-i prvli!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar Prahova devale n mii de grli se-mparte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-ntins arginteaz ast prunt al ei pietros;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n vile-i afunde s-aude ndeparte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O eco ngnat pe malul cel rpos.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Frumoase! sfinte locuri! de ce i ast dat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-avei tot acel fermec!... Pe cine oari jelii?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A timpilor via nu vine c-altdat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-nvie-a voastre plante? De ce v vetejii?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce suspin vntul? Dumbrava ce ofteaz?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce mugete rul i locul s-a negrit?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce oricare preajm subt nori se-mpovreaz?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce ast doliu mare natura a-nvlit?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O! unde este timpul cnd, plin de tineree,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n braele fecioarei, fecioarei ce iubeam,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sorbeam al vostru balsam -a voastr frumusee</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rpea a mea simire pe snul ce-adoram.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">E-al aptelea an sta de cnd, n aste locuri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Gustam o fericire ce nu voi mai cerca;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar vrsta i simirea, -acele tineri focuri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce pier, se sting cu timpul,  ncep a m lsa.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un lucru de nimica, o mic nlucire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Priveam de lucru mare, de toate m-ncntam;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acum sunt trist i rece, i nu am mulumire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici chiar la fericirea ce-atunci nu cunoteam.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n viaa lui o dat oricine i iubete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i simte de iubire, i poate a iubi; </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Simirea nainte se trece,-mbtrnete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i corpul dup dnsa ncepe-a s-ofili.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Obiectul ce atuncea putea s le-ndulceasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acuma e departe,  s-a-ntors d-unde-a venit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aa e fericirea: ea vine s goneasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Odihna num-a noastr, i-ndat-a i pierit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Frumoas ca un angel ce cerul ne arat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Era abia n vrst s-atepte-un mritat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cine a vzut-o a trebuit ndat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-i dea acea cunun ce-att a meritat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca prim-acea zpad ce cade afinat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe locuri nembiate l-al soarelui ivit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Era oricare parte-i plpnd i curat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i snu-i d-alabastru n veci era-nvlit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici cerul cel mai dulce n noaptea cea senin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd norii dorm departe cu vnturile-n ei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i bolta-i luminat de luna cea mai plin, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu are-un alabastru ca cel din ochii ei.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">D-apuc acum mtasea, deloc nu m-nfioar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici este pipitu-i att de voluptos</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-acele fire netezi din bucla-i cea uoar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce rtcea pe snu-i divin i graios.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-nsinuia ctarea-i, cnd vrea ca s-mi zmbeasc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Subt rumena ei buz de foi de trandafir,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mrgritar nu poate, gndesc, s se gseasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A fi att de luciu i neted ntr-un ir.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Deloc nu ne neal acel care ne spune</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C faa ne arat ce-avem n noi ascuns;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Natura nu ne minte: aceea ce depune</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n inima oricrui, pe fa-i st expus.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aa de simitoare la o nenorocire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C d-ar fi fost n mn-i, durere-ar fi lipsit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea nu ura pe nimeni; ntreaga-i fericire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Era s poat face pe altul norocit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin geana ei cea lung o ngereasc mil</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prea c s coboar pe oameni a jeli;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La tot nenorocitul, vedeai c-i face-o sil</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-ascunz-a ei durere, pe ali a nu mhni.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nenorociri strine vedeam c o omoar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe frunte-i sta durerea a oricrui strin; </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De n-a fi cunoscut-o de crim c-i fecioar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A fi gndit c-un cuget revolt-al ei venin.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">A! fugi, fiin drag! Departe d-ast lume!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aci nu era locu-i, tu-n drum ai rtcit;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aci sunt toate altfel,nimic n-are-al su nume; </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Virtutea este-o crim, natura a pierit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce i eu cu tine, n tnra junie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd toate-mi prea bune, cnd toat-era amor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce n-a fost atuncea s scap din viclenie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S las amara-mi via, cu tine-n sferi s zbor?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce Dumnezeu oar a dat n om putina</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S ie suvenirea de cele ce-au trecut?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce s nu se piarz dodat cu fiina</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i toat suvenirea acelor ce-am pierdut?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Orice vieuitoare iubete primvara;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Al meu amor e vecinic i iarna nu l-a stins;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se nate dimineaa, l indoiete seara,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n veci e frde moarte, n veci este aprins.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">O lacrim </text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I10"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Inima ce ptimete<text:line-break/>D-un suvenir nempcat;<text:line-break/>Inima a crii ran<text:line-break/>S-a nchis vremelnicete;<text:line-break/>Inima ce nc-i hran<text:line-break/>Viermelui ce-o otrvete,<text:line-break/>Prin lacrima ce-a vrsat</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Simte c s-a uurat.<text:line-break/>Cnd va inima s spuie<text:line-break/>Ct de mult s-a ntristat<text:line-break/>i c-n tot prpstii vede, <text:line-break/>Atunci cnd, ca s supuie<text:line-break/>Pe acela ce n-o crede,<text:line-break/>Vro alt speran nu e,<text:line-break/>Prin lacrima ce-a vrsat<text:line-break/>Simte c l-a-nduplecat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Atunci cnd inima bate<text:line-break/>Pe un piept nflcrat<text:line-break/>i se-mbat de plcere;<text:line-break/>Cnd iubitul va s-arate<text:line-break/>Amorul ce altu-i cere<text:line-break/>i gurile sunt legate,<text:line-break/>Prin lacrima ce-a vrsat<text:line-break/>Parc s-a ndestulat.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II10"/><text:soft-page-break/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O, vezi lacrima-mi i crede<text:line-break/>C eu nu te-am nelat!<text:line-break/>Inima n-are-alt limb<text:line-break/>Pentru-acela ce n-o vede.<text:line-break/>Atunci cnd a ta se schimb,<text:line-break/>A mea toat se prevede,<text:line-break/>Spune tot ce a rbdat<text:line-break/>Prin lacrima ce-a vrsat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Era neleas-odat<text:line-break/>Ast limb ce-ai uitat;<text:line-break/>inea loc de jurminte<text:line-break/>Cnd da gura ncletat<text:line-break/>Suspin n loc de cuvinte;<text:line-break/>O, privirea-i flcrat<text:line-break/>De cte ori m-a-ncntat<text:line-break/>Lacrima ce ai vrsat!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Aste suflete, odat,<text:line-break/>Pe buz-i s-au srutat;<text:line-break/>i, din inima-i fecioar,<text:line-break/>Curgea lacrima curat,<text:line-break/>Care nc m-nfioar<text:line-break/>Cnd n minte-mi se arat;<text:line-break/>De crezi c te-am nelat<text:line-break/>Vezi lacrima ce-am vrsat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pentru orice ndoial<text:line-break/>Vezi lacrima ce-a picat:<text:line-break/>E c-atuncea de fierbinte!<text:line-break/>Numai lacrima nu-nal,<text:line-break/>Numai lacrima nu minte!<text:line-break/>Pentru orice bnuial<text:line-break/>Inima-mi i-a artat<text:line-break/>Lacrima ce a vrsat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Omu-o vars-n bucurie,<text:line-break/>Ca i cnd e ntristat.<text:line-break/>Numai o simire-o stoarce<text:line-break/>Din inimi n agonie;<text:line-break/>Arde ns, cnd se-ntoarce<text:line-break/>n dureri o bucurie:<text:line-break/>Cearc-aceasta ce-am vrsat<text:line-break/>i vezi de te-am nelat.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">O iganc cu pruncul su la statua libertii n Bucureti </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Uite, maic, i surde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Uite, fiul meu iubit!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rzi, c ziua i-e senin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rzi, c viaa i e lin!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De stpni, cu bici de gde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu, tu nu-i fi chinuit!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Du la gur i srut</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ast bilet, ast snt odor</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-i d drepturi i dreptatea!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Faa ta e Libertatea;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Curcubeu de zi plcut</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E stindardul tricolor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, Doamne! liber, oar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Liber este fiul meu?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-a s sim el robia,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-a s sim tirania,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Viaa trist i amar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Viaa care-am trit eu?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vezi tu, maic, ce icoan!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aa este Dumnezeu.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Asta-i snta Libertate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stnd i dnd la toi dreptate!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe tirani i-a pus pe goan,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ne-a spart lan i jugul greu.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Jur-i, maic-,a ta guri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">P-ast stindard, pe snul meu:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-o s-o aperi tu la mare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-o s-i fii un reazem tare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-i dai via i credin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-o s-i fie Dumnezeu!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Patria, n libertate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce te face cetean,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O s vaz al tu snge</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C i-l veri, cnd s-o atinge</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Legea ei ce d dreptate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca un nobil pmntean.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Jur eu astzi pentru tine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Jur eu, maic,-n locul tu!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Jurimntu-mi fie-i Crezul!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Asta fie-i tot botezul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce te duce-n cer la bine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce te mntuie de ru!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Jur s aibi recunotin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ctre fraii ti romni,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce te scot azi din robie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te primesc &apos;n a lor frie;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Uit-a noastr umilin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-am fost vite la stpni.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">S triasc Romnia</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce ne ia n snul ei!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Noi, ce nu eram n lege,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din fii liberi nu ne-alege;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-a ucis de veci robia</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cumpliii farisei!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Ocna</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Telega, 1843, septembrie 6</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">ncongiurat de paznici, cu fiarele-n picioare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu minile-n ctue, de gt cu lanul greu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un om frumos la fa, n spasmuri, n fioare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aci cruntnd la paznici, aci zmbind la soare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Czu la gura ocnei chemnd pe Dumnezeu.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i o durere-ascuns, durere sufleteasc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mustrarea, disperarea juca pe faa sa.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i mai mrea n sil durerea cea trupeasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voind s mai aline, voind s liniteasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A sufletului ran ce nu se vindeca.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se afunda n gnduri, srea strignd: Maria!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Maria nu e moart!... intea un pzitor...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se veselea pe clip, uita atunci urgia,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se azvrlea spre dnsul, i-n ochii-i bucuria</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rdea cum rde raza cnd scap printre nor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce bun ai fost tu, Doamne, cnd ai sdit iubirea!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce crud ai fost tu, Doamne, cnd moarte ai rostit!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sau a plcerii numai s fi avut simirea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sau de dureri trecute s pierdem suvenirea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sau omul s nu tie deloc cnd a greit!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, voi ce-avei puterea s osndii o vin!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Gndii c l-ast vin al lumii Creator</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu a prescris osnda?  Cnd sufletul suspin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sub lovituri de cuget, a voastre munci alin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Durerea din nuntru  sunt balsam, sunt favor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din ghizdurile ocnei, pe funia srat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe funia ce duce pe oameni n tartar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Legar osnditul n manta-i cea marcat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-l slobozir-n gura cea neagr, fiorat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spre moartea inventat n timpul cel barbar.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se nvrtete roata i scripetele zboar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n vitri sinistre, avnt fiortor, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca cucuvaia nopii ce flfie uoar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ip peste capul acelui ce-a s moar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se viet pre capu-i cu glas ngrozitor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe gtul lung al ocnei s-exal infectate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Durerea, agonia, suspinuri i fiori.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i oaspele s-afund pe ci ntunecate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n rsetele-acelor fpturi denaturate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce s-au deprins la crime a fi executori.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se mrginete gtul i caosul se-ntinde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i oameni ca insecte, ca licurici lucesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu focuri n spinare, cu feele murinde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe bolovani n trmbe, pe stncile sclipinde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe munii cei de sare pe care se muncesc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se leagn cluul i liliacul zboar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Alunic ca umbr prin norii cei srai</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin care osnditul, ce spaima l doboar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se las n zstimpuri, se strnge, se-nfioar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ncovoiat pre coard cu perii ardicai!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Are s mearg nc, cci fundul e departe!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cer i ziua lumii se vd albind ca stea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce palid i fix n negure dearte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Albete cteodat, ca steaua ce-i mparte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-ascunde-n cer schinteia cnd soare e sub e.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Locuitorii nopii cu feele plite</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i las bolovanii i vin de-l ncongiur;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu luminri n cretet, cu barbele zburlite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Proi pe brae, piepturi, cu haine zdrenuite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Buhavi de umezeal, dau roat mpregiur,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Clipind la luminare i mestecnd tutunul.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu glasuri ngroate urlar rguit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Blestem i anateme, cci le furar bunul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci le hrpir ziua, cci nu putea nici unul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S vaz la lumin pe cel ce-a mai venit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Apoi trr-n noapte i pe clu legar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un mort ce se umflase, un trup de vinovat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te du, bdi,-i zise, n lume este var,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E soare, e lumin. Civa l srutar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ncepu s ipe machina fiorat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Optzeci erau la numr fpturile uitate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe care omenirea la iad a osndit;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Optzeci pe care legea, cretina caritate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Regenerarea rei i stricta echitate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A smuls de vii din lume i-n ocn a pornit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Optzeci mai rmsese; optzeci era-n picioare.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ceilali gemeau n lacuri i fr ajutor.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Chema la dnii moartea, scorbutul s-i doboare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cad reumatismul junghie, cci agonia doare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci sunt aci pe via, moartea e viaa lor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vai mie!  striga-n limb-l, btndu-se n sare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i mai gonind nduful, un orb israelit </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vai mie! dai-mi ap, c-mi este sete tare!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i un cretin d-alturi ce-i da a sa suflare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">li spuse, dndu-i mna, c apa s-a sfrit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se adunar-n noapte confraii n durere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i smulser cu grij din cuiburile lor</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cte vreo dou paie, ca singura avere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce ei posed n ocn, i-n larga ncpere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Adogar cuibul d-un nou locuitor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Era blai i june martirul ce venise</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i trase simpatia acelor ce-l zri.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum seamn c-un frate ce am acas!  zise</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un flciandru ager ce umezeal-albise, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S fim noi frai de cruce ct ne-om mai chinui!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar spune-ne, mi vere, ce vin aa mare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fcut-ai tu n lume? Nu tinui nimic,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-aci e obiceiul s spuie fiecare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pcatele-i din lume; i mie cum mi pare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu nu eti ho de codru; ai vrun pcat mai mic.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">nfricoata cale ce junele fcuse</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i dase iar simirea, i-n suvenirea lui</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prea c se strecoar procesul ce trecuse,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Durerea, fericirea i cte petrecuse:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu n-am hrpit, mi frate, averea nimului.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Am fost crescut acas n larg, n destulare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prinii mei cu cinste triau n satul lor.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eram flcu n hor, frunta cu stare mare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu cal de clrie i alii de-nhmare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Motean, la prini unul, triam un trai uor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prinii biet, srmanii, voiau s m nsoare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">mi tot spuneau de fete, dar nu-mi gseam pe plac</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M tot plimbam prin sate, mergeam la eztoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd vz odat o fat, ce-n ochii ei, ca-n soare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S cat nu fu putin. O vz aci i tac.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">M tot codeam prin cas, spuneam la fete glume;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M dam pe lng dnsa, dar nu-i puteam vorbi.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Roea de-i prindeam ochii, sau m striga pe nume</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fetiile zburdalnici! Ca ea frumoas-n lume</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i mndr i ginga gndesc c n-a mai fi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ct vru s ias-afar fetia rumeoar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu sai -o iau n brae i parc fu a mea.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O strng i ea-mi rspunde. O iau la subioar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i fug, cci era mic, ca peana de uoar;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btea sub -i pieptul i gura i ardea.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ajung cu ea acas -o bag la alde tata;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aci o vzui bine i tare mi plcu.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu mi-am gsit nevast. V place vou fata?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Trimitei la mo popa, c nunta este gata;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S nu-ntrebai ce are i cine o fcu.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">M srutar-ndat prinii n urare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i eu i cu Maria puparm mna lor.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">D-aci apoi plecarm, fcurm nunt mare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i strnserm o plas s vie-n desftare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci mndr l-era nora i june-al lor fecior.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vreo dou luni trecusem cu ea n csnicie;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd pe o lun plin ce peste noi plutea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ne desftam sub cerg ascuni pe deal n vie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ne glumeam atta, cu-atta veselie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nct i luna pare cu drag c ne privea.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar somnul citeodat aduce grele vise!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ntr-nsul necuratul i joac ooada sa!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se vede c norase i nimeni nu simise;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci ploaia nu-ncepuse, dar trsnetul izbise</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un nuc btrn n preajm, i cinele ltra.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mie-mi pru deodat Maria spriat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C strig, i la dnsa se d un lup turbat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Apuc n zpcire securea rezemat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De cptiul nostru, izbesc pe biata fat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Care dormea n pace. O dat a ipat!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aci s-opri voinicul i perii-i se zburlir,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cearcne de snge rotir ochii si,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i dinii i scrnir, i muchii tresrir,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i spume de balaur pe gura lui ieir,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nrile-i deschise zvrlea n toi vpi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Od la baia lui Ercule </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">(Mehadia)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Izvor de via nou i demn d-orice cntare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De unde-i vine cursul cu ast fierbntare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lichidul gumvital?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pucioas, fier ce-mprim n marmur calaiul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prelins din Etna este, sau Ecla-i ine traiul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce ocne de metal?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin unda-i cea fierbinte, re-ntorci tu oari din via?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Re-ntorci puteri din moarte?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A btrneii ghea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vii tu a re-nclzi? Eti ramur din focul ce totul crmuiete?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De unde-i iei puterea?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce soare te-nclzete? Ce mn te porni?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe frigul lui Aheron, de care tot se teme,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aduni scntei din viaa ce moartea fr vreme</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i tineri nebolii O las trecnd la iaduri?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eti poarta-eternitii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La care vine omul s lege firul vieii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu viei din cei pierii?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici Baia, nici Abano, ce unda-i erpuiete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n opt-armonioas i pacinic prvlete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Timavul linitit, nu au a ta putere.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici chiar acea fntn</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-n Rinul lin i vars prea ludat vn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unde Corol s-a mrit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd unda ta cea cald, n colciri spumate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La obrie-i fierbe cristaluri colorate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-ntinde curcubeu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ntocmai ca-ntr-acela ce curm vijelia,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bolnavu-n el privete sperana, bucuria</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i chiar pe Dumnezeu.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Puternice printe! n oriice schimbare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe globul sta-i face, pstreaz-a ei izvoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A nu i le slei!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Curgi, curgi fntn lin ct va inea tria!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">L-a viaa-ne cea scurt, mai d din vecinicia</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce ceru-i drui!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btrnului cel grbov, ce-n cale oviete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai d-i din nou via i sngele-nclzete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i f-l a mai tri!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fecioarei ofilite ce patima o stinge,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai d-i vioiciunea, i f ci te-or atinge</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Puteri a dobndi!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Patria</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Atena, 20 august 1850</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fie neam orict de mare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fie neam, francez, englez,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Neam mai mndru i mai tare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca romnul eu nu crez.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Neamu-n care nate-oricine</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe acela va iubi!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eti romn? voi fi cu tine;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-s romn, i-n veci voi fi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Las s-mi cnte musclimea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mine, urii, gheaa lor;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Las s-i laude nemimea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rinul i acel Tirol;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spuie-i Francia avuia,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Grecii cerul zmbitor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Englitera industria;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sunt romn, romn s mor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dulce cer c-al rii mele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Veseli muni i vin hrnit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai livezi, mai holde grele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai fetie de iubit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zic cine orice-o zice,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">P-alt ar n-om gsi!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dai-mi, dai a ei colnice,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-s romn pn-oi muri!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">ara mea din balt-n munte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se rsfa-n avuii.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Brazii verzi i rd pe frunte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Istru-i car bogii.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ruri, grle, ca cosie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Plete, plete se cobor</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn-n poale-i, n lungi vie;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lng ele voi s mor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">ara mea vestit-n lupte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Armele deloc n-o mint;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe grli, malurile-i rupte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Curge aur i argint.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Flota-i ar umplea Euxinul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spre Colhide, pe Bosfor!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Batei, batei-i tocsinul1!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aprnd-o voi s mor!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Pe piatra mormntal </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">A DEI C. FILIPESCU, n.BAL</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P15"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Orict vei fi de grabnic, oprete, cltor:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A nsuflat respectul cu duhul, cu tiina;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu facerea de bine a tras recunotina,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci ua-i fu deschis la ci cer ajutor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Pedeapsa cu moarte </text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I11"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Gemea poporu-n curtea palatului Dreptii. <text:line-break/>Era o zi de august i gura rutii<text:line-break/>Scrnea, se schidolea<text:line-break/>Voind s fete moartea. Sclipea-ntre dini mnia,<text:line-break/>Plngea, rnjea schidoal, dar nu ieea, pustia,<text:line-break/>Cci legea o oprea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O sal larg ntins i-n rou mbrcat<text:line-break/>i resfrngea coloarea prin raza sngerat,<text:line-break/>Coloarea de tartar,<text:line-break/>Pe searbedele fee, btrne i zbrcite,<text:line-break/>Plecate ctre piepturi, cu frunile-ncreite<text:line-break/>intind un act barbar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">P-un je ascuns sta unul de a-nsemnat pcatul<text:line-break/>Pe-a inimii icoan: buhav, c-un odhi, spurcatul,<text:line-break/>Rnjea rnjit uscat.<text:line-break/>Cu cap de cucuvaie, cu gheare mituite,<text:line-break/>Cu ochiul tras n sticle, n sticle ndoite,<text:line-break/>Chiora pe vinovat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dup-amuirea lung citir, mai citir,<text:line-break/>i mai ctar-n barb, gndir, mai optir, <text:line-break/>Se scoal-l nsemnat<text:line-break/>i-ncepe s vorbeasc: Boieri! Eu zic s moar,<text:line-break/>S moar vinovatul; cci moartea nfioar<text:line-break/>i trebui pilde-n stat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Gndii c-avem i suflet! s facem rzbunare:<text:line-break/>O cere omortul; o cere-n gura mare;<text:line-break/>O cere din mormnt.<text:line-break/>Pedeapsa o d legea ca s se corecteze<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Acel ce face crima,  ca s se ndrepteze. <text:line-break/>Eu nu vorbesc n vnt. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Eu nu sum de prerea acelui Becaria;<text:line-break/>Eu tiu ce se cuvine; nu-mi place flecria<text:line-break/>Lui domnul Monteschiu,<text:line-break/>Lamartine, Hugo, aizeci dintr-o societate:<text:line-break/>De-mi scap-omortorul, eu voi, dup dreptate,<text:line-break/>S-l osndesc n fiu.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II11"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Plit de o durere adnc, nempcat,<text:line-break/>Pe care-o d sperana cnd este nelat,<text:line-break/>Greit-ntr-al su plan,<text:line-break/>Se dobora pe fiare, flmnd, n baionete,<text:line-break/>Cu mdulri rnite, cu coatele-ntre spete,<text:line-break/>Un biet uitat igan!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Se cltina de boal, de crud disperare.<text:line-break/>Cnd hotrrea morii citir-n adunare,<text:line-break/>Suflarea-i se curm.<text:line-break/>Copii, soie, mum deloc i se ivir.<text:line-break/>Se-mpletici s caz; da-n spngi l sprijinir<text:line-break/>i iar se ntrem.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="III6"/>III</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Gndii voi la durere? gndii voi vre odat<text:line-break/>C i iganul sta e so, e i el tat,<text:line-break/>Va fi iubind ceva?<text:line-break/>Se afl i ntr-nsul dorina-naintrii; <text:line-break/>Cci firea nu a dat-o-n veci numai puterii; <text:line-break/>E-n om, natura sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Cum vrei voi ca iganul, ce-n hul se trate,<text:line-break/>Cnd vede libertatea a fiilor ce-o nate,<text:line-break/>A neamului su tot,<text:line-break/>A lui i a soiei; cnd tie c-o s fie<text:line-break/>D-aci-nainte liber, asupra-i nu-i sclavie,<text:line-break/>Stpnii nu mai pot;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Va fi stpn pe timpu-i, va rde cu natura,<text:line-break/>S-o bucura de munca-i i va simi cldura<text:line-break/>Ce Domnul a sdit<text:line-break/>n snul de familii, n vorba asta: tat!<text:line-break/>S fie surd la toate? natura lui stricat,<text:line-break/>Gndii c s-a rcit?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">E crud, crud legea ce-apas i strivete<text:line-break/>Gndirea zeitii, mister ce crmuiete<text:line-break/>Materie i spirit i face de suntem!<text:line-break/>Amor i Libertate sunt legea Provedinei;<text:line-break/>Sunt osia naturii; i cin le ia fiinei, <text:line-break/>Urgie! anatem!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Statistica de crime nu poate s v-arate <text:line-break/>Pe cnd bntuia rul pe om, societate,<text:line-break/>Opinc i boier,<text:line-break/>n zile de tortur, de epe, sugrumare?<text:line-break/>i cnd era mai bine: n vremile barbare,<text:line-break/>Sau azi cnd nu s-omoar, cnd n-avem nici hengher<text:line-break/>Gndii la instituii, la coli, nnobilare,<text:line-break/>La nlesnirea vieii, l-a rii destulare,<text:line-break/>-atuncea s-a strpit<text:line-break/>i crima i hoia. E viiul n prvili;<text:line-break/>D-aci se nate rul. Curmai aceste stvili<text:line-break/>Ce revolteaz omul i cel mai linitit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">-apoi iganul sta e lucru, e avere,<text:line-break/>Proprietatea voastr; el nu e n cdere<text:line-break/>S judece ca omul; nu poate a gndi;<text:line-break/>E vit brut: n-are nici drept, nici datorie;<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Incult ca dobitocul ce pate n pustie;<text:line-break/>i prvilile voastre nu pot a-l osndi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd face vita moarte o osndii s moar? <text:line-break/>El a privit ciocoiul cum bate i doboar,<text:line-break/>Lsnd pe zile morii iganii ce-i robete, <text:line-break/>i nu se face vorb. I-au dat de but bine,<text:line-break/>I-au dat o arm-n mn, cnd nu era n sine,<text:line-break/>I-au zis: omoar-i gdea i eu te ocrotesc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Tu mine vei fi liber cu copilaii-n pace;<text:line-break/>i dau de cheltuial, i dau orice-i va place,<text:line-break/>Te-oi face negustor,<text:line-break/>Te-oi face om pe lume; iar altfel,  vai de tine<text:line-break/>Acuma dar alege-i, ca ce-ai voi mai bine:<text:line-break/>S-omori sau s te-omor?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Voi osndii iganul ce, beat d-a lui dorin,<text:line-break/>A svrit o crim. Gndii, n contiin,<text:line-break/>Cine este mai miel:<text:line-break/>iganul ce omoar, omoar a da via<text:line-break/>i lui i seminiei,  sau voi carii de ghea,<text:line-break/>Clcnd i instituii, l omori pe el?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Voi osndii o crim fcut n beie,<text:line-break/>n disperaii crude, n patimi, n mnie,<text:line-break/>Cnd omul e nebun;<text:line-break/>-apoi, cu snge rece, n bine, fericire,<text:line-break/>Nempini deloc de patimi, strigai c-o glsuire<text:line-break/>C morii i rzbun?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Strigai: s moar omul! s moar-n agonie!<text:line-break/>V ducei la biserici?  Nu-i asta barbarie,<text:line-break/>S fii neierttori? <text:line-break/>Crmuitori ai rii i ai societii,<text:line-break/>Exemple-ai rzbunrii i ai moralitii?<text:line-break/>Chiar voi omortori?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>i unde se sfrete aceast rzbunare<text:line-break/>Dup principul vostru? gndii voi o-mpcare<text:line-break/>n fiii ce triesc?<text:line-break/>Voi singuri dai exemplu i-i invitai la ur,<text:line-break/>Deschidei ran nou prin nou lovitur,<text:line-break/>Dai snge de privesc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd zicei vorba: moarte! simii oari cum vibreaz<text:line-break/>n mum, fii, prieteni ce plng i sngereaz; <text:line-break/>Vedei-i stnd la pori<text:line-break/>Cu gurile n aer, cu ochii fr via,<text:line-break/>Cu braele spre ceruri; i trec sudori de ghea; -<text:line-break/>Vedei? ei sunt mai mori!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Voieti s dai exemplu -omori un om ce plnge!<text:line-break/>Voii s-mblnzii tigrii i i hrnii cu snge!<text:line-break/>Voii a-i corecta ;<text:line-break/>i ndemnai la crime!  O! cu brutalitatea<text:line-break/>Nu se civilizeaz deloc societatea;<text:line-break/>Cci crima nate crim i crima n-o-nceta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Attea milioane ce dai pe la poliii,<text:line-break/>La temnii i la paznici, la dorobani, miliii,<text:line-break/>L-attea nscociri,<text:line-break/>Nu pot ca s v scape de ast barbarie?<text:line-break/>Nu pot s ie omul nebun, sau n mnie,<text:line-break/>De relele-i porniri?</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="IV3"/>IV</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Mulimea s-adunase ca-n zi de srbtoare.<text:line-break/>Era o zi senin; era mreul soare<text:line-break/>Ajuns n culmea sa.<text:line-break/>Juca pe cmp copiii, mulimea fcea glume;<text:line-break/>Sileau i dregtorii iganul s sugrume; <text:line-break/>Dar gde nu era.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Puin, i dorobanii un alt igan gsir,<text:line-break/>L-aduser n bice, i-n bice l silir<text:line-break/>S-nvee-a sugruma.<text:line-break/>Cnd se-nl iganul s scape de robie,<text:line-break/>Rcneau i fii i rude, rcnea a lui soie<text:line-break/>i soul i chema.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Czu de trei ori robul din treangul infamiei;<text:line-break/>Vzu de trei ori moartea n munca agoniei:<text:line-break/>Zbiera fr puteri.<text:line-break/>Mugea-necat n snge, cu ochii scoi afar;<text:line-break/>Se zvrcolea ca arpe i se zburlea ca fiar<text:line-break/>Martirul n dureri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Poporul, plin de scrb, n groaza lui cea mare,<text:line-break/>Era uimit de spaim i fr rsuflare<text:line-break/>Fugea necontenit.<text:line-break/>Privelitea aceasta el nu o mai vzuse<text:line-break/>nc de cnd cu turcii. De mult nu se produse<text:line-break/>Revista de-ngrozit.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="V2"/>V</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Buzul optea nopii, spunea d-o grozvie,<text:line-break/>Plngea pe unde luna, i cinii pe cmpie<text:line-break/>Urlau nencetat.<text:line-break/>A doua zi, n aer, pe linite, rcoare,<text:line-break/>Sta, vnt ca porumba, cu ochii albi n soare,<text:line-break/>iganul spnzurat.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Prince strin </text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I12"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Mi-e urt tirania<text:line-break/>-orice cap ncoronat;<text:line-break/>ns astzi Romnia<text:line-break/>E-n nevoie de-mprat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De tirani de orice parte<text:line-break/>Suntem stranic ocolii<text:line-break/>i stau gata a ne-mparte,<text:line-break/>Cci ne vd neocrotii.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Vrem ca neamul s-i ia zborul,<text:line-break/>Nu mai vrem boier tronat,<text:line-break/>Cnd bat conii cu piciorul<text:line-break/>S-l vedem intrnd supat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ce-au fcut n Romnia<text:line-break/>Pmntenii patrioi,<text:line-break/>Ci au cumprat domnia<text:line-break/>De la pragul astei Pori?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Voi ce ai umblat pn lume!<text:line-break/>Mai gsit-ai vrun popor<text:line-break/>n mizerii fr nume,<text:line-break/>Ca romnul muncitor?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Fr legi, n umilin,<text:line-break/>Fr coli  ca nite boi <text:line-break/>Zcem ntr-o netiin<text:line-break/>i de lume i de noi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i ciocoiul i strinul<text:line-break/>Se ntrec a ne prda;<text:line-break/>Ne mresc pe zile chinul<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Spre a nu ne detepta.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II12"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">neleg s vei robia;<text:line-break/>Vei s fii un crud tiran;<text:line-break/>Dar ncai s-i vz mndria<text:line-break/>De un liber suveran.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Nu, smerit, c-urechi plotite,<text:line-break/>Btut d-ali stpni mai mari,<text:line-break/>S cai brute umilite,<text:line-break/>Imitnd p-acei tirani.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">D-eti stpn, m ocrotete;<text:line-break/>Bate p-l de m btu;<text:line-break/>Nu cnd el se ostenete,<text:line-break/>S m bai apoi i tu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Oriicum e rea robia;<text:line-break/>La rob ns a robi,<text:line-break/>i pierzi i de om mndria,<text:line-break/>Vei mai bine vit-a fi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cerem dar nti Unirea<text:line-break/>Cu Moldova ntr-un stat;<text:line-break/>i-i depunem crmuirea<text:line-break/>La un prince coronat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Liberal monarhie<text:line-break/>Cu drept num-executiv;<text:line-break/>i, fr-aristocraie;<text:line-break/>Guvern reprezentativ.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i strigm din orice parte:<text:line-break/>Nu vrem un mar plouat;<text:line-break/>Vrem din neamul Bonaparte;<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Snge de latin curat.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Pruncul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Aprilie 7, 1839</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rndunea frumoas.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pasre vroas.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zboar, ndrznete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La noi te oprete, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bine ai venit!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bun psric,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eti tu rnduric</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Care ne vestete:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ne pregtete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vre un timp dorit?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu, ca mielueaua,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vii cu vioreaua</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S ne-aduci iubirea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S ne-aduci zmbirea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dulcelui zefir.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Simbol de rodire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Simbol de unire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Amor, bucurie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Venirea-i s fie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La ci te admir!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sub alba cortin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unde-o mn lin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Leagnu-i umbrete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Guria-i zmbete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n somn linitit;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Gungunete, plnge,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Suge i se strnge</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd visul se schimb,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd visul te plimb,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe pom nflorit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Astfel trandafirul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-l crete zefirul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ncet bobocete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Frunza-l nvlete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn va flora;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Astfel, prin ghizdeie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un pui cu tuleie </text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Muma l nutrete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Noaptea-l nclzete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn va zbura.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Gura ta de miere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu cunoate fiere;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Buza-i ca rubinul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-a ajuns veninul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce noi bem turbai.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De suspini vreodat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Inima-i curat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Faa-i veselete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i buza-i zmbete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu ochi lcrimai.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu n-ai griji nici fric.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Gura-i mititic,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mna-i ca nluc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Parc tot apuc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Orice poi s vezi.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De dureri strine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De e ru sau bine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ri de vars snge,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sclavul daca plnge,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu nici tii, nici crezi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ct prefer eu plnsu-i</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-ntrerupe rsu-i</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dect veselia,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dect bucuria</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Care cercm noi!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ochii ti de lapte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu vd rele fapte;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i sugi degielul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca i mieluelul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iarb, spicuri noi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Simi tu oari veghierea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Simi tu mngierea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">L-a ta legnare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La a ta micare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd sugi buza ta?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Simi ci te-nconjoar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Simi ci te adoar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Simi tu cte fee</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stau s te rsfee</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd te-i detepta?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te detepi, -un tat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mume-tei te-arat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Braele-i ntinde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te salt, te prinde</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">P-un sn palpitnd.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mum-ta-n plcere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">cheam, te cere,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ardo rea-i te strnge</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n plcere-i plnge</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Privindu-te blnd.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea la cer privete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i i mulumete;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La tine se uit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cu totul uit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-a cercat dureri.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ct mulumire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dup-o chinuire!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu faci armonia,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu faci bucuria</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-ale lor averi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ct de mult mi place</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S vz s se joace</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mna-i rumeoar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca aureoar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe snu-i de crin!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ct e de frumoas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lacrim-amoroas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din ochii focoi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Verzi i schinteioi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe snu-i cel plin!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Rechemarea</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, iart-mi ndrzneala, sublima mea fiin!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De chem iubitu-i nume p-ast loc ce-ai prsit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E singura-ndulcire la cruda-mi suferin;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E balsam ce alin un piept prea obosit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n toat ntristarea-mi, de n-a avea icoana</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce lai tu dup tine-n ast suflet dureros,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce alt mngiere mi-ar uura povara</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-att de greu m-apas pe globul cel spinos?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Viaa mi-e ntreag n ast suvenire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce vine ca sperana s-opreasc-al meu suspin;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vederea umbrei tale mi-e dat motenire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nu rostesc alt nume cnd cerului m-nchin.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S vz cu nepsare aceste sfinte locuri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n care fui odat att de fericit!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S nu mai sim fioare, gndind l-acele jocuri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-n braele naturii cu ea am svrit!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">S viu pe aste maluri, s vd &apos;ast dumbrav,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S calc aste colnice fr a-mi repeta</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Plcerile d-atuncea, -a uitrii-otrav</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n inim-mi s-o fac a nu mai palpita?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aceste sacre-nscripii ce timpul adnceaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n coaja noduroas copacilor ce cresc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce ore de via, d-amor nfieaz,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S fiu strein de ele? S nu mai le citesc?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">S nu mai iu eu minte acele nopi de var,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe cnd, cu ea-mpreun, ast lac l ocoleam;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd, fr-a prinde veste, gndind c-i de cu sear,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vedeam c iese ziua i nu ne mai trezeam?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">S uit, cnd rtcit, cu frica-n cttur-i,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din braele-unei mume, n brae-mi s-arunca?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd snul ei p pieptu-mi i gura mea n gur-i</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Uita i datoria i chiar fiina sa?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">S nu adun n patu-mi, i plin de nerbdare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S iau aceste rnduri cu lacrmi a uda?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fiina-mi cea mai scump s caz n uitare?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S nu am mngierea mcar a o cnta?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu, spirt al vieii mele; num-ast suvenire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">mi poate-ndulci viaa din care tu scpai.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai fie dar cu mine i pn la unire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd, lepdnd povara-mi, voi fi-n al tu lca.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acolo, mpreun, scpai din ast-urgie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vom fi etern n pace; d-acolo ne-om ruga</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eternului printe s nu se mai mnie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S nu mai hotrasc n lume a ne-arunca.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Reflecie</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I13"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O, cte trebuine chiar omul i le face,<text:line-break/>Pizma pe sine nsui, se las-a se tr<text:line-break/>De patimi i de pofte; i vinde a sa pace<text:line-break/>-alearg el de sine sub jug a se vr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n veci fr simire, triesc ca dobitoace,<text:line-break/>Stpni i cat singuri, le zic c sunt pstori;<text:line-break/>Ca vita fr voie la glasul lor se-ntoarce,<text:line-break/>i gem, se-mpovreaz subt asprii protectori.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Gsesc de fericire subt jug ca s triasc;<text:line-break/>Genunchii lor se-nmoaie i capu l-e plecat,<text:line-break/>Si oricare povar sunt gata s primeasc;<text:line-break/>Se-ntrec, srut piciorul ce simt c i-a clcat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Se bucur i sunt veseli cnd capt vreo porunc<text:line-break/>i mndri de onoarea c sunt deosebii,<text:line-break/>Alerg, cu mare fal, i-n valuri se arunc;<text:line-break/>i uit-a lor fiin la cte-s poruncii.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">La slujbe ruinoase se-ntrec s le-mplineasc,<text:line-break/>i faptele cu fal ca merite i spun,<text:line-break/>i tremur ca stpnul s nu i necjeasc<text:line-break/>i liberndu-l, p-altu s-aleag mai de bun.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ce dulce e viaa acelui ce triete<text:line-break/>Stpn pe sine nsui i nu e-al nimului,<text:line-break/>Se bucur de toate i toate i priete;<text:line-break/>Natura, universul, ntregi sunt ale lui.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iar trist este starea acelui ce se vede<text:line-break/>Legat, c nu mai poate de sine-a dispoza;<text:line-break/>Main fr suflet, nici tie, nici prevede<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>De-i dreapt acea lege ce vin a-i impoza.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i daca vre o dat simirea-i se dezghea,<text:line-break/>i cere socoteal de cte a fcut;<text:line-break/>Sau va i el odat s schimbe ast via,<text:line-break/>Un glas din iad rsun, i strig: eti vndut!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Departe toate astea! n turme ei triasc,<text:line-break/>Cu pielea i cu viaa tiranii a-i hrni;<text:line-break/>Eu crez n Libertate, i ea m crmuiasc,<text:line-break/>Nu-mi trebuie protector n lan a m-ocroti.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Departe ast via de omul cel ce simte,<text:line-break/>Rmie pentru-acela nscut automat,<text:line-break/>Ce n-are-inteligin, nici poate da cuvinte<text:line-break/>Spre ce veni n lume, spre ce fu ntrupat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ce e acea onoare ce tremur a o pierde<text:line-break/>La micele cprie a unui ngmfat,<text:line-break/>Stpn ce i sugrum i nencetat i crede<text:line-break/>Nscui pentru serviciu la cte a visat?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ce este acel aur din care-i fac podoaba<text:line-break/>Spre fala unui mndru despot ce le-a luat<text:line-break/>i sufletul i mintea, i le-a depus otrava<text:line-break/>Ce-omoar-inteligina ce cerul le-a lsat?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Acel ce-n srcie nu poate s triasc,<text:line-break/>El sclav a fost s fie i sclav etern va fi!<text:line-break/>Serveasc dar, de-i place att s s-umileasc,<text:line-break/>Trasc-rse pe praguri, cci sclav el va muri.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II13"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">mi place viaa lin, sperana nainte;<text:line-break/>i-n locuri singurateci, n sine-mi mulumit,<text:line-break/>S nu port acea grij ce duc cei fr minte;<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>S dorm mi place pacinic, de cuget netrudit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i pur, tot vergin rmie a mea pan;<text:line-break/>S nu m fac-n via-mi de mine-a m roi.<text:line-break/>Corupia departe; tentaii de Satan<text:line-break/>S nu gseasc-n mine crare a veni.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Eu las societatea i grijile ce-omoar<text:line-break/>Pe toi nesocotiii ce-un bine-i nlucesc,<text:line-break/>Ce-aint vre o himer i-n ea se dezonoar,<text:line-break/>Ce-o duc n agonie i-ntr-nsa se sfresc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Detept cu aurora, s stau la o fntn<text:line-break/>i rou dimineei pe fruntea mea cznd,<text:line-break/>S-mi cnte rndurica i fluierul din stn,<text:line-break/>S vz cum nate ziua i turmele pscnd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S vz pe muncitorul cum elina despic,<text:line-break/>i-n brazda lui adnc s-l vz a semna<text:line-break/>Sperana unei toamne; sudoarea lui ce pic,<text:line-break/>S-l vz privind-o vesel, cnd brazda-i va uda.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">La pacinica murmur de-un rs ce erpuiete<text:line-break/>Prin vile verzite cu unda-i de clistar,<text:line-break/>S-adorm n murgul serii, cnd mierla flfiete<text:line-break/>Prin frunzele stufoase a unui vechi stejar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S-ascult privighetoarea pe cnd se dezmierdeaz<text:line-break/>P-o crac nverzit n noaptea fr nor,<text:line-break/>Acolo unde lauri i puc nu cuteaz<text:line-break/>S tulbure-al ei cntec, s-i dea vre un fior.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Venii, iubite muze; etern s fii cu mine;<text:line-break/>S nu gndii vreodat c eu v voi trda<text:line-break/>La cte v degrad acei ce nu-s n sine<text:line-break/>i vnd pudoarea voastr, tiranii a cnta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Venii, frumoase zne! Cu voi eu toat viaa<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>O Patrie -Amorul n pace voi cnta;<text:line-break/>Cu voi eu mpreun doresc s gust dulceaa<text:line-break/>Ce-o gust aceia numai ce tiu a v visa.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Rugciunea</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph">!         .<text:line-break/>     <text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="3"/>. </text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I14"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Trece noaptea. Un luceafr s-a ivit spre orient.<text:line-break/>Stelele i pierd lumina i luna va s apuie.<text:line-break/>Ca o femeie din somnu-i ce mijate un moment,<text:line-break/>Rsritul i revars, peste aburi ce se suie,<text:line-break/>Nite plete aurite.<text:line-break/>Nu mai poate rndurica<text:line-break/>Cntnd. Toat psrica<text:line-break/>Se spal-n rou oprite<text:line-break/>Sub frunza unde-a dormit.<text:line-break/>Tuciul solemnei rsun, ne cheam a ne-nchina.<text:line-break/>Toat fiina se roag, simirea sa se renate:<text:line-break/>Muma i privete pruncul, oaia mielul care pate;<text:line-break/>Pasu-ncepe-a fi simit,<text:line-break/>Fiara hran a-i cta.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II14"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar, stpne: n tot lucrul este-nscris mna ta.<text:line-break/>Sau n umbr, sau n soare, sau pe stnc, sau pe unde,<text:line-break/>Sau pe iarb, pe zpad,  pe tine-oi ntmpina.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>n senin, n vijelie, n insecta ce s-ascunde,<text:line-break/>n elefantul gigantic,<text:line-break/>ntr-un mieluel, hien,<text:line-break/>n goace, n balen,<text:line-break/>Chiar n ateul cel groaznic,<text:line-break/>Te explic i te onor.<text:line-break/>n m-i trage, stpne, ntr-un alt domen al tu,<text:line-break/>Pn-mi vei lsa gndirea, pn cnd mi-i lsa graiul,<text:line-break/>Pn cnd, subt ast form sunt, triesc i-mi gsesc raiul,<text:line-break/>Pe eternul l ador,  M cunosc c sunt al su.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="III7"/>III</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ast soare ce m-nclzete; aerul cel tritor;<text:line-break/>Apa care m adap; pmntul care m poart;<text:line-break/>Aste timpuri ce se schimb, fiecare roditor;<text:line-break/>Ast mare fr margini; ast noapte nstelat;<text:line-break/>Vederea ce mi le-arat,<text:line-break/>Auzul ce mi le spune,<text:line-break/>Voina-mi ce le supune, <text:line-break/>Oari, ce fiin spurcat<text:line-break/>Vrodat-a tgduit?<text:line-break/>Cum poate omul s fie, s triasc, fr-a ti<text:line-break/>C este, triete, simte?<text:line-break/>i daca este, triete,<text:line-break/>Cine l-a fcut? Ce-l ine? Unde? Cine l hrnete?<text:line-break/>Prin ce? Cum s-a zmislit? <text:line-break/>Scepticul s-ar amei!...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="IV4"/>IV</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Nu e nici un om, stpne, ce n-a avut dumnezeu.<text:line-break/>Nu pot s te neleag, pentru asta n-ai un nume.<text:line-break/>nelepii toi te cat: Brahma, Odin, Prometeu;<text:line-break/>Dar ne este scurt mintea, nu poate ptrunde-n lume.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Te-au aflat ns, te crede;<text:line-break/>Dar nu te pot nelege,<text:line-break/>Cci e-adnc a ta lege!<text:line-break/>Moisi, i el te vede:<text:line-break/>Dar nu spune ce fel eti.<text:line-break/>Zoroastru, Minos, Solon, Socrat i cu Ciceron,<text:line-break/>Se mir i ei cu plugarul ce simte tainile tale,<text:line-break/>Vede nencetat efectul n toate muncile sale,<text:line-break/>Se gndesc,  unde trieti?<text:line-break/>Dar s-opresc toi cu Newton.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="V3"/>V</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Stoicii cei tari i mndri, Pitagori cum -i de-n jur;<text:line-break/>Democrit care i rde, Eraclid care ne plnge;<text:line-break/>Din Platon ce ne mngie, pn-n crudul Epicur;<text:line-break/>Luther i Calvin, Saint-Simon; Mahomet ce cere snge,<text:line-break/>Cnd p-ascuns i cnd de fa,<text:line-break/>Cnd numind, cnd fr nume,<text:line-break/>Cum c ast mare lume<text:line-break/>Are un stpn ne-nva,<text:line-break/>Care trebuie-a-l slvi.<text:line-break/>i baza voinei tale fiecare a simit:<text:line-break/>Omul, omului s fac aceea care dorete<text:line-break/>S-i fac i lui iar omul.<text:line-break/>Nimini nu tgduiete<text:line-break/>Cum c, stpne, ai voit<text:line-break/>Omul a fi fericit.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="VI1"/>VI</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unul, un miel fr pat depune la templul tu;<text:line-break/>Altul, colo i njunghie ecatomba</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3"><text:note text:id="ftn25" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>25</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
       <text:p text:style-name="P22"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ecatomba  jertf.</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">cea bogat:<text:line-break/>Altul, vezi c-i sacrific soia, sngele su;<text:line-break/>-un caic taie, mnnc prada lui cea necurat<text:line-break/></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n faa statuiei tale.<text:line-break/>tiu c rtcesc, printe;<text:line-break/>Dar, vai! ce alte cuvinte<text:line-break/>l fac crud cu ale sale,<text:line-break/>Daca nu iubirea ta?<text:line-break/>Trudele care martirii de cnd lumea au rbdat;<text:line-break/>Acele-otodafe</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3"><text:note text:id="ftn26" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>26</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
       <text:p text:style-name="P12">autodafe  ardere pe rug.</text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">groaznici, care i-aprindea cretinii,<text:line-break/>Rzboaiele sngeroase ntre cretini cu pgnii,<text:line-break/>N-au fost n onoarea ta? Stric ei, daca au stricat?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="VII1"/>VII</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De cnd tu liberai viaa; de cnd ai fcut pe om,<text:line-break/>De cnd, ca s te cunoasc, i-ai spus marea trebuin,<text:line-break/>De cnd, ca s te gseasc, el sfram-orice atom;<text:line-break/>De cnd mintea-i se trudete ca s afle-a ta voin<text:line-break/>ntr-o pasre ce zboar,<text:line-break/>ntr-un fenomen departe,<text:line-break/>ntr-un fum ce se mparte,<text:line-break/>Chiar n victima ce-omoar,<text:line-break/>D-atunci, oare-ai msurat,<text:line-break/>Stpne, din aste neamuri, care mai mult te-a mrit!<text:line-break/>Dar i-au dat schidoale forme! dar te micora-n ermonii;<text:line-break/>Cultul lor era onoare, zbieretele lor, armonii!<text:line-break/>Credea c te-a-ndatorat<text:line-break/>C-o cruzime de-ngrozit.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="VIII1"/>VIII</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Tu vei primi dopotriv i p-l ru ca i p-l bun;<text:line-break/>Tu ai lsat n om nsui pe om cin s pedepseasc,<text:line-break/>Cine s-i fac mustrare i cine s-l rsplteasc.<text:line-break/>Tu primeti pe toi n snu-i, cci ie toi se supun!<text:line-break/>Ast stpn ce-ai pus n mine<text:line-break/>Fr clip privegheaz:<text:line-break/>E-aci blnd, aci turbeaz;<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cnd m deprtez de tine,<text:line-break/>M ntoarce napoi.<text:line-break/>i cnd sunt fr pcate, cnd de rele sunt pltit,<text:line-break/>El atuncea m liber i snul tu m primete.<text:line-break/>De tot ce-am fcut aicea, unde voia-i m-osndete,<text:line-break/>La ora mea de apoi,<text:line-break/>Sunt curat cum am venit.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="IX"/>IX</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Eu nu te-am crezut, printe, cu slbiciuni omeneti.<text:line-break/>Nici pe lemne, nici de piatr, nici n mantel albastr,<text:line-break/>Nici pe acvil clare, nici pe nori c te-odineti, <text:line-break/>Slabe simboluri ce nate mintea mrginit-a noastr<text:line-break/>Le-am despreuit pe toate, N-am hotrt lcuina-i,<text:line-break/>N-am crezut c tiu voina-i,<text:line-break/>N-am crezut c daruri poate<text:line-break/>Pe tine a-ndupleca. i ce daruri avem,<text:line-break/>Doamne, care s putem s-i dm?<text:line-break/>Tmie? snge sau aur?<text:line-break/>Orice-avem e de la tine.<text:line-break/>Iart, Doamne, pe aceia care se privesc pe sine,<text:line-break/>i voiesc a-i aplica Slbiciuni ce noi purtm!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="X"/>X</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iart pe toi dopotriv: i pe cel ce te va om,<text:line-break/>i pe cel ce te va arpe, i pe cel ce te va soare;<text:line-break/>Pe cel ce te mrginete ntr-un fel sau un atom;<text:line-break/>Pe cel care, ca s-i plac, se pornete s omoare<text:line-break/>Pe cel ce cu bani n mn<text:line-break/>Vine s te mituiasc!<text:line-break/>Pe cel ce va s zideasc<text:line-break/>Un templu unde te mn,<text:line-break/>-a-i d pravili ei cutez!<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Pe cei ce-au a tale daruri i-i mai cer -alt ajutor,<text:line-break/>Iart pe cel ce se roag s-i ajui cnd face crime:<text:line-break/>Pe ateul ce te-mbal, blestem a ta asprime!<text:line-break/>O! ast blestem este: crez<text:line-break/>n eternul Creator!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="XI"/>XI</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd durerea ne gtete fericiri nou-a gusta;<text:line-break/>Cnd lenea nu ne d hrana, sau cnd sub tirani ne pas;<text:line-break/>Cnd cugetul ne trudete; cnd pizma ne-a revolta:<text:line-break/>Vrnd ca s scpm de toate cte aci ne apas,<text:line-break/>Atunci alergm la tine:<text:line-break/>Unii rog, alii blesteam <text:line-break/>Te gonesc, alii te cheam;<text:line-break/>Cci nu tiu cum e mai bine,<text:line-break/>i le trebuie-ajutor!<text:line-break/>Cnd cugetul se mnie, unde putem alerga?<text:line-break/>Atunci, zpcii, stpne, te cutm i dm nval;<text:line-break/>Te chemm ca s dai pacea-n ast demon ce se rscoal:<text:line-break/>Cnd n-am crede-un Creator,<text:line-break/>Atunci nu l-am blestema.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="XII"/>XII</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iart, Doamne, dopotriv pe tot neamul omenesc!<text:line-break/>Pe tiranii ce turbeaz cnd ncep ca s bea snge,<text:line-break/>Care, orbi-n a lor turbare, sug p-acei ce se smeresc<text:line-break/>i zburlez ca nite fiare cnd privesc pe cel ce plnge.<text:line-break/>Iart-un preot ce te vinde;<text:line-break/>P-i de-i uit datoria;<text:line-break/>P-i de-ncurajez sclavia;<text:line-break/>Pe cel care se ntinde<text:line-break/>S ia hrana-lui srac.<text:line-break/>Pe cel ce nedreptete ca i p-l nedreptit,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Tart p-l de-ncurajaz crimile cele spurcate;<text:line-break/>Pe cel ce se veselete de un ru oe altul pate;<text:line-break/>Pe cel care, dupe plac,<text:line-break/>D dreptatea la-l greit.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="XIII"/>XIII</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iart pe cel ce n umbr a-nfipt fier omortor;<text:line-break/>Pe cel care, orb de glorii, chiar pe fraii si strivete;<text:line-break/>Pe cel ce i smulge nsui viaa care i-e dator;<text:line-break/>Pe cel ce cumpr, vinde omul care i robete;<text:line-break/>Pe cel care se supune;<text:line-break/>Pe cel care linguate;<text:line-break/>Pe cel care se trate,<text:line-break/>Ca pe cel cu fapte bune,<text:line-break/>Ca pe cel folositor.<text:line-break/>Pe spionul ce-i d fraii la gzi ce l-a cumprat;<text:line-break/>Pe cei ce-i blestem copiii; pe cei ce-i mbal prinii<text:line-break/>Pe cei care, bei de pofte, i rod viaa lor cu dinii;<text:line-break/>Laii ce-au calomniat, i mravul trdtor.<text:bookmark text:name="Note11"/><text:bookmark text:name="cite_note-29"/></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Rsunet la Hora Unirei de d. V. Alecsandri</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vin s strngem mn-n mn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Toi c-o inim romn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i s-ntindem dan premare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">L-a unirii-ne srbare!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Piar cei ce ne-nvenin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Trntori, viespe din stupin!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ntre noi s nu mai fie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dect frai i veselie.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi bdi moldovene,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prinde-te cu mine, nene,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca s fim ntr-o unire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i la via i-n pieire!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n unire-avem putere;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Altfel nu putem, mi vere!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i dumanul se sfiete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vznd pe romn c crete!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Suntem gemeni, mi frtate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din prini ntr-o dreptate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca doi ochi la semnare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca doi brazi la nlare.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T5"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">te chemi, aa m cheam;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce te temi, d-aia mi-e team;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">mi eti frate i-i sunt frate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n noi doi un suflet bate.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ai la Milcov cu grbire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-l secm dintr-o sorbire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i s tragem dan premare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Peste vechile hotare.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i s-aduc sntul soare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-acea zi de srbtoare:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Danu-n hor s-ocoleasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Toat ara romneasc!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ascultai! rsun valea!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De pe Prut i de pe Jiu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vin romnii, negresc calea;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vin n cete mii de mii.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Munii i-ar surpa, d-ar vrea-o,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-s ca holdele de gru!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">D-ar fi Dunrea, ar bea-o,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar o pozn de pru!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu clipii n zi de Pate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Liliecilor spurcai!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Soboli, Cristuleul nate!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n pmnt v adncai!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ci suntei cu fruni senine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Inimi calzi, de neam romni,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Credei c-n unire-i bine;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-avem team de pgni.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">S ne facem ar mare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i unit ntr-un: stat!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cine-i mare e i tare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cine-i tare-i respectat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu tot doine i jelire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu tot plns i suspinat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu tot fric de pieire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La-orice vnt a adiat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Uite-n sus i mergi d-a dreptul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spre vrjmaul ce-o cta</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-i nesocoteasc dreptul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i s calce ara ta.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dreptu-ne de aprare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Europa l-a prescris.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-avem nici o-mpiedicare:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E-n tractatul din Paris.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Europa azi ne cere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce dorim s artm.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Frai, sculai-v-n picere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cu toii s strigm:</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cerem toi i vrem Unire!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-ateptm nici un minut;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mine-om sta la chibzuire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce mai este de fcut.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cel ce cere dezunirea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu-i bun nici stpnitor;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ala vrea n veci robirea;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E un mrav trdtor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">S-a dus! eu orice-oi face </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-a dus! i orice-oi face</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sunt toate n zadar;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar cugetul mi-e-n pace,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci tu-mi dai ast pahar.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu mergi la bogie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i uii c te-am amat;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd eu, pe avuie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu te-a fi schimbat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai bine lng tine</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe praguri a robi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dect, cu alta-n mine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe tron a-mpri.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd viaa-mi se precurm,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd gata sunt s mor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Credina mea din urm</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eti tu -al meu amor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Salahorul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Paris, 1854</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Bicele mi crap pielea,<text:line-break/>Deger gol pe scu de ghea...<text:line-break/>E departe nc schelea,<text:line-break/>i-s flmnd i fr via!...<text:line-break/>ntre blane ca fuioru,<text:line-break/>Intre muzici i fclii,<text:line-break/>Voi v batei cu picioru,<text:line-break/>Dnuii pe rane vii.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Tragei dan pe rana noastr;<text:line-break/>Noi ipm, voi hihotai!<text:line-break/>Nu suntem de legea voastr!<text:line-break/>De bani nu v sturai!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O, soia-mi e strpit<text:line-break/>Subt o crosnie de lemne<text:line-break/>n hordii, i vineit<text:line-break/>Carnea-mi d-a bicelor semne!<text:line-break/>Copilaii-mi plng acas,<text:line-break/>Bouleanii mi-au murit,<text:line-break/>N-a rmas romn n plas,<text:line-break/>Munca pe cmp ne-a pierit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pn cinci din ast pine<text:line-break/>Ce sudoarea mea produce,<text:line-break/>Nici un pic mcar pe mine<text:line-break/>Romnaul s n-apuce!<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Aste holde aurite<text:line-break/>mbuiba-vor tot strin?<text:line-break/>-aste dealuri nverzite<text:line-break/>Pentru dnsul vars vin?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Lna oielor mele<text:line-break/>Pentru el se toarce-n drst?<text:line-break/>-oi rbda eu mult n piele,<text:line-break/>Sila fie-mi fr vrst?<text:line-break/>Sufletul mai am n oase <text:line-break/>Pe dnsul, Sfinte, m jur<text:line-break/>C-n palatele frumoase<text:line-break/>Chiar la glasu-i voi fi dur!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De cinci ani salahorie!<text:line-break/>Trag cu pieptu-n jug ca vit,<text:line-break/>Vatra mi-a rmas pustie,<text:line-break/>-nc-mi cer ciocoii mit!<text:line-break/>O, boieri cu noi d-un snge,<text:line-break/>Voivozilor pmnteni,<text:line-break/>Voi rdei i ara plnge<text:line-break/>De la munte la blteni!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Fiica voastr, cea nevast,<text:line-break/>Se golete la barbar<text:line-break/>i cu dnsul coast-n coast,<text:line-break/>Joac, beat de tovar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Chiar brbatu pe soie<text:line-break/>i-o trimite la strin<text:line-break/>S-i aduc din hordie<text:line-break/>Un nian</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3"><text:note text:id="ftn27" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>27</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
       <text:p text:style-name="P12">nian  decoraie.</text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">, un post, un cin.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Juni posadnici</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3"><text:note text:id="ftn28" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>28</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
       <text:p text:style-name="P22"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T4">posadnic  desfrnat.</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">,  alivanta!<text:line-break/>Cu zulufii hlciuc,<text:line-break/>i vnd trupu i amanta<text:line-break/>La manaf baibugiuc,<text:line-break/>i prini cu hrci cnite<text:line-break/>i de boale schilodii,<text:line-break/></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mumele sulemenite<text:line-break/>i cu dinii nnegrii,<text:line-break/>in veriga,- i rd la u;<text:line-break/>i bloi, ascult suflnd<text:line-break/>Neamu-nalt, zbrcit-mtu,<text:line-break/>P-un sn tinerel gemnd.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">N-avei ar, n-avei lege,<text:line-break/>N-avei inim-omeneasc!<text:line-break/>ntre voi, n-avem ce-alege, <text:line-break/>Piar brasla boiereasc!,<text:line-break/>i de e fatalitate<text:line-break/>S avem stpnitor,<text:line-break/>Vie din strintate<text:line-break/>S v bage n popor!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Schitul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acum e miezul nopii, i tuciul, deteptat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lovete i rsun din nalta-i locuin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca glasul ce pornete o oaste-n biruin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n muni, din stnc-n stnc, eco l-a repetat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i preajmile-n departe parc-ar spimnta;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Parc-a sosit i ora d-a doua nviere;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Parc se-nal tronul la care ni se cere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cugetul i fapta rsplat a-i cta.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca suflete ntocmai cnd strig Mihail;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca umbre cror moartea locaul le arat;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca oaste ce se cearc de este-n veci tot gata;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca emigrai ce afl c-i chem de prin exil, </text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe sute de potece btute nencetat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De greii sandali negri ce-n nopi fr de stele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n zile fr soare, pe lapovie grele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe vijelii, pe vifori, deloc n-au pregetat, </text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se mic prin ntuneric prinii singurii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai negri dect noaptea, mai vechi dect stejarii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu pletele ca blana pe care-mbrac arii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De privigheri i posturi nencetat slbii.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cnd lucete-un fulger pe civa grbovi, orbi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Al cror snge-nghea n vinele slbite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se vd jucnd pe raze acele barbe-albite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca fulgii unei ier ne pe penele de corbi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Orbii de btrnee, slbii d-al rugii jug,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se leagn n toiege, cci mai le-au trecut seara; </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sunt grei ca i pmntul, i galbeni ca i ceara</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce lumineaz groapa de mori fr cociug.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se mic ncet spre centrul n care e-nlat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un templu-a crui cruce de nori se ruginete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Precum se roade piatra-i de plnsul ce pistete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din fruntea ncreit a celui genucheat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nimic nu i conduce spre templul nnegrit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nimic, dect o lamp ce parc licureaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n fundul monstirii, precum ne lumineaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O raz de speran cnd sufletu-i mhnit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Frai, vom muri! optete pmntu-n preajma lor</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vom muri! rspund pacinic, n loc de salutare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vom muri! se ngn i mai n deprtare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i moartea se ureaz ca un ceresc favor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sprnceana lor ascunde o pleop ce-a secat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Privind icoana morii n hrca cea uscat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca slcii plngtoare o piatr ngheat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sub care focul, viaa, sperana a-ncetat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar ns-a lor speran e vie ca Cristos;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E verde ca tulpina a crii crci prlite</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se-ncarc-n miezul iernii de scuurile-albite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd mana-eternitii via-i d din jos.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aa se hrnesc i ei de mana cea din cer;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aa credina vine p-ascuns de i nutrete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe cnd asprimea rugii i postul i slbete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n lunga lor veghere pe un toiag de fier.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i tnrul acela ce-ntreag viaa sa</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ast loca petrece n trud, pocin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce a crescut n rug, n posturi, umilin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i n-a avut prilejul de rele-a se-mbta, </text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca i btrnul care n crime-i obosit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-adun s-i ia rsplata; cci nu e osebire:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mntuitorul lumii, n marea sa iubire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Primete p-l din urm ca p-l nti-venit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-adun ca s se roage de Tatl Creator</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A uura rna la ginte rposate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La mii de generaii de lume nevisate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu care-ngroa globul srmanul muritor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O! generaii care strate, strate se ntind</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe stratele-nvechite, ca undele de valuri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce se adun din vrfuri, se prvlesc din maluri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se-ntind pe oceanuri, vechi valuri cotropind.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O! pentru generaii ce trec nencetat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe ast inut de doliu, cum trec i nite turme</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De oi fr putere etern p-aceleai urme</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce turmele trecute, trecnd, au nsemnat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acum sunt toi n strane ca n mormntul lor.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ochiu-n pmnt aint trufia pieritoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i mintea-le se-nal la viaa viitoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unde i-au pus comoara prin rug i amor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Moisi, Isaia, Daniil se detept;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ai lui Iehova preoi ce-au profetat n lume</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-a fost i ce-a s fie,  al mntuirii nume, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Le strig ca din morminte la ci vrun bine-atept.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Asculi tu oare, Doamne, de unde locuieti,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum s-urc cu tmia un: Doamne miluiete?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">P-ati grbovi care-i strig un: acum slobozete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ii s vaz lumea cum ai s-o mntuieti?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Trei mii de ani mai bine, stpne, au trecut,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De cnd aceste imnuri, n trist armonie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nal omenirea, s-aline-a ta mnie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-o mntuieti de Rul ce voia-i a fcut!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ai hotrt tu, Doamne, sfrit la ura ta?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vrun Hanaan ne-ateapt sau a Sodomii soart?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai e vre o cercare l-a fericirii poart?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai sunt cutremuri, groaze pn te-i arta?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O! mintea mea se pierde cu ct o duc mai sus!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se pierde-n mii de gnduri, ca urma-n labirinte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca ruga i ca plnsul vrsate pe morminte;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se pierde ca tmia pe vnturi de apus!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se pierde, s-adnceaz ntr-un deert noptos;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se pierde s strbat voina-i, vecinicia,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca acvila ce-alearg s msure tria,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-orbit n lumin, se prvlete-n-jos.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Sonet la *** </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu nu poci, surioar, s fac portretul tu:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zburdalnic-aezat, tcut vorbitoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cochet virtuoas, modest muctoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Orice trsuri i-oi face, eu vz c iese ru.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">P-un serios profesor l faci a fi ingu;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">P-un libertin de frunte, ce patimi nu-l mai doare.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un simplu al tu zmbet e-n stare s-l omoare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Orice-nelept te vede, s-a dus curajul su.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dac schimbri la fa a ti c se cuvine</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S crez n timpul nostru,  privindu-te pe tine.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A mai croi un basmu l-al Vinerii fecior.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atunci, cu-ncredinare, tiu c-a brodi-o bine:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E tnr,  ncnt,  schimbarea e n sine, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce alt s fie, a zice, dect, dect Amor!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Stane</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I15"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">De cte ori n brae te vz cu al tu fiu, <text:line-break/>D-a ti c parabola-mi o iart cuviina,<text:line-break/>Sau daca adevrul nu vatm credina, <text:line-break/>Puterea-i m silete un eretic s fiu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cnd stai cu toat mila spre pruncu-i a cta,<text:line-break/>mi pare pe Madona c-o vz d-al doilea-n lume;<text:line-break/>i-i spui, n contiin, c nu-i poci da alt nume,<text:line-break/>Dect c eti aceea ce Gabriel cnta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Iar daca a mea dogm va fi o rtcire,<text:line-break/>Artistul e de vin, c-a lui dumnezeire<text:line-break/>Ca tine de frumoas a vrut imagina.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Eu sim de datorie i de cretintate,<text:line-break/>Eu sim c dau exemplu de-adnc pietate,<text:line-break/>A m-nchina la tine i a te adora.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II15"/><text:soft-page-break/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Onoarea cea adnc ce-nspir-a ta persoan<text:line-break/>Mai are nc-o tain ce-nspir i amor:<text:line-break/>De cte ori m-apropiu, sau vz a ta icoan,<text:line-break/>Din unghii pn-n cretet m trece un fior.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Amorul m ndeamn durerea mea a-i spune,<text:line-break/>Respectul m oprete i-mi zice ca s tac;<text:line-break/>Puternici dopotriv, nici unul se supune,<text:line-break/>Se lupt etern n mine i nu tiu ce s fac.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Putina st la tine, o, angele de pace!<text:line-break/>S intri ntre dnii, s-ajui pe cel ce-i place,<text:line-break/>S curmi aceast lupt ce-atta m-a slbit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">i spui c unul ns e crunt cu mintea-n sine;<text:line-break/>Iar altul este tnr, frumos, leit ca tine;<text:line-break/>Acuma dar alege-i, cci el a biruit.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="III8"/>III</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">ntocmai ca o rou ce-n nasturi dimineaa<text:line-break/>Se las pe un mugur ce-acum a nverzit,<text:line-break/>Vz lacrma ce cade din pleopa-i ce-mi d viaa,<text:line-break/>-o snt lege-Amorul n ea a zugrvit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cnd ochii ti de flcri, frumoi ca primvara,<text:line-break/>Azvrl a lor schinteie d-un verde de smarant,<text:line-break/>Pe buza ta cea vie i vesel ca vara,<text:line-break/>Etern n floare-i este un mndru amarant.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">De ce o plsmuire nu va s m supuie!<text:line-break/>De ce a mea speran nu poate s se suie<text:line-break/>La dulcea amgire c poate m-ei iubi!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cnd te recheam mintea-mi, eu sim o strmutare<text:line-break/>Ce -mi d dureri cumplite; dar crez c-o vindecare,<text:line-break/>n loc s-mi fac bine, mormntu-mi ar grbi.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="IV5"/>IV</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Ce este fericirea? Care s fie raiul?<text:line-break/>Care s fie pomul oprit la muritori,<text:line-break/>Daca nu este snu-i care oprete graiul<text:line-break/>i face ca rebelii s-i fie-adoratori?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Ce floare e aceea ce-Amorul protecteaz,<text:line-break/>De nu sunt trandafirii ce-n fa-i nfloresc<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i care, pe-ndrzneul ce a-i privi cuteaz,<text:line-break/>mpung att de ager deloc ce-i ntlnesc?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Ce oar e sgeata ce fabula ne spune,<text:line-break/>De nu e cea schinteie ce ochiul tu depune<text:line-break/>Cu ast firbineal n sngele din mine?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Ce este fermecarea? Ce poate fi rpirea?<text:line-break/>Oari ncntarea ce e? De nu e chiar uimirea<text:line-break/>Ce sim c-ncet m fur cnd m-aflu lng tine?</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Susana</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I16"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">nalt i mrea, Susana-nainteaz<text:line-break/>Urmat d-a ei sclave, cnd luna arginteaz<text:line-break/>Pe chedri, sicomori.<text:line-break/>Cnta rugind pre Domnul, cu sclavele-mpreun,<text:line-break/>Pe Ioachim s-l ie, s-i fie calea bun,<text:line-break/>Cci vine cu comori.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Sub albia ei mantel, pe un tunic de ln<text:line-break/>Albastru ca seninul, s-arat-o alb mn<text:line-break/>ntr-un bogat colan<text:line-break/>Din care se atrn i dou pozunare<text:line-break/>Lucrate numa-n aur. Mrgritar prea mare<text:line-break/>Formeaz-un greu ghiordan</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Plin d-amulei simbolici ce-opresc, nfrunt deochiul;<text:line-break/>i lungi cercei de pietre, ce nu-i aint ochiul,<text:line-break/>Dau flcri prin voal.<text:line-break/>De sub cmaa lung i puintel sumeas,<text:line-break/>Ar fi pndit profanul secunda cnd s ias,<text:line-break/>Strns mult ntr-un sandal,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Greu, plin de catareme n chip de semilun,<text:line-break/>Pind cu gravitate, piciorul care sun<text:line-break/>De zale-ncongiurat;<text:line-break/>De zale tot de aur, de ctrmi lucrate<text:line-break/>n onix i rubinuri, de funde mari, lsate<text:line-break/>P-o pulp de-ncntat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">n preajma ei, n cale, zbor spirite de pace;<text:line-break/>Mrgritarul curge cu vocea ce ntoarce<text:line-break/>Cnticul cel frumos.<text:line-break/>Zefirii joc pe snu-i o vi rtcit,<text:line-break/>i luna i rsfrnge o raz aurit<text:line-break/>Pe stema de mados.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:soft-page-break/>Ochiu-i cel viu i negru n ceruri s-ainteaz;<text:line-break/>i faa-i plin, alb, s-aprinde, o-nviaz<text:line-break/>Un sacru spirit de foc.<text:line-break/>Ea cere n canticu-i pe so s i-l aduc,<text:line-break/>S i-l aduc-n grab, sau c pe ea s-o duc<text:line-break/>Cu dnsul la un loc.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II16"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Pe o tera-nalt, treptat i ntins,<text:line-break/>Ce rcorete noaptea n ast clim-aprins,<text:line-break/>Mii vase de un stat<text:line-break/>Lucrate d-alabastru, de marmur, aram,<text:line-break/>Prin plante felurite, bazinuri fr seam<text:line-break/>A muntelui lucrat,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Scotea n reliefuri a lui Baal izbnde,<text:line-break/>Minunele lui Iosif, a neamului osnde,<text:line-break/>Sau grele vntori,<text:line-break/>Sau ntmplri prin care frumoasa i smerita<text:line-break/>Babiloneanca fiie, n templul zis Milita,<text:line-break/>Se d la cltori.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Sub ase stlpi granitici -un rou vl de ln<text:line-break/>Pe el cu animale cusute tot de mn,<text:line-break/>Mre era drapat<text:line-break/>Un pat de abanosuri, ascuns n bumbac moale,<text:line-break/>-un je de dini de filde, cu draperii pe poale,<text:line-break/>-o baie de agat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">S-exal chiparosul; curmalul i finicul<text:line-break/>Se-ntinde n alee; colo undeaz spicul,<text:line-break/>Susamii ce suspin;<text:line-break/>i mai departe, pacinic, Efratul, plin de vase,<text:line-break/>Se vars printre grne nalte i frumoase<text:line-break/>Din valea fr spin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">D-a dreapta se nal un turn trufa, gigantic,<text:line-break/>Zidit de toat-Asia dup un plan fantastic,<text:line-break/>De Iehova damnat;<text:line-break/>-alturea cu dnsul a lui Nembrod cldire,<text:line-break/>Semea ca i turnul, i d a ei privire<text:line-break/>n raiul suspendat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">D-a stnga stau palaturi de haldeeni zidite,<text:line-break/>ntinse i mree, cu naft tencuite<text:line-break/>De Nabopalazar. nc se in n contra acelui Isaia;<text:line-break/>Mai stau ca s priveasc p-l de-a supus Asia<text:line-break/>C-i pune un hotar.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="III9"/><text:soft-page-break/>III</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"><text:span text:style-name="T8">Ardic vlul sta! mi place luna plin!<text:line-break/>Zefirii dulci s-adie suflarea lor cea lin;<text:line-break/>S vz un cer senin!<text:line-break/>Cntarea mea s mearg d-a dreptul ctre Domnul<text:line-break/>Eu voi s-l rog fierbinte ca s-mi trimi somnul,<text:line-break/>Eu voi s m nchin;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cci noaptea cea trecut,  o! iesme-ngrozitoare,<text:line-break/>i spirite mlinei vise-omortoare<text:line-break/>n preajm-mi au zburat.<text:line-break/>O! Ioachim se vede c ptimete-n cale!<text:line-break/>Era mhnit i searbd... Venise-ntr-ale sale<text:line-break/>i nu m-a srutat!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Doi demoni din tartaruri prea c-mi stau la u,<text:line-break/>Poporul strngea pietre, taica-i punea cenu;<text:line-break/>i eu m tot smulgeam...<text:line-break/>Pe mine vrea s-omoare: zicea c-s vinovat;<text:line-break/>Dar nger de foc iute din ceruri se arat,<text:line-break/>Cnd eu m sfiam;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Strbate ca un fulger; se-ntoarce prin mulime;<text:line-break/>i intr, trece, piere.  Iubite Ioachime!<text:line-break/>O! noi plngeam mereu!...<text:line-break/>Cnd iat-un june tnr se-nal dintre lume,<text:line-break/>Vorbete... Toi ntreab:  cum este al su nume<text:line-break/>Trimis este de zeu?...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cci spiritul se puse pe fruntea sa cea lat;<text:line-break/>Vorbea -oprea poporul! -o lacrm curat<text:line-break/>Din ochi i-a schinteiat...<text:line-break/>Era blai i dulce,  micrile-i, ctare:<text:line-break/>Prea c-ar fi fost David! ca el vorbea de tare!<text:line-break/>Profetul,  m-a scpat!...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="IV6"/>IV</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Aa vorbea Susana, aproape d-a sa baie,<text:line-break/>Plngea -era frumoas!... n ochi avea vpaie,<text:line-break/>n ap se uita,<text:line-break/>Cnd sclavele din preajm-i voalu-i ardicase<text:line-break/>i una dintre ele de ea s-apropiase<text:line-break/>i-ncet o dezbrca.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">i scoaser podoaba, tunica-i deschiar,<text:line-break/>De bru se descinsese; sovonu-i desprinser,<text:line-break/>Pru-i czu pe sin:<text:line-break/>Un pr supire, negru, i ajungea la glezne,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Se desprea n dou i se zrea prea lesne<text:line-break/>Un piept rotund i plin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Alene gnditoare, culcat pe covoru-i,<text:line-break/>Lsa n mna sclavei a descula picioru-i<text:line-break/>D-onix, mrgritar.<text:line-break/>O pulp de zpad, ieit i rotund,<text:line-break/>-un mic clci rozatic sub o gropi-afund<text:line-break/>Da tortur-n Sefar;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cci el -al su complice, pitii aci-n grdin,<text:line-break/>Turbnd de poft mult, se roag, se nchin,<text:line-break/>Chem ceru-ntr-agiutor...<text:line-break/>Era schidoli btrnii: prunelele turbate<text:line-break/>Zvrlea schintei de poft, i palpite-nfocate<text:line-break/>Fierbea n pieptul lor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Prelung, cu barba rar, cu fruntea ncreit,<text:line-break/>Cu ochii roi n hrca pleuv i albit,<text:line-break/>Sefar, n sicomori,<text:line-break/>i ntindea grumazii, iind n urm tare<text:line-break/>Pe grbovul complice, zgit, n nerbdare,<text:line-break/>n spasmuri i sudori.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="V4"/>V</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cnd fuse dezbrcat, naint spre baie,<text:line-break/>Fricoas, tremurnd;  btrnii stau s saie,<text:line-break/>mpuni de pofta lor.<text:line-break/>Acum v ducei toate, lsai-m n pace;<text:line-break/>Voi singur, la ceruri, cntrile-mi a face,<text:line-break/>Ca imn la Creator...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">S nu vorbeti, Susano, cci altfel eti pierdut!<text:line-break/>n noi poporul crede, i tu vei sta ca mut<text:line-break/>Cnd noi te-om osndi!<text:line-break/>Spunei-mi care vin?... fugii s ies din baie!...<text:line-break/>Srmana nu-nelege ce va a lor vpaie,<text:line-break/>Nu poate a-i opri...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Mirobolam s-aprindei subt patu-mi de culcare,<text:line-break/>S-aprindei smirn mult n casa cea mai mare,<text:line-break/>-atunci cnd voi striga,<text:line-break/>Vedei s fii p-aproape i s-alergai ndat.<text:line-break/>Cu mirt i c-un burete s vie vre o fat<text:line-break/>Pe corp a m spla.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="VI2"/><text:soft-page-break/>VI</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Susana era-n baia senin, aromat;<text:line-break/>Luna juca pe unda cea crea, colorat<text:line-break/>Cu ap din Eufrat.<text:line-break/>Snu-i mpunge apa i prul su plutete;<text:line-break/>O mn parc-ascunde edenul ce domnete<text:line-break/>Pe bustu-i minunat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Ea se privea n ap pe gnduri, dar voioas;<text:line-break/>Uitase s se-nchine,  cci prea era frumoas...<text:line-break/>Se bucura de ea.<text:line-break/>Se gdela de ap... Btrnii n turbare<text:line-break/>S-azvrl uimii la dnsa; ea ip i tresare!...<text:line-break/>Cu ochii-i sprijinea...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Frumoas eti, Susano! Strigar n uimire<text:line-break/>Invierunai btrnii. Ieim, ieim din fire!<text:line-break/>D! d un srutat,<text:line-break/>O, fiica lui Halsia!... nici iadul n-a s tie!...<text:line-break/>Susana, n ideea de crim, preacurvie,<text:line-break/>Da ipt desperat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">O!Las-te, Susano! Te-om face fericit!<text:line-break/>i s-a-nchina poporul! Sraca, zpcit,<text:line-break/>Cu ochii speriai,<text:line-break/>Se zvrcolea n ap; strngea-n,tre brae snul;<text:line-break/>Se da afund;  dar apa-e curat ca seninul...<text:line-break/>Btrnii nfocai!...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="VII2"/>VII</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"><text:span text:style-name="T8">Ca p-i d-au zidit turnul, Doamne, i zpcete!<text:line-break/>Ca pe-a lui Lot soie, Doamne, m mpietrete!...<text:line-break/>Cum voi putea scpa?...<text:line-break/>Susana-i vinovat!  strigar-atunci btrnii <text:line-break/>inea pe bra un june! A, vino, Ioachime,<text:line-break/>Cci ea l sruta!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">S vie tot poporul!  Vedei ce pngrire!...<text:line-break/>Vedei!... o! ce ruine i ce nelegiuire!<text:line-break/>Ce lucru neiertat!<text:line-break/>Vin! unde eti, Halsie? Vin! Vezi-i btrneea!...<text:line-break/>A lui Ioachim, srmanul, vai! vezi-i tinereea!<text:line-break/>O! ce grozav pcat!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Vedei colo portia ce a deschis spurcatul!<text:line-break/>Vai! n-am putut s-l prindem; nu am privit pcatul;<text:line-break/>Cci el curnd s-a tras!...<text:line-break/>Aci pictorul meter brodeasc pe Susania!<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Aci s zugrveasc, de poate, pe srmana<text:line-break/>n ndoit extaz!...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">The spleen </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De mult se stinse ziua! Rresc i se-ndeseaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Troienii grei de aburi! De mult p-albastrul cer</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rsar i apun stele, -asupr-mi aipeaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Al nopii trist i searbd, ntunecos mister.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce lung-mi fuse noaptea i trist prevegherea!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce gnduri m frmnt! Viperi ce-a-nfuriat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se zvrcol i rumpe n toat-le puterea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ast vas ce le coprinde, i-ntreg m-au veninat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-alunec prin creieri, precum prin vijelie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Alunec, lucete un fulger trector,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i, erpuind, izbete o cremene pustie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aa i ele-n pieptu-mi izbesc cu un fior.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Plutete, plan luna pe lumea adormit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca barc de lumin n ocean senin;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n brae de fantasme simirea amorit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sloboade la plcere un amoros suspin.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar eu, ca sentinel-n perpetua durere,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aint, ncrunt vederea p-al Timpului compas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-ncet, ncet pate i trece n tcere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe smalul fr margini ce numr-al su pas.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce de mine somnul nu va s se lipeasc?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce cnd tot coprinde, eu singur sunt detept?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De unde aste groaze ce stau s nvleasc?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce crime se revoalt? Ce crime m atept?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nimic din toat lumea n ast minut nu-mi place</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mustrare e de cuget!... Dar iar, ce-am fcut</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E doar vro pedeaps la fapte ce voi face?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S mustr viitorul ca i un timp trecut?...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca o ruin vie ce ar simi mugirea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A mrii furiate, a cerului turbat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n lutu-mi ce se surp se turbur gndirea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i inima-mi vestete rstimp nfricoat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sim globul c se mic i cerul se cltete...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Torentele-i de flcri asupr-mi vor cdea?...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E iadul nainte-mi; e mort orice triete:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sunt cobe eu a lumei? sau lumea cobea mea?..</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Un vis n Carpai </text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I17"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Noaptea este neagr, i p-ast col de munte,<text:line-break/>Frigul cel de toamn las p-a mea frunte<text:line-break/>Bruma sa cea rece.<text:line-break/>Tot tace mprejuru-mi, i ochiul nu ptrunde<text:line-break/>Ast cea deas, ce n vi afunde<text:line-break/>Lumea va s-nece.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Umezile boite fulgerul despic.<text:line-break/>Tunetul detun, pe maluri se ardic<text:line-break/>Fr precurmare.<text:line-break/>Crivu-n pdure departe mugete<text:line-break/>i cremenea stncii ce-un oim lcuiete<text:line-break/>Vars grl mare.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II17"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">n ast umezeal, un somn de grele vise<text:line-break/>Aripa sa ntinse pe pleoapele-mi nchise<text:line-break/>i sufletu-mi zri un ce de-nfiorat:<text:line-break/>ntr-un palat de flcri, o sal-i luminat<text:line-break/>De mii fclii i lampe, n stof mbrcat,<text:line-break/>-un om ntr-nsa sta pios ngenucheat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">P searbda lui fa a lampelor lucire<text:line-break/>Lsa s se-ntrevaz adnca lui mhnire,<text:line-break/>Cnd minile spre cer i ardica rugnd.<text:line-break/>M-apropiu cu ncetul s-i aflu tnguirea;<text:line-break/>Doream s-i aflu starea, s-i tiu nenorocirea,<text:line-break/>i iat ce-auzii din gura lui ieind:</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="III10"/>III</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"><text:span text:style-name="T8">Doamne! l-a ta provedin<text:line-break/>Cu toat a mea credin,<text:line-break/></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T8">Eu viu a m ruga.<text:line-break/>i daca a mea dorin<text:line-break/>Va fi i a ta voin,<text:line-break/>Grbete-a asculta!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Ajut-mi docamdat s-mi fac nti un nume:<text:line-break/>S poat s m creaz i bun i ru n lume,<text:line-break/>Cci a lor credin voi ti-ntrebuina.<text:line-break/>Voi prigoni tiranii cu totul s se sting;<text:line-break/>Cruzimea tiraniii pe nimeni s n-ating,<text:line-break/>Tot nedreptitul la mine-a alerga.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Apoi, dup aceastea, i-oi face s-neleag<text:line-break/>Mulimea c e oarb i trebuie s-aleag<text:line-break/>Cine s-o conduc,  i-n fa voi sta eu.<text:line-break/>Oh! d-le lor credin i mie d-mi putere;<text:line-break/>D ntre dnii ura i mie prevedere<text:line-break/>Ca s-i fac s vaz n mine, Dumnezeu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Atta cer, Stpne, i celelalte toate<text:line-break/>Le-oi face-aa de bine, ct crez c nu se poate<text:line-break/>S nu vii din ceruri cu mine-a lcui.<text:line-break/>Voi stinge suvenirea a oricrui nemernic<text:line-break/>Ce-avu puterea toat i nu tiu fi vrednic<text:line-break/>D-absolutul bine ce tu lsai aci.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Tiberii, Caligulii, Neronii i Cristierii,<text:line-break/>i-atia slabi de nger ce vrur-a da puterii<text:line-break/>Aripa ntreag i nu tiur cum,<text:line-break/>i voi terge cu o fapt-n a lumii suvenire;<text:line-break/>Voi face i demonii de mine s se mire;<text:line-break/>Cap s m numeasc n iaduri de acum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Voi face tot supusul la mine s se-nchine<text:line-break/>i orice apsare s zic c e bine:<text:line-break/>Eu s fiu stpnul i toi s-mi fie robi.<text:line-break/>La oriice caprice s-i vz, cu bucurie,<text:line-break/>C-alerg s le-mplineasc; nimic ei s nu tie;<text:line-break/>La a mea porunc, s moar toi ca orbi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">P orice ndrznea fiin gnditoare,<text:line-break/>Voi pune-n temnii negre s nu mai vaz soare;<text:line-break/>Subt pmnt s geam; -acolo va pieri.<text:line-break/>Cu preotu-mpreun, s-mi rz de omenire;<text:line-break/>Prin lege s-i iau mintea, prin sceptru-a sa simire<text:line-break/>Corp, simire, minte voi ti a le strivi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">i daca nesupuii vor ardica o frunte<text:line-break/>S-mi cear socoteal, sau legea-mi s nfrunte,<text:line-break/>Voi ti s-i pui eu bine prin nsi fraii lor.<text:line-break/>Le-oi ti eu stinge neamul cu nsi a lor mn,<text:line-break/>i linitind iar pacea, peste a lor rn<text:line-break/>Voi ardica templuri la bunu-mi Creator.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Iar dup ce voi face ntreag-le pierirea,<text:line-break/>S pui s se omoare, s piar omenirea<text:line-break/>i s las un Noe s poat povesti<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>La alte generaii, c-a stat un prin n lume,<text:line-break/>Ce cu a sa putere i-a dobndit un nume<text:line-break/>Demn de toat stima, ct globu-l va tri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">i-n zilele-mi din urm, spre jalea cea obteasc,<text:line-break/>Voi face din tot locul tot cerul s roeasc<text:line-break/>De ceti aprinse n flcri de rubin.<text:line-break/>-atunci, prin muni de corpuri, un ocean de snge,<text:line-break/>mpurpurnd tot globul, n aburi va resfrnge<text:line-break/>Numele-i, prea sfinte, n linii de senin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">ntr-o grozav spaim, deloc sunt n picioare,<text:line-break/>i-n ochii-mi sta aievea icoana-ngrozitoare;<text:line-break/>O sudoare rece ntreg m-a petrecut.<text:line-break/>Mi-arunc n ceruri ochii i nu-mi vine-a mai crede<text:line-break/>C ochiul nemuririi, prin neguri, mai prevede<text:line-break/>Unde merge lumea i ce plan s-a fcut.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Vaca vduvei </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P15"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd Murgil-ncurc calea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dup-al soarelui sfinit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De mugiri rsun valea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i Brndua mi-a sosit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E oas, e lptoas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Clopotul i-l neleg,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea e mai devreme-acas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dup dnsa nu alerg.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Curge laptele din uger</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca un ipot, un izvor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i Florica i-a strns luger,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">I-a pus sarea n obor.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vielua Viorica</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Salt, salt spre bordei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i fetia mea Florica</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lupt, lupt de curmei;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Amndou-alearg, alearg:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Una-n blid, la dumicat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Alta prinde, va s sparg</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ugerul ce i-am lsat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar Brndua linge p-una</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i la alta cat blnd,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Coarnele i sunt ca luna,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Le mngie tot mugind.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd Zioril se deteapt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bag vieaua n celar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i Florica-n prisp-ateapt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu Brndua pe vcar.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Am vndut pe la Drgaic</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Doi juncui trai prin inel,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lini ca rochia de chitaic,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-ast-iarn un viel.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">P-amndou ea ne ine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea ni-i singurul venit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La orice nevoie vine; </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, nu-i cerei ierbrit!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Vara</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I18"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Frumoas este vara!<text:line-break/>E cerul cu lumin<text:line-break/>i pomii cu verdea;<text:line-break/>Natura este plin;<text:line-break/>Roatic e seara,<text:line-break/>Glbuie dimineaa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cmpii prea colorate<text:line-break/>Exal miros din flori,<text:line-break/>i viersuri variate<text:line-break/>n cerul fr nori,<text:line-break/>Ca dintr-o harp mare<text:line-break/>S-aud n deprtare<text:line-break/>i-n inimi dau fiori.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">mi place ast dat,<text:line-break/>April cnd nflorete<text:line-break/>i pomii i cmpia,<text:line-break/>Pdurea cea uscat<text:line-break/>S vz cum nverzete,<text:line-break/>Cum nate bucuria.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">S vz cum se destinde<text:line-break/>Azurul cel ceresc;<text:line-break/>S vz cum se aprinde<text:line-break/>Cu focul pmntesc,<text:line-break/>Cu munca i cu sporul,<text:line-break/>Sperana i amorul<text:line-break/>n toi ci vieuiesc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">mi plac i gndceii<text:line-break/>Cu-aripe mititele,<text:line-break/>Cu felurimi de fee,<text:line-break/>mi plac i flutureii<text:line-break/>De smal pe floricele,<text:line-break/>Cnd zbor cu aripi cree.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:soft-page-break/>mi place rndurica<text:line-break/>La cuib s-o vz zidind,<text:line-break/>mi place psric<text:line-break/>S-o vz pe pui hrnind,<text:line-break/>mi plac i brotceii, <text:line-break/>Se-mbuc i porumbeii<text:line-break/>Iubind i gungunind.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">mi place-atunci grdina<text:line-break/>i florile-ngrijite; <text:line-break/>S vz crescnd zambila;<text:line-break/>S vz roind stupina<text:line-break/>Pe coaste nsmltite;<text:line-break/>S vz rznd copila;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">S vz eznd la soare<text:line-break/>Copilul mic i blnd;<text:line-break/>S vz c nu mai moare<text:line-break/>Un orfelin flmnd.<text:line-break/>S vz ndestularea;<text:line-break/>S vz mbielugarea<text:line-break/>Pe cer i pe pmnt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Atunci cel ce iubete,<text:line-break/>Sau a iubit vreodat,<text:line-break/>S-absoarbe n tcere,<text:line-break/>De vise se rpete,<text:line-break/>De vise ce-i arat<text:line-break/>Trecuta lui plcere</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">n unda care fuge,<text:line-break/>n crngul cel ntins,<text:line-break/>n mielul care suge,<text:line-break/>n focul cel aprins,<text:line-break/>n umbra ce se-mparte,<text:line-break/>n dealul cel departe,<text:line-break/>n danul ce s-a prins.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Atunci, el parc vede<text:line-break/>Ieind din crini, lalele,<text:line-break/>O nimf ce viseaz;<text:line-break/>Atunci, pare c-ar crede<text:line-break/>C vede-n viorele<text:line-break/>Ctri ce-l ainteaz.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Zefirii cnd prin frunze<text:line-break/>Adie-n brebenei,<text:line-break/>El simte p-a lui buze<text:line-break/>Trecnd suflarea ei.<text:line-break/>O simte-ntr-o cntare<text:line-break/>De cuc, privighetoare,<text:line-break/>O simte-n fluturei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Se-nsoar-atuncea firea;<text:line-break/>Srbeaz universul<text:line-break/>Ateii i pgnii!<text:line-break/>Fetie-nv iubirea,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Poetul afl viersul,<text:line-break/>ntineresc btrnii.<text:line-break/>n om e fantazia,<text:line-break/>Amoru-n trandafir;<text:line-break/>n ochi e bucuria,<text:line-break/>Plcerea n zefir;<text:line-break/>Plcerea n gndire,<text:line-break/>Plcerea n unire;<text:line-break/>Natura e-n delir.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II18"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">O! mult mi place vara<text:line-break/>Cu verzi pduri stufoase,<text:line-break/>Cu pomii plini de roade,<text:line-break/>Cu grnele, secara<text:line-break/>n holde mari, frumoase,<text:line-break/>Cu spicul care cade!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cu noaptea nstelat,<text:line-break/>Cu cerul cel senin,<text:line-break/>Cu luna cea curat,<text:line-break/>Cu aerul cel lin,<text:line-break/>Cu pasri cnttoare,<text:line-break/>Cu fluturi peste floare,<text:line-break/>Cu stupi cu fagul plin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">O! vara, cltorul,<text:line-break/>S umble-i este lesne<text:line-break/>i-n munte i-n cmpie;<text:line-break/>Cci rece e izvorul,<text:line-break/>Cci rar se afl-n bezne,<text:line-break/>Cci tot e veselie;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cci roua scnteiaz<text:line-break/>Cnd ziua s-a ivi;<text:line-break/>Cci raza-l lumineaz,<text:line-break/>i cnd o osteni,<text:line-break/>O umbr se destinde,<text:line-break/>n brae-i l coprinde,<text:line-break/>n somn a-l odini!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Atunci, mulimi de glasuri,<text:line-break/>De pasri certtoare<text:line-break/>l fur ncet pe vise;<text:line-break/>Atunci el simte psuri<text:line-break/>De nimfe juctoare<text:line-break/>Cu snuri tot deschise.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">O! Vara, orfelinul<text:line-break/>Prinii i-a aflat!<text:line-break/>O! Vara piere chinul;<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Sracul e bogat;<text:line-break/>Viaa e frumoas;<text:line-break/>Natura e pompoas;<text:line-break/>Coliba e palat!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Viaa-mi se strecoar </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">1837, martie</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Viaa-mi se strecoar, ca rul se grbete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-ajung la izvorul de unde a plecat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De june nc veted, nimic nu m oprete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca s ating eu moartea ce tu mi-ai nsemnat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mormntu-mi este-aproape, mi grin, m coprinde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe calea morii ns eu stau, m mai opresc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M uit la vreo scpare, dar noaptea se destinde</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i norii desperanii n fa m izbesc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O! taina mea cea mare n veci tu nu vei ti-o;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Greala-i fr tire eu nu te las s plngi;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i grabnica mea moarte tu nu vei auzi-o</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dect ca o nuvel de care nu te-atingi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar daca a mea umbr la tine se abate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-i spuie c mormntu-mi suspin d-al tu dor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te du atunci pe pasu-i rina-mi s-i arate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-atunci, clcnd pe dnsa, precurm al meu dor!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu salcia ce-a plnge s lai atunci s caz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O lacrm la crucea ce ie-am consfinit!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu candela-mi cea trist strbate a ei raz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin negura etern ce voi fi rtcit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe piatr-mi las-i ochii,.citete al meu nume,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Gndete-n care vrst m despresc de lume</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i scrie cu-a ta mn p-ast lesped de granit:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aci am pus p-acela ce-atta m-a iubit!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>nc o salutare </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P17"><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cest que lamour est comme un arbre: il pousse<text:line-break/>de lui-mme, jette profondment ses racines dans<text:line-break/>tout notre tre, et continue souvent de verdoyer sur<text:line-break/>un coeur en ruines.</text:span><text:bookmark text:name="cite_ref-19"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/nc_o_salutare#cite_note-1" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T3">[1]</text:span></text:a></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">nc o salutare, i fie cea din urm!<text:line-break/>nc o salutare, -apoi, apoi precurm,<text:line-break/>Precurm-ast ntlnit,<text:line-break/>Fantasm ce m-ncongiuri, fantasm mult iubit,<text:line-break/>n care-a mea via n veci fu absorbit,<text:line-break/>n care am trit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">Eti tu ast fantasm! te sim! te saluteaz<text:line-break/>Ast suflet, al tu frate! <text:line-break/>Vezi tu? m-nfioreaz<text:line-break/>O cttur-a ta!...<text:line-break/>Frumoas ca n ziua d-ntia ntlnire;<text:line-break/>Frumoas ca sperana ce-ntia mea iubiren faa ta cta, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">Te vz pe rnd, cnd trist, rident, cnd glumind,<text:line-break/>Te vz n aromire; te vz apoi dormind;<text:line-break/>Te vz oricum voiesc!<text:line-break/>Puterea a te-aduce mi dete mie-Amorul<text:line-break/>Ca s-mi nutreasc mintea, ca s-mi aline dorul;<text:line-break/>Cci, crede: te iubesc!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">i ce mi pas dac vederea-i mi-e oprit!<text:line-break/>Oh! ast frumusee de care-eti ocolit,<text:line-break/>Trsurile cereti,<text:line-break/>Sunt slab-nchipuire a inimei din tine! <text:line-break/>i ce? Fantasma asta ce-etern a fost cu mine, <text:line-break/>n ea tu nu trieti?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">Nu este al tu suflet ce-acum m ocolete?<text:line-break/>Nu este al tu suflet pe care-al meu iubete?<text:line-break/>Tu nu m vezi deloc?<text:line-break/>i ce amestec este ntre amor i luturi?<text:line-break/>Amorul este spirit i n cereti inuturi,<text:line-break/>Un spirit are loc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">Cnd luna este plin i-n unde se descrie,<text:line-break/>Cnd zefirii prin frunze alin, alin adie,<text:line-break/>Cnd ziorile zresc;<text:line-break/>Cnd soarele se-nal, cnd soarele apune,<text:line-break/>Cnd pasrea de var durerea sa i spune,<text:line-break/>Cnd pomii nfloresc</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">i cmpii se-nsmlteaz, cnd fructul lor se coace,<text:line-break/>Cnd vine seceriul, cnd mustu-n lin se stoarce,<text:line-break/>Cnd pomii glbenii i leapd podoaba ce vntul risipete,<text:line-break/>Cnd pasrea de var durerea sa i spune,<text:line-break/>Cnd fulgul de ninsoare pmntul nvelete,<text:line-break/>Troienii-s grmdii;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11"><text:soft-page-break/>Pe cnd natura-e vie, pe cnd natura-e moart,<text:line-break/>A ta, a ta fantasm, a ta fantasm poart<text:line-break/>Tot lucru-n ochiul meu.<text:line-break/>Pe tine vz n somnu-mi, pe tine-n deteptare,<text:line-break/>Pe tine n tot gndul, n orice cugetare,<text:line-break/>Cnd chem pe Dumnezeu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">Tu! tu mi eti natura! tu-mi eti divinitatea!<text:line-break/>i daca-mi place viaa, de voi eternitatea,<text:line-break/>E numai fapta ta!...<text:line-break/>Mai iart-m o dait s-i spui a mea cin!<text:line-break/>D drumul unei lacrimi la cruda-mi suferin,<text:line-break/>Cci poate m-i ierta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">O! lacrma nmoaie oricare ndurerare!<text:line-break/>D-i drumul, i n somnu-i, n toat-a ta visare,<text:line-break/>Ei s m vezi plngnd.<text:line-break/>D! d audiin l-ast suflet ce-l zdrobete<text:line-break/>Cirea i mustrarea! l iart i-l priimete<text:line-break/>n faa ta rugind! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">i cine tie daca o astfel de-ntlnire<text:line-break/>Nu poate s aduc -o altfel de unire,<text:line-break/>Un altfel de iertat!<text:line-break/>Cci sufletul, o, angel, are n el ideea<text:line-break/>Care concepe fapta; ideea fu schinteia<text:line-break/>Ce Totul a creat...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">Ce cugete m fur, ce cer mi se deschide!<text:line-break/>Visarea m rpete! un paradis surde<text:line-break/>i angeli m coprind!...<text:line-break/>Sunt oare n ajunul acelui ceresc Bine?<text:line-break/>S mai auz eu glasu-i, s mai triesc n tine,<text:line-break/>S te mai vz zmbind!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">Tu tii, tu tii prea bine de plnge, se bocete<text:line-break/>O frunte-att de lat? tu tii de s-umilete<text:line-break/>Un caracter c-al meu; <text:line-break/>Dar ns nainite-i am fost lichid cear<text:line-break/>Din care-a ta ochead a scos ce-a vrut s cear;<text:line-break/>Cci tu fui al meu zeu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">Adnc fu mplntat n mine-a ta putere!<text:line-break/>Din ziua-n care chipu-i inti a mea vedere,<text:line-break/>Eu fui fptura ta.<text:line-break/>Mi-era ntins fruntea, acum e ncreit;<text:line-break/>i palida mea fa, i tmpla mea albit<text:line-break/>i-o poate arta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">Tu nu mai vei s afli de-mi este ru sau bine!<text:line-break/>O singur greal a ters cu totu-n tine<text:line-break/>O via de amor.<text:line-break/>Lovirea ce i-am dat-o, o crez c doare tare:<text:line-break/>E greu un bra de frate!<text:line-break/>D ran-afund, mare<text:line-break/>Un frate-ucigtor!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11"><text:soft-page-break/>Dar ns o cire atta de amar,<text:line-break/>Dar ns-a contiinii-mi cumplit, grea povar<text:line-break/>Destul te-a rzbunat.<text:line-break/>D-ai ti tu ce durere d-atuncea m muncete,<text:line-break/>Ce iad mi este viaa, ce gnd m tot gonete,<text:line-break/>De mult m-ai fi iertat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">Cci tu eti tip, o, angel! eti tipul de femeie;<text:line-break/>i o femeie iart, cci are-n ea schinteie<text:line-break/>D-a drept din Dumnezeu;<text:line-break/>Din Dumnezeu ce iart pe cel ce se ciete;<text:line-break/>Din Dumnezeu ce tie martirul ce-l dubete<text:line-break/>i dorul su cel greu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">Dar daca a mea vin a fost att de mare,<text:line-break/>nct cu svrire te-a dus n ndurare,<text:line-break/>Cu totul te-a-mpietrit;<text:line-break/>De vezi c nu sunt lacrmi s-i poat da simire<text:line-break/>De vezi c nu te-nmoaie deloc a mea cire</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">i ct am suferit;<text:line-break/>De nu e sacrificiu ce-n ajutor s-mi vie;<text:line-break/>De nu e ncercare ce poate s nvie<text:line-break/>Comptimirea ta;<text:line-break/>Daca ast nume nu-l vei mai mult la auzire-i;<text:line-break/>i daca el nu are mai mult n suvenire-i<text:line-break/>Un drum a mai intra, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">Atunci, priimete, scumpo, s treac lng tine<text:line-break/>Tmia ce s-exal din cel ce-i va tot bine,<text:line-break/>Ce-n veci te-a adorat!<text:line-break/>Priimete-mi adorarea ca o tmie snt!<text:line-break/>Ascult mpcat ast suflet ce te cnt<text:line-break/>De cnd te-a contmplat!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">Cnd, ctre moate sacre, n templul Provedinei<text:line-break/>De pe altar se-nal profumele Credinei,<text:line-break/>Credem c s-au priimit;<text:line-break/>M las n prerea c ruga mea din urm<text:line-break/>Ajunge pn la tine, cci viaa mea se curm,<text:line-break/>E-aproape de sfrit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P11">Iar dac-adnc n tine tot nc mai triete<text:line-break/>O tnr schinteie, de simi c se-mblnzete<text:line-break/>Auzu-i la dureri, <text:line-break/>Atunci, atunci, o, angel, mcar i de departe,<text:line-break/>Trimite-mi raza vieii-mi!  Atunci, ah! f-mi o parte<text:line-break/>Din vechele-mi averi!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="P25" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="Note13"/>Note</text:h>
   <text:list xml:id="list1809129887" text:style-name="L4">
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:bookmark text:name="cite_note-114"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/nc_o_salutare#cite_ref-1" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T2"></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci dragostea este ca un copac: crete de la sine, i nfige rdcinile adnc in ntreaga noastr fiin i adesea continu s nverzeasc pe o inim n ruin.</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
   </text:list>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>i ce-ar fi oare omul </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ce-ar fi oare Omul cnd n-ar simi Amor?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-ar fi i lumea asta de soare nenclzit;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-ar fi fptura-ntreag de oameni neprivit; </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O noapte fr stele, sau cerul ntr-un nor;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Deerturi nisipoase ce-ngroap-al nostru pas;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copac ce n-are frunz; cmpie fr floare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Livede fr fluturi i flori fr odoare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pduri ce nu rsun d-al paserilor glas;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Femeie fr lacrimi, o mum fr dor;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O primvar trist de tot fr verdea;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Natura amorit, natura fr via;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Asemene-ar fi Omul cnd n-ar simi Amor!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">iganul vndut </text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I19"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"><text:span text:style-name="T8">Vai! ieri aveam soie, aveam i tat, mum,<text:line-break/>Aveam un copila! <text:line-break/>Viaa-mi prea lesne, robia-mi prea glum<text:line-break/>Privind al meu sla!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cnd triti veneam, pe noapte din munca cea n sil<text:line-break/>n care ne-osndeam<text:line-break/>i dam o roat vetrii,  oh! ne priveam cu mil,<text:line-break/>Dar tot ne mngiam;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Mcar c de la munc veneam obosii foarte<text:line-break/>De foame i bti;<text:line-break/>Mcar c-adesea-oar rugam a noastr moarte<text:line-break/>Ca s scpm de ri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cnd este-ntre-ai si omul i afl mngierea<text:line-break/>D-ar fi orict mhnit!<text:line-break/>Dar cnd strin e omul, atunci e grea durerea<text:line-break/>i focul ndoit!...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II19"/><text:soft-page-break/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">O! oameni fr lege! Stpni fr-ndurare<text:line-break/>Cu inim de fier!<text:line-break/>Cnd smulgei unei mume un singur fiu ce are,<text:line-break/>Gndii atunci la cer?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Gndii oari la durerea ce cearc-acea srac?<text:line-break/>L-acele reci sudori<text:line-break/>n care desperarea i lacrima i seac,<text:line-break/>L-acele cruzi fiori</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Ce se deept ntr-nsa cnd i aduce-aminte<text:line-break/>C nu mai are fiu,<text:line-break/>C nu o s-l mai vad!  i piere dinainte! <text:line-break/>l d-n mormnt de viu?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">O! cnd ne dai botezul zicei c suntem rude;<text:line-break/>Zicei c suntem frai!...<text:line-break/>De Domnul nu v temei? Nu tii c el v-aude?<text:line-break/>Gndii c-l nelai?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cnd v jucai cu oameni ntocmai ca cu vite, <text:line-break/>i ce zic!  mult mai reu!...<text:line-break/>Cci voi ctai de vite; sunt mult mai ngrijite;<text:line-break/>Iar noi, muncii mereu!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Un cal n grajdul vostru ce ngrijire n-are?<text:line-break/>P-un cal ci robi n-ai da!<text:line-break/>iganul rob, srmanul, ar fi el oare-n stare<text:line-break/>C-un cal a msura?</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="III11"/>III</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">M-or fi plngnd prinii!...<text:line-break/>De mum-mea mi-e team<text:line-break/>C-o fi murit jelind!<text:line-break/>Cnd i ntreab fiu-meu: Unde e tata, mam?<text:line-break/>Of! cum l-or fi minind!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cnd s-l mai vd o dat, parc mi-ar fi mai bine,<text:line-break/>Parc-a putea s mor!...<text:line-break/>Nevasta mea, sraca! o fi plngnd de mine,<text:line-break/>O fi murind de dor!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Acela ce ne vinde nu vinde i gndirea;<text:line-break/>Mcar c s-a tocmit<text:line-break/>Pe sufletele noastre; mcar c omenirea<text:line-break/>Nimic a socotit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">i-a rs el d-astea toate! i-a rs el de durere<text:line-break/>Pentru puin venit!...<text:line-break/>S-i fi luat lui fiii, prinii i muiere, <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Oari cum ar fi trit?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">O! ct ar fi mai bine s fim ca dobitoace,<text:line-break/>S nu simim deloc<text:line-break/>A noastr chinuire!<text:line-break/>S nu tim ce ne face<text:line-break/>Pe cnd n cri ne joc!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="IV7"/>IV</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Ce-o fi luat pe mine?... A fi-n mai bun stare!<text:line-break/>Of! ranele m dor<text:line-break/>i lanul ru m strnge!<text:line-break/>M-au strns, cumpliii, tare...<text:line-break/>Cum a voi s mor!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Vedea-va faa-i, Doamne, stpnul ce m vinde?<text:line-break/>Copiii i-or tri?<text:line-break/>Pe neamul su pcatul oari nu se va ntinde<text:line-break/>Cnd el nu va mai fi?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Oare-mi pstrezi acolo ceea ce-aci-mi lipsete?<text:line-break/>Voi fi eu rspltit<text:line-break/>De muncile i chinuri, la care m-osndete<text:line-break/>Acest nelegiuit?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Bagi tu de seam, Doamne, la ast omenire,<text:line-break/>Cum merge treaba-aci?<text:line-break/>tiai ce am a trage cnd mi dedei simire<text:line-break/>i ce fel voi tri?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cnd mi dedei via, cnd mi dedei soie,<text:line-break/>Cnd tat m-ai fcut,<text:line-break/>tiai ce-mi scrie soarta?  &apos;Nscut c-s n robie,<text:line-break/>i c-o s fiu vndut?</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="V5"/>V</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">Aa vorbea-ntr-o noapte, flmnd, nchis n cas,<text:line-break/>iganul cumprat.<text:line-break/>Privea gemnd la lun; dar nu putea s ias,<text:line-break/>Cci strns era legat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10">A doua zi, stpnul mai c se ntristase<text:line-break/>Aflnd c-a pgubit<text:line-break/>Patrusprezece galbeni;  atta cumprase<text:line-break/>iganul ce-a murit.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>ii tu minte oar </text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I20"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">ii tu minte oar,<text:line-break/>La bi, ast-var,<text:line-break/>Cnd pe rpi tcute,<text:line-break/>Pe vrfuri de munte,<text:line-break/>Noi ne ntlneam?</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II20"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">ii tu minte oar,<text:line-break/>Pentru-ntia oar,<text:line-break/>Cnd la tulpini,<text:line-break/>Jos lng grli,<text:line-break/>Noi ne srutam?</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="III12"/>III</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">ii tu minte oar,<text:line-break/>Cnd ieeam pe sear,<text:line-break/>Ne-ascundeam de lume<text:line-break/>-adunam alune<text:line-break/>ntr-un aluni?</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="IV8"/>IV</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">ii tu minte oar,<text:line-break/>Acea cprioar,<text:line-break/>Ce dasupra noastr<text:line-break/>Cobora pe coast<text:line-break/>Cnd noi stam piti?</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="V6"/><text:soft-page-break/>V</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">ii tu minte oar,<text:line-break/>Bura cea uoar,<text:line-break/>Cnd pe subt umbrare,<text:line-break/>Fugeam, fuga mare,<text:line-break/>Tot ntr-o manta?</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="VI3"/>VI</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">ii tu minte oar,<text:line-break/>Noaptea de la moar;<text:line-break/>Grmad-n drochi,<text:line-break/>Cnd eu pe chichi<text:line-break/>ineam mna ta?</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="VII3"/>VII</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">ii tu minte oar,<text:line-break/>La zapciu pe scar,<text:line-break/>Cnd toi cri n cas<text:line-break/>Jucau lng mas,<text:line-break/>Cum ne-mbriam?</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="VIII2"/>VIII</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">ii tu minte oar,<text:line-break/>n acea ccioar,<text:line-break/>Abia dup boal,<text:line-break/>Culcat p-a ta poal,<text:line-break/>&apos;n ochi cum ne citeam?</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="IX1"/>IX</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">ii tu minte oar,<text:line-break/>Acea dumbrvioar,<text:line-break/>Devale la grl,<text:line-break/>Cnd, privind la trl,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Stam l-acel izvor</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="X1"/>X</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9">ii tu minte oar,<text:line-break/>Toi cnd ne ctar,<text:line-break/>i noi n trsur,<text:line-break/>Strni i gur-n gur,<text:line-break/>Ne juram amor?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"/>
  </office:text>
